	 ('76c21140-dfc3-4cd7-842f-7c9b95ea75f3'::uuid,'Woman-Yelling-At-Cat','This meme template combines two distinct images to create a humorous juxtaposition. On the left side, we see two women in what appears to be a dramatic scene from a reality TV show or similar program. One woman, with blonde hair, is shouting and pointing emphatically off-screen, her face contorted in an expression of shock or outrage. Beside her, a brunette woman looks on with a concerned and slightly open-mouthed expression.

On the right side of the image, we see a dinner table setting with a white cat sitting at the table. The cat has a distinct, somewhat grumpy or unimpressed expression, with narrowed eyes that give it an air of disdain or indifference. In front of the cat is a plate with what looks like a salad, and a human hand can be seen reaching into the frame, presumably to serve or adjust something on the table.

The humor of this meme template comes from the contrast between the intense, emotional reaction of the women on the left and the completely unbothered, almost bored-looking cat on the right. It''s as if the cat is the target of the woman''s outburst but remains utterly unaffected by it.

This format is often used to humorously depict overreactions to mundane situations, with the cat representing a calm, unimpressed response to someone else''s dramatics. The template plays on the idea of cats being aloof and unbothered by human concerns, which is a common theme in internet cat humor.

The composition of the meme, splitting the frame between human drama and feline indifference, creates a perfect setup for various comedic scenarios where someone''s intense emotions are met with complete apathy or disinterest.','/memes/Woman-Yelling-At-Cat.jpg',2,'{}','{"Women yelling","confused cat","girl screaming at cat","angry woman yelling at cat at dinner table","lady screams at cat","woman pointing at cat","smudge the cat","woman yelling at a cat","crying woman","fury lady cat eating salad","cat table","cat no","me dijiste que","chica gritando a gato","girl screaming cat"}',0.0,'[-0.014329761,0.0022769074,0.0032541137,-0.0034458314,-0.008528855,-0.062960155,-0.036172144,0.021026393,-0.026791772,0.057785388,0.010670413,0.0052949768,0.020480132,-0.009297783,-0.014610326,-0.010070475,-0.0012020806,-0.03564807,-0.03594148,0.016527606,0.008215573,0.009116777,-0.0682913,-0.022038568,0.003307925,0.085089184,0.0068386905,0.020692507,0.07459684,0.002425339,0.006282691,-0.008599887,-0.0125621725,-0.042695273,0.01595941,-0.019162195,0.029491402,-0.015095435,-0.042992953,-0.01996764,0.03153063,-0.025826067,0.03149037,-0.040746752,-0.020580886,-0.021004079,0.0011971323,0.014522662,0.029899333,-0.024417857,0.014326211,-0.040879052,0.013359232,-0.017713478,-0.04925206,-0.030387435,-0.03053793,-0.004724592,0.015328732,0.006704264,0.05358631,0.0029131228,-0.012028159,-0.041149143,-0.017149713,0.0040688016,-0.0053849523,-0.025004644,-0.029612305,-0.037824888,0.01620173,0.0025333338,-0.021764673,-0.0054975855,-0.07271058,-0.03246529,-0.022111595,-0.016979279,0.012117095,0.0066167633,0.036288384,0.026819222,-0.016499657,-0.014268877,-0.022517765,-0.018460907,0.01534358,0.035824906,-0.0050008763,-0.012775257,-0.009796667,0.03976624,-0.015216339,0.043827154,0.010837809,0.052015364,0.0100101335,0.025310148,0.003182472,0.005176793,-0.02200688,0.043155093,-0.01758581,0.037518393,-0.07100971,0.01711548,0.06331854,-0.00532125,-0.043579377,-0.028075334,-0.02825379,-0.010289587,0.0078260