	 ('ce6ac796-b227-41ec-b596-010b0e39ca0a'::uuid,'Awkward-Moment-Sealion','This meme template features a close-up portrait of an adorable seal, known colloquially as the "Awkward Moment Seal" or "Uncomfortable Situation Seal." The image captures the seal''s face in exquisite detail, showcasing its distinctive features that make it perfect for expressing discomfort or awkwardness in social situations.

The seal''s large, dark eyes are the focal point of the image, appearing slightly wide and alert, giving an impression of surprise or unease. Its gaze is directed slightly off-center, as if avoiding direct eye contact, which adds to the sense of discomfort the meme typically conveys.

The seal''s snout is prominently featured, with its nostrils clearly visible and whiskers sprouting from its muzzle. The texture of its skin is evident, with a pattern of small dots across its nose and face, giving it a soft, velvety appearance characteristic of seals.

One of the most striking elements is the seal''s mouth, which appears to be tightly closed and slightly curved, creating what looks like an awkward, forced smile or grimace. This expression is key to the meme''s popularity, as it perfectly encapsulates the feeling of being in an uncomfortable situation and not knowing how to react.

The seal''s head is framed by several folds of skin around its neck, creating a series of concentric rings that add to the rotund, pillowy appearance of the animal. These folds contribute to the overall endearing quality of the image while also emphasizing the seal''s posture of slight recoil or tension.

The background of the image is blurred but appears to be a natural, outdoor setting, likely a beach or coastline where seals are commonly found. This neutral backdrop keeps the focus squarely on the seal''s expressive face.

