	 ('fd43258f-0f93-4c10-8c11-7425a5a95a3b'::uuid,'Change-My-Mind','This meme template features a young man seated at a small folding table outdoors, seemingly on a college campus or in a public park setting. The scene has a casual, impromptu feel to it.

The central figure is wearing a bright blue sweatshirt and has short dark hair. He''s sitting behind the table with a confident, slightly challenging expression, gesturing with one hand as if inviting debate or discussion.

On the table in front of him are a few sheets of paper, a drink, and what appears to be a name placard, though its text isn''t visible in this image. The most prominent element is a large sign attached to the front of the table that reads "CHANGE MY MIND" in bold, capital letters.

The background shows a brick pathway, grassy areas, and trees, suggesting a park-like environment. There are buildings visible in the distance, reinforcing the impression of a campus or urban park setting.

This image has become a popular meme template used to express opinions on controversial topics, inviting others to debate or "change the mind" of the person holding the opinion. The format lends itself to easy editing, where the "CHANGE MY MIND" text can be replaced with various statements or claims, often provocative or humorous in nature.

