	 ('95016826-5ba5-46d8-9ff4-cdb633c31c5d'::uuid,'Hide-the-Pain-Harold','This meme template features two sequential images of an older man sitting at a desk, interacting with a laptop. The setting appears to be a bright, modern home office or living space with minimalist decor visible in the background, including small potted plants and a circular ornament on a shelf.

In the first image, the man is looking at his laptop screen with an expression of mild amusement or interest. He''s holding a light-colored mug, presumably containing a hot beverage. He''s dressed casually in a light gray button-up shirt, suggesting a relaxed, at-home atmosphere.

The second image shows the same scene moments later. The key difference is the man''s facial expression, which has transformed into a wide, beaming smile. His eyes are crinkled with joy, and his teeth are visible in a hearty laugh. This dramatic shift in expression is the focal point of the meme and is typically used to convey a sudden realization or discovery of something highly amusing or satisfying.

The man''s appearance - with his balding head, white beard, and gentle demeanor - gives him a grandfatherly or wise elder persona. This adds to the meme''s versatility, as it can be used to represent various scenarios involving unexpected joy, especially in contexts where an older person might be seen as out of touch but then shows surprising understanding or appreciation.

The clean, bright aesthetic of the room and the modern laptop juxtaposed with the older man''s appearance creates an interesting visual contrast that adds depth to the meme''s potential interpretations. This template is often used to express moments of sudden clarity, ironic humor, or the joy of discovering something unexpectedly delightful on the internet.','/memes/Hide-the-Pain-Harold.jpg',2,'{}','{"sad life harold",maurice,"hide pain climate change",herold}',0.0,'[0.026714133,-0.0385971,0.02121668,0.033786096,0.00940386,-0.046394683,-0.00982227,0.0018807302,0.0018140333,0.04277063,0.004320997,0.011265791,0.02691923,0.013820914,-0.0017629642,-0.036674935,-0.005352097,-0.025751937,-0.043058343,0.018105263,0.03211655,0.014429564,-0.042237453,-0.041452724,-0.00012810217,0.049764466,-0.012988407,0.032642864,0.07800971,0.01319457,0.008835384,-0.004139515,0.0032701564,-0.044334084,-0.01177562,-0.0036751784,0.015442998,-0.037700865,-0.009422519,-0.04225162,0.02334781,-0.005101978,0.027947254,-0.025972337,-0.048023753,-0.021454666,-0.019206835,0.0029185705,0.052033413,-0.013076314,0.020380171,-0.03836795,0.009361659,0.0036030137,0.007254893,-0.04588049,-0.023694653,0.00453931,0.00024398691,0.018211665,0.048554562,0.040580608,-0.0017943482,-0.04354415,0.002388734,0.001971477,-0.004106339,-0.015396214,-0.03719745,-0.0050732107,-0.002427724,0.019953074,-0.006568559,-0.02874132,-0.04139077,0.005925109,-0.015607098,0.016724544,-0.013837112,0.014452146,0.036157854,0.039443478,0.0012198981,-0.01825165,-0.03562812,-0.02894875,0.060100846,0.043416146,0.0031388688,-0.036555205,0.018534949,0.025982322,0.015238577,0.010719601,0.0038899384,0.053255774,-0.018747805,0.06218135,-0.0027202212,0.028040944,-0.015173543,0.033627305,-0.038397804,0.030378094,-0.054751895,0.00513221,0.04821541,-0.018175619,-0.04090956,-0.03888904,0.021585956,-0.018568957,0.009605162,0.03567721,-0.017057978,0.017315088,0.0048148707,0.04022085,-0.027129835,0.006377432,-0.052204356,-0.018964209,-0.011176411,-0.020