	 ('1a9a5c46-40ba-4ffe-b7e3-37d7ed48f2d7'::uuid,'Surprised-Pikachu','This meme template features a close-up image of Pikachu, the iconic yellow electric mouse Pokémon from the popular Nintendo franchise. The image is a zoomed-in, slightly blurry screenshot likely taken from the Pokémon animated series, giving it a low-resolution, pixelated quality that adds to its meme appeal.

Pikachu''s face dominates the frame, filling most of the image. Its bright yellow coloring stands out vividly against a blurred background of green and brown tones, suggesting a forest or natural setting. The Pokémon''s distinctive features are clearly visible: large, round eyes with reddish-brown irises, small black nose, and red circular cheeks characteristic of the species.

What makes this particular image memetic is Pikachu''s expression. Its mouth is open in a small, perfectly round "O" shape, giving the creature a look of shock, surprise, or confusion. This exaggerated expression, combined with the wide-eyed stare, conveys a sense of sudden realization or disbelief that resonates with meme creators and viewers alike.

The image''s composition, focusing tightly on Pikachu''s face, emphasizes the reaction and allows the expression to be the central element of any meme created with this template. The slightly off-center framing adds to the sense of unexpectedness or awkwardness often associated with the meme''s usage.

This "Surprised Pikachu" meme template has become widely recognized in internet culture, often used to depict reactions to obvious or predictable outcomes that someone failed to anticipate. Its popularity stems from its versatility in expressing bewilderment across various situations, as well as the nostalgic and cute appeal of Pikachu as a character beloved by many generations.','/memes/Surprised-Pikachu.jpg',1,'{}','{"shocked pikachu","surprised picachu"}',0.0,'[0.022616468,-0.008946464,0.0028313864,0.0022636068,0.0031430942,-0.04258654,0.016213164,-0.03405389,0.03544766,0.04539196,0.016676692,-0.030132718,0.032152567,0.020157905,-0.020002116,-0.008651664,-0.0063731144,-0.026456706,-0.013875224,0.01536545,-0.00021976225,0.011571599,-0.036456846,-0.040617384,0.004261569,0.043468073,0.006697754,-0.01698232,0.031813186,-0.0033757216,-0.008642817,0.0163948,0.008479791,-0.039005827,-0.014223484,-0.022494528,0.009206454,-0.023252062,-0.049043033,-0.027409403,0.069537684,-0.022002062,0.035715044,-0.013828398,-0.04183251,-0.031262968,-0.02446546,0.0004961133,0.027350763,-0.050828103,0.02709574,0.028923964,-0.004881998,0.032032378,-0.048796497,-0.043705087,0.009719148,-0.037612453,0.009476269,0.038763426,0.01577602,0.009126583,0.016439496,-0.03985371,-0.026580038,0.0048091575,-0.045605414,-0.03201809,-0.016592113,0.004876971,0.019003803,-0.00069918856,0.0028650598,-0.011574036,-0.05183945,0.0062085763,-0.011440089,-0.0044394713,-0.00887759,0.0133610815,0.03466399,0.026461063,-0.030630691,-0.035391137,-0.032647606,-0.026729831,0.015710834,-0.0057918443,-0.035861026,-0.0106134685,-0.020541437,0.07874989,0.0031332786,0.036545873,0.038348198,0.027064951,0.0026731852,0.028145453,-0.021174379,-0.022760345,0.018551545,0.038155824,0.02095888,0.03583253,-0.013262402,-0.015946602,0.0083321305,-0.008491621,-0.04849313,-0.020984814,0.016661724,-0.022111695,0.011694974,-0.01576946,-0.030893842,0.04530333,-0.020161966,0.060246736,-0.034453988,-0.021433976,-0.06837792,-0.02551071,-0.0248