	 ('5e557779-3a4d-4512-ade2-9ff827d2ead2'::uuid,'Creepy-Condescending-Wonka','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a character from the 1971 film "Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory." The image captures the eccentric and mischievous essence of the candy maker.

The character is wearing a distinctive costume that includes a large purple velvet coat and a brown top hat. A lavender bow tie and a floral-patterned vest peek out from beneath the coat, adding to the whimsical appearance. His attire is reminiscent of a Victorian-era dandy, but with a fantastical twist.

The character''s face is the focal point of the image. He has a sly, knowing smile that borders on a smirk. His blue eyes are bright and appear to be twinkling with amusement or secret knowledge. Curly blond hair peeks out from under his hat, framing his face.

The character''s pose is casual yet deliberate. He''s leaning his head on one hand, with his elbow presumably resting on something out of frame. This posture gives him an air of relaxed confidence and adds to the sense that he''s privy to some inside joke or secret.

The background of the image is blurry but appears to be a colorful set, likely from the film. Hints of yellow and other bright colors can be seen, reinforcing the magical and fantastical setting of the story.

