	 ('6abee3af-cc9a-4b87-ad22-e34bd3017cc3'::uuid,'Inhaling-Seagull','This meme template features a series of four vertically stacked images showcasing a seagull''s dramatic transformation from calm to chaotic.

In the first panel, we see a serene white seagull perched on what appears to be a green-tiled roof or ledge. The bird looks composed, its yellow beak closed, and its eye calmly observing its surroundings. The background shows some wooden structures, suggesting an urban or seaside setting.

The second image captures the same seagull, but now its beak is slightly open, hinting at the beginning of some vocalization or reaction. The bird''s posture is more alert, with its head tilted slightly upward.

In the third panel, the seagull''s transformation becomes more pronounced. Its beak is wide open in what appears to be a loud squawk or scream. The bird''s head is tilted back dramatically, creating a comical and exaggerated expression of surprise, anger, or excitement.

The final image takes the meme to its climactic point. The entire panel is washed in a bright, alarming red filter. Within this red chaos, we can barely make out the blurred, ghostly silhouette of the seagull, now appearing to be in full meltdown mode. The bird''s form is distorted and elongated, suggesting rapid movement or perhaps a metaphorical representation of its internal state.

This progression from calm to calamity makes the template perfect for illustrating situations that quickly escalate or spiral out of control. The stark contrast between the composed seagull at the start and the chaotic red scene at the end provides a versatile format for depicting overreactions, sudden realizations, or the rapid deterioration of any given situation in a humorous and exaggerated manner.','/memes/Inhaling-Seagull.jpg',4,'{}','{"inhaling bird"}',0.0,'[-0.005788497,0.00076539064,0.026006795,0.0011373505,0.01483897,-0.0814508,-0.036608964,0.018791482,0.01555615,0.03487007,-0.0075705606,0.004125926,0.02934329,0.0040013436,0.0033350445,-0.0030723386,-0.0039641424,-0.03450456,-0.029188778,0.005399996,-0.013239184,-0.03253886,-0.06541795,-0.07136491,0.0069060926,0.047711037,0.01594093,-0.0018128448,0.0647121,0.025691105,0.012473463,-0.019578196,-0.019654911,-0.04816063,-0.00493199,-0.002483819,0.00526833,-0.0612584,-0.015438129,-0.028238513,0.038379848,-0.029893314,0.019849382,-0.021066874,-0.007979188,-0.0423945,-0.0030814472,-0.00029215732,0.0033269394,-0.002319591,0.0041398434,-0.027690502,0.037043676,-0.033021472,-0.039555065,-0.033005383,-0.022202535,-0.021221492,0.004562199,0.022445561,0.029795626,0.02883681,0.030810904,-0.04659233,-0.027965989,0.017271612,-0.03207968,-0.0040320344,-0.049394358,-0.030957477,-0.05482061,0.021732574,0.02016179,-0.00058905454,-0.08676628,-0.0091394875,-0.013100696,-0.00942137,0.005101409,0.01367163,0.028438637,0.059410624,-0.055381883,-0.0155266225,-0.049007222,-0.013729186,-0.008112661,0.034890264,0.040701985,-0.027230648,-0.023131456,0.06998744,-0.009508449,0.025845172,0.007897924,0.05030258,-0.002283145,0.031673484,-0.0075295633,0.031106494,0.0073001944,0.042230807,0.0061346553,0.044109393,-0.06823097,-0.0030443654,0.0359025,-0.0080556795,-0.016469741,-0.07141377,-0.01085607,0.0020481197,0.022954788,-0.008208524,0.023214731,0.02115037,0.0032448592,0.06956438,-0.07099685,0.0028572876,-0.041476212,-0.008202189,-0.0583429