	 ('9a2de4f0-4633-4d8c-8048-fdb96911aa66'::uuid,'Conspiracy-Keanu','This meme template features a close-up shot of a young man with a distinctive, somewhat bewildered expression. He has shaggy, dark hair that falls around his face in a messy, unkempt style typical of the 1990s or early 2000s. His eyebrows are slightly raised, and his mouth is slightly open, giving him a look of confusion, surprise, or disbelief.

The man is wearing a formal outfit, visible as a white collared shirt and a dark jacket or suit, which contrasts with his casual hairstyle. This juxtaposition adds to the comedic potential of the image.

The background is blurry but appears to be outdoors, with muted green and brown tones suggesting a natural setting. The lighting on the man''s face is even, highlighting his features and expression clearly.

The image quality and style suggest it''s a screenshot or still from a movie or TV show, likely from the late 20th or early 21st century. The slightly grainy texture and color palette are characteristic of film from that era.

This particular expression and pose have become iconic in meme culture, often used to convey confusion, skepticism, or a moment of realization. The subject''s wide-eyed, slightly open-mouthed look is perfect for expressing reactions to surprising or perplexing information or situations.

