	 ('702a8d8c-b37f-4252-896e-dcbf28f2c349'::uuid,'Blank-Nut-Button','This meme template features a close-up view of two key elements: a large, bright blue button and a human hand. The composition is dynamic, with the hand appearing to move swiftly towards the button from the right side of the frame.

The button is the focal point of the image. It''s a vibrant, royal blue color that stands out starkly against the darker background. The button appears to be part of some kind of control panel or device, though only the button itself is clearly visible. Its surface is smooth and slightly domed, giving it a tactile quality that seems to invite pressing.

The hand entering the frame from the right is captured in motion, creating a sense of urgency or impulsiveness. The fingers are splayed out, palm facing the button, in a pose that suggests the person is about to slap or slam their hand down onto the button. Only part of the hand is visible, adding to the feeling of swift movement.

The background of the image is intentionally blurry and dark, which serves to heighten the focus on the button and the approaching hand. This blurriness also adds to the sense of motion in the image.

The overall quality of the image is somewhat grainy or pixelated, which is characteristic of many meme templates. This low-fidelity aesthetic contributes to its memetic quality, making it easily recognizable and replicable.

The composition of the image creates tension and anticipation. Viewers are left wondering what will happen when the hand makes contact with the button, which makes this template versatile for a variety of humorous or relatable scenarios where someone is about to make a decisive, potentially regrettable action.

This meme template is often used to represent impulsive decisions, temptations that are hard to resist, or moments of weakness where one gives in to an urge despite potential consequences. Its simplicity and clear visual narrative make it a popular choice for creating relatable content across various topics and situations.','/memes/Blank-Nut-Button.jpg',2,'{}','{"blank blue button","smash button","press button","button slam","button meme","panic button",botton,"nut button (crystalbot)"}',0.0,'[0.003939533,-0.01513046,0.013670737,0.03444792,0.008927159,-0.049532514,-0.033573315,0.01126335,-0.0024567212,0.058582224,-0.019599413,-0.006792429,0.016908677,0.010273369,0.012289719,0.0042291284,0.005010508,-0.0003290465,-0.0097684,0.025450712,0.009546809,-0.019209877,-0.08519522,-0.06646559,-0.026435161,0.046896722,-0.006075372,0.010793598,0.043221325,0.02256145,0.014688363,0.007353527,0.03011333,-0.037866823,-0.006289732,0.005817937,0.026218561,-0.04918147,-0.024317207,-0.035580806,0.043599077,-0.036020987,0.043711875,-0.018240765,-0.032106217,-0.02954113,-0.021315297,0.0075247474,-0.0021234145,-0.015665311,0.017911347,0.007402722,0.004391283,0.0085780285,-0.030541692,0.00019990605,-0.034605373,-0.039014764,0.0066644195,0.017543485,0.013142942,-0.030171908,-3.7077355e-06,-0.063482665,-0.009962938,0.011675107,-0.0065289526,-0.010991665,-0.058052823,-0.051876407,-0.0050868774,0.015431484,0.0033444394,-0.029369468,-0.03396278,0.011450247,-0.03864183,-0.011378425,0.011438307,-0.001118366,0.013484871,0.029381381,-0.014390761,-0.01988697,-0.04705487,0.028137285,0.009832854,0.015939163,0.0011902277,-0.051738188,0.00066664885,0.052674852,-0.013375174,0.017937336,0.017117435,0.0124150785,0.018684871,0.03755711,0.016384862,-0.0016148762,0.0011644914,0.020660968,-0.040066406,0.023169272,-0.014526499,0.011412294,0.046574682,0.009011944,-0.04278234,-0.05917959,-0.006481253,-0.012973873,0.0015124747,-0.00943917,-0.02290759,0.045739017,-0.0071720416,0.053612962,-0.033372108,0.00013208298