	 ('56e66b10-3b76-4562-8545-dcf754ccddd9'::uuid,'Black-Girl-Wat','This meme template features a close-up shot of a young woman with a distinctive expression of confusion, frustration, or disbelief. The subject is African American, with her dark hair pulled up into a high ponytail or bun secured by a thin headband. She''s wearing a dark blue, possibly knitted sweater.

The woman''s facial expression is the focal point of the image. Her brow is slightly furrowed, eyes widened, and mouth slightly open in a look that conveys a mix of bewilderment and exasperation. This expression is often used to represent reactions to absurd or incomprehensible situations.

Adding to the expressiveness of the image, the woman''s hand is raised in front of her, palm up, fingers spread in a gesture that seems to say "What?" or "Why?" This hand gesture reinforces the overall sentiment of confusion or disbelief.

The background of the image appears to be an indoor setting, possibly a classroom or cafeteria. There are indistinct figures visible in red clothing in the background, suggesting other people are present in the space.

The image quality is somewhat grainy or low-resolution, which is common for memes that have been widely shared and reposted. This low-fi quality adds to its authenticity as a candid, relatable moment captured in time.

