	 ('2d3bed31-3473-4101-b74f-5031234b2e2c'::uuid,'Scumbag-Steve','This meme template features a young man standing in a doorway, captured in what appears to be a candid, low-light photograph. The image has a slightly grainy quality, suggesting it may have been taken with an older camera or in poor lighting conditions.

The subject is wearing an eclectic combination of clothing that immediately draws attention. On his head is a distinctive brown patterned cap, reminiscent of a designer brand''s signature print. The cap is tilted slightly to one side, giving him a casual, perhaps trying-to-be-cool appearance.

He''s sporting a mustard-yellow or ochre colored t-shirt, which is partially covered by an unusual vest or sleeveless jacket. This outer layer appears to be made of dark fabric with a prominent fur or faux-fur collar, creating a stark contrast against his shirt and adding to the overall quirky ensemble.

The young man''s expression is neutral to slightly bewildered, with his mouth slightly open and eyes looking directly at the camera. His face appears somewhat flushed, possibly due to the lighting or other factors.

The background of the image shows part of a white door frame and a glimpse into a darker room behind him. This composition gives the impression that he might have just emerged from or is about to enter the room.

The overall effect of the image is one of awkwardness and perhaps misplaced confidence. It captures a moment that feels both candid and slightly absurd, making it ripe for meme usage where the subject''s appearance or expression can be juxtaposed with various humorous captions or scenarios.

