	 ('3e5d1db9-f2e1-436b-b8a3-3a1e4a27f097'::uuid,'Face-You-Make-Robert-Downey-Jr','This meme template features a close-up shot of a middle-aged man with a distinctive appearance. He has short, dark hair styled in a slightly messy fashion and sports a well-groomed goatee. The man''s expression is one of skepticism or mild disbelief, with his eyebrows slightly raised and his mouth slightly open, as if he''s about to retort or express doubt.

He''s wearing a dark suit jacket over a black shirt with white polka dots, giving him a sleek, professional appearance. His arms are crossed over his chest, reinforcing the impression of skepticism or defensiveness. On his wrist, a watch is partially visible, adding to the polished look.

The background is blurred and warm-toned, suggesting an indoor setting, possibly in an office or upscale venue. The lighting creates a soft, almost sepia-like quality to the image, enhancing the dramatic effect of the man''s expression and pose.

This image is often used in memes to convey skepticism, doubt, or a "really?" reaction to statements or situations. The man''s facial expression and body language make it versatile for expressing disbelief or questioning the validity of something presented.

The composition of the image, focusing tightly on the man''s face and upper body, emphasizes his expression and body language, making it highly effective as a reaction image in various meme contexts. The professional attire and setting also lend themselves to memes about work, success, or dealing with absurd situations in a composed manner.','/memes/Face-You-Make-Robert-Downey-Jr.jpg',1,'{}','{"tony stark","rdj rolling eyes","iron man eye roll","annoyed stark","robert roll eyes","ugh... lisa episode...","that face you make"}',0.0,'[0.046528056,-0.031109449,0.026995637,0.0033400636,0.015034211,-0.033315614,-0.017631589,-0.011311319,0.0053399713,0.06168672,0.019226529,-0.043219607,0.043422002,-0.00978767,-0.020716505,0.024556484,0.014426252,-0.020893114,0.002411587,0.0040028226,0.045778185,-0.016061163,-0.06672528,-0.05559212,-0.015588206,0.039690975,-0.008648299,-0.00576589,0.051676307,0.006865089,0.014912559,0.014651168,-0.0030769757,-0.068690464,-0.016297204,-0.02473443,0.04125476,-0.06052985,-0.031577148,-0.011469226,0.0194172,-0.011450628,0.0224523,-0.023902373,-0.041133333,-0.0419191,-0.041152623,-0.025490852,0.018560704,-0.0027503013,0.028263299,-0.012445322,0.012137571,0.026788086,-0.014448374,-0.032826625,-0.007946684,0.009667934,0.0055267094,0.023564378,0.05020057,0.028859362,0.011233842,-0.03719428,-0.041237816,0.04166989,-0.019764647,-0.000990652,-0.030682232,-0.033314623,0.016240336,-0.0027972239,0.02800456,0.018388323,-0.044420324,0.009132378,-0.03628092,-0.027062474,0.031418297,0.0056857816,0.02050842,0.015411113,-0.011116556,-0.016064253,-0.010502656,-0.008005448,0.024147738,0.050008595,0.0057817167,-0.015339737,0.02074171,0.06833696,0.00082201895,0.00044176928,0.009325142,0.034371104,-0.0048900205,0.036285676,0.008384931,0.052482482,-0.03558483,0.051180307,-0.02239044,0.024707943,-0.021011991,0.021725725,0.024261946,-0.0060282648,-0.0521686,-0.028798658,0.039766658,-0.044170488,-0.018337248,-0.0020901898,-0.05188056,0.02398044,0.018125052,0.03034508,-