	 ('9918881b-8f28-4f08-9a99-8eefadeeaac4'::uuid,'Unsettled-Tom','This meme template features a striking close-up of two cartoon characters'' faces, positioned side-by-side in an intense, confrontational manner. The image is cropped tightly to focus on their eyes and partial facial features, creating a dramatic and slightly unsettling effect.

On the left side of the image is a grey face with large, piercing yellow eyes that dominate the frame. These eyes have a distinct rectangular shape with rounded corners, giving them an alien or robotic appearance. The yellow is bright and contrasts sharply with the surrounding grey skin. Within each yellow eye is a smaller, oval-shaped green pupil, adding to the character''s otherworldly look. Thick black eyebrows arch over these eyes, emphasizing their intense expression.

On the right side, we see a portion of a white face, presumably belonging to another character. This face has a single visible eye that is small and black, creating a stark contrast with the large yellow eyes next to it. Below this eye, we can see a hint of a red mark or possibly a mouth, adding a touch of color to the white face.

The composition is intentionally asymmetrical and off-balance, with the grey face taking up more of the frame than the white face. This creates tension and draws the viewer''s attention to the contrast between the two characters. The background is mostly grey, further emphasizing the vibrant colors of the eyes.

This meme template seems designed to convey a sense of shock, surprise, or confrontation between two very different entities. The exaggerated features and close-up perspective make it ideal for expressing extreme reactions or unexpected encounters in a humorous or dramatic context.','/memes/Unsettled-Tom.jpg',2,'{}','{"tom face","concerned tom","tom and jerry","disgusted tom","surprised tom","tom staring down",unsettled/shocking}',0.0,'[0.027007097,-0.0044942573,-0.00037699912,0.0143828485,-0.008226133,-0.047450587,-0.02771959,-0.015473372,-0.0320022,0.058059607,0.000838685,-0.0006927809,0.031211099,0.011118436,0.017682435,0.0015487649,-0.009752917,-0.01716511,-0.017139694,0.017631715,-0.012938015,0.01440631,-0.06617078,-0.020869816,-0.011956688,0.057661925,0.0010002156,-0.012388795,0.044710007,0.029515574,0.0031815122,0.015091797,-0.0056800894,-0.03787794,0.013583932,-0.0021582546,0.04266636,-0.042407483,0.012323445,-0.018622054,0.050093226,-0.00910961,0.02758907,-0.04179695,-0.03582471,-0.019568752,0.002341301,0.0020744991,0.0027038956,-0.002241341,0.023711419,-0.025496723,0.017177736,0.039099883,-0.032883476,-0.022967413,-0.007248327,-0.032895353,0.0071870396,0.017413856,0.026506737,0.030366369,0.025999928,-0.054990157,-0.045759745,0.007490689,-0.029921286,-0.01878226,-0.021142436,0.0016252011,0.020964393,0.0077157896,0.00049946347,-0.010019191,-0.038966745,-0.021925064,-0.022099303,-0.033694077,0.054124944,0.0059359986,0.03640794,0.038846094,-0.018374614,-0.044697657,-0.009603952,0.0005969,0.02401487,0.016150761,0.009502459,-0.02304142,-0.019561747,0.056621023,-0.014208629,0.029698748,0.040095128,0.033971068,-0.01740488,0.031481422,-0.009812104,0.012153133,-0.008005213,0.061748307,-0.015156359,0.059845835,-0.038047213,0.010052131,0.0333975,0.0063587325,-0.0201875,-0.026530089,0.020942476,-0.020605104,0.0007001637,-0.0049224347,-0.041651644,0.030028941,-0.019370995,0.06129497,-0.06554022,-0.017081723,-0.047914427,-0.0022776427,-0.045780096,0.018334059,-0.00010380