	 ('e95a9787-d0ab-484a-9add-a280325fdb65'::uuid,'Sparta-Leonidas','This iconic meme template is taken from the 2006 film "300," depicting a dramatic battlefield scene. The image centers on a muscular, bare-chested warrior in the foreground, wearing a red cape and wielding a sword. His face is contorted in an intense battle cry, mouth wide open, eyes narrowed, and veins bulging on his neck. The warrior sports a thick, dark beard and short-cropped hair, embodying a fierce, ancient Spartan aesthetic.

Behind him stretches a vast battlefield, hazy with dust or mist. The background is filled with indistinct figures, suggesting a large army or the chaos of combat. The overall color palette is muted, dominated by earthy tones of brown, red, and gold, which adds to the gritty, historical atmosphere of the scene.

This image is often used in memes to represent moments of extreme determination, defiance, or rallying cries. The warrior''s passionate expression and commanding presence make it a powerful template for conveying intense emotions or calls to action in a variety of contexts, from serious to humorous.

The cinematic quality of the shot, with its dramatic lighting and composition, elevates the impact of the image. The contrast between the sharply focused warrior in the foreground and the blurred, chaotic background further emphasizes the central figure''s importance and the weight of the moment being captured.

This meme template has become deeply ingrained in internet culture, often associated with expressions of bravado, over-the-top enthusiasm, or satirical takes on confrontational situations. Its popularity stems from the raw emotion and larger-than-life heroic imagery it presents, making it versatile for a wide range of meme applications.','/memes/Sparta-Leonidas.jpg',2,'{}','{"Leonidas from the movie 300","tonight we dine"}',0.0,'[0.004355121,-0.039622042,0.026962647,0.026558353,0.001943784,-0.04557385,-0.039494324,-0.022725198,-0.011196727,0.037896182,0.01457674,-0.0026295132,0.007693322,0.0042680292,0.022401232,0.01427722,-0.02749964,-0.055401832,-0.072643876,0.003223,-0.008013348,-0.02278566,-0.067268066,-0.027829876,0.010367872,0.057115808,-0.010937703,0.023264522,0.055681862,0.025625132,0.009998719,0.009692086,0.0027672504,-0.057455856,8.538344e-05,-0.01768411,-0.0010664276,-0.08390984,-0.05162517,-0.019786632,0.049303524,-0.040625624,0.014334997,-0.016369307,-0.022308914,0.0007616127,-0.014990775,-0.023912882,0.011525502,-0.02009638,-0.0016902572,-0.01890342,0.0030213636,0.016519029,-0.03263868,-0.014319267,-0.0035616565,-0.013041722,0.018044392,0.032288227,0.04792605,0.012426392,-0.013829762,-0.031877816,-0.013480949,-0.014274576,0.023886682,0.011409286,-0.010909332,0.0014341032,-0.015782472,-0.009420093,0.0093407035,-0.010284006,-0.03811567,-0.011577001,-0.040502813,-0.031979565,0.019894088,-0.0040862416,0.033898916,0.047581352,-0.022095421,-0.004841074,-0.017411988,0.004419746,0.0099208215,0.040013585,0.0066229342,-0.024405954,0.01983903,0.045122653,0.012144649,0.017269855,-0.008547359,0.031330265,-0.0044892034,0.043528896,-0.024958985,0.0105043175,-0.0055531594,0.06284289,-0.026954858,0.033611033,-0.04688925,0.017226793,0.016635371,-0.028856296,-0.014170476,-0.05370485,0.023305217,-0.035164937,-0.0027295768,0.007214449,0.0013379335,0.019857207,-0.03333738,0.035932556,-0.039868753,0.010233329,-0.020715443,0.018219508,-0.005712702,-0.0038098297,-0.023307988,-