	 ('98bdb319-ef50-4b24-9693-31c654540551'::uuid,'The-Most-Interesting-Man-In-The-World','This meme template features a sophisticated-looking older gentleman seated in what appears to be an upscale setting. He has silver-gray hair and a well-groomed beard, giving him a distinguished appearance. The man is wearing a dark pinstriped suit jacket over a light-colored shirt, exuding an air of casual elegance.

The subject is positioned in a relaxed, confident pose, leaning slightly forward with one arm resting on what seems to be a table or bar. His expression is one of subtle amusement or interest, with a hint of a smile and engaged eyes that suggest he''s about to share some wisdom or a witty observation.

In front of him on the table is a green bottle of Dos Equis beer, a detail that has become iconic in this meme template. The background suggests a luxurious environment, with warm, rich tones and what appears to be ornate wallpaper or decor, though it''s slightly out of focus.

The lighting in the image is warm and flattering, highlighting the man''s features and creating a sense of intimacy, as if the viewer is engaged in a personal conversation with him. The overall composition of the image is balanced, drawing the eye to the man''s face and then to the beer bottle, creating a visual connection between the two elements.

This template has become widely recognized in internet culture, often used to express interesting man qualities or to make humorous statements about sophistication, worldliness, or exceptional abilities. The juxtaposition of the refined gentleman with the casual beer bottle adds to the template''s versatility and appeal in meme creation.','/memes/The-Most-Interesting-Man-In-The-World.jpg',2,'{}','{"I dont always... but when I do","Dos Equis Man","I don''t always","dos xx","don''t usually guy","i don’t always"}',0.0,'[0.016332302,-0.026061624,0.062292688,0.028753411,-0.0014847382,-0.03249637,-0.015603272,0.01714524,-0.020148033,0.029003246,0.023232993,-0.016420938,0.02129388,0.010060936,0.02517548,0.01248593,0.011148543,-0.014560372,-0.039517064,0.022498373,0.03110651,-0.004640018,-0.0746442,-0.032054804,-0.0064872047,0.05764104,-0.026798317,0.036586497,0.07286395,0.009332034,0.023415476,0.028859198,-0.011451454,-0.046573084,-0.019004885,-0.0013476665,0.010808007,-0.04737228,-0.012016596,-0.0050479714,0.04587303,-0.004851172,0.02826487,-0.003108698,-0.027853817,-0.008281233,-0.022875281,-0.036191475,0.0077829873,-0.013831161,0.029739771,-0.04468331,0.037005115,0.016898295,-0.0108117405,-0.029817244,-0.044195693,0.003793002,0.01968748,0.017479235,0.02638927,0.014564238,-0.012986064,-0.020969495,0.0042456635,0.010227815,-0.008482185,-0.006288667,-0.02896411,-0.02578811,-0.00321381,-0.010713007,-0.003513911,0.02274459,-0.050922386,0.0068865577,-0.019948926,-0.0026238721,0.0285713,0.00010718336,0.022861786,0.040625814,0.020283906,-0.0019275123,-0.03845216,-0.0054591084,0.054622073,0.07909027,0.03889735,-0.022320267,0.0036048684,0.051602293,-0.0030383768,-0.016644986,-0.0024874182,0.034214966,-0.0030654229,0.058271702,-0.000980901,0.02184183,-0.037454322,0.04104901,-0.02688768,0.030322699,-0.024823656,0.013618766,0.039355744,-0.00024176746,-0.04514057,-0.032623608,0.02039525,-0.025151407,-0.008578036,0.012297325,-0.044322792,0.021551944,-0.017712142,0.01266138,-0.04446433