	 ('2213b6b6-d2ac-4624-b61d-d5f4e5775a26'::uuid,'Archer','This meme template features a stylized cartoon portrait of a man, drawn in the distinctive art style of the animated television series "Archer." The character is depicted from the chest up, facing directly at the viewer with a serious, slightly stern expression.

The man has a chiseled, square-jawed face with sharp, angular features that epitomize a classically handsome, masculine appearance. His eyes are a striking bright blue, set beneath thick, dark eyebrows that are slightly furrowed. His black hair is neatly combed in a short, conservative style typical of the 1960s era.

He''s wearing a crisp white dress shirt with a dark tie and a gray suit jacket, suggesting a professional or corporate setting. This attire, combined with his stern demeanor, gives the impression of a no-nonsense businessman or secret agent character.

The background of the image shows an office interior, with fluorescent lighting visible on the ceiling. To the right, there''s a partial view of what appears to be a mid-century modern orange chair or couch, further emphasizing the retro aesthetic of the scene.

The art style is characterized by bold lines, flat colors, and a lack of complex shading, which is typical of the show''s visual approach. This style allows for clear, expressive character depictions that work well in both animated contexts and as static meme images.

This particular image is often used in memes to convey a sense of skepticism, judgment, or deadpan reaction to various situations, playing off the character''s stern and somewhat intimidating demeanor. The character''s intense gaze and serious expression make it versatile for a wide range of humorous contexts, especially those involving dry wit or sarcasm.','/memes/Archer.jpg',2,'{}','{"Do you want X? Because that''s how you get X. Do you want ants? Because that''s how you get ants.","sterling archer","do you want ants archer","archer ants"}',0.0,'[0.060311392,-0.0062295436,0.019476268,-0.006083903,0.013873142,-0.023679277,-0.015524945,0.004353404,-0.0036631874,0.027470686,0.00770098,-0.019520178,0.043414146,-0.004785925,-0.0077839987,0.009532231,-0.0045307814,0.0013662215,-0.006816478,0.043440633,0.0030643463,-0.0026686797,-0.059210636,-0.03470909,0.006198336,0.056455612,-0.012003573,0.032168657,0.027484708,0.019371234,0.02300927,0.01709077,-0.046318643,-0.05786205,-0.011160144,0.0069742124,0.040172562,-0.064220965,-0.0068639438,-0.024212375,0.012370932,-0.020886587,0.009455303,-0.005891525,-0.014217877,-0.05590876,-0.008222153,-0.011331082,0.0003290292,0.004239021,0.025511255,0.0034625414,0.039509337,0.018113362,-0.000990814,-0.06887696,0.018509513,0.012812811,0.013102907,0.02194114,0.033059973,-0.017319666,-0.016158504,-0.019260375,-0.025154874,0.01940466,-0.0150110945,0.006734271,-0.020610511,0.023622923,0.006970518,0.018910369,0.0147359,0.02206057,-0.05024369,-0.003657937,-0.016130764,-0.001471434,0.026478091,0.0033696808,0.02660435,0.03232603,-0.01904313,-0.034598466,-0.020253394,-0.0034144025,0.021451864,0.04125836,0.010154637,-0.043845512,-0.0060371878,0.06775544,-0.0036131162,0.000104634535,-0.0018045038,0.046502754,-0.0017982131,0.031089317,0.024328593,0.0030417158,-0.030307163,0.040827706,-0.021456894,0.009087643,-0.026296042,0.01514349,0.024889167,-0.0009154939,-0.024582697,-0.012070005,0.024974095,-0.019709991,-0.010911313,-0.0027767883,-0.06545288,0.01