	 ('d78f1eb1-87a5-4c22-8048-0f491b0d8a41'::uuid,'Matrix-Morpheus','This meme template features a close-up shot of a character from the iconic sci-fi film "The Matrix." The image showcases a bald African American man wearing reflective, oval-shaped sunglasses that dominate his face. The sunglasses are so reflective that you can see small figures or shapes reflected in them, hinting at an intense or significant moment in the film.

The man''s expression is serious and somewhat skeptical, with his mouth slightly open as if he''s about to speak or is processing information. His skin has a slight sheen to it, which along with the lighting gives the image a cool, greenish tint characteristic of the film''s visual style.

The character is wearing what appears to be a high-collared dark jacket or coat, further emphasizing the futuristic, dystopian aesthetic of the movie. The background is blurred but seems to be a dimly lit interior space, maintaining the film''s gritty, underground atmosphere.

This particular image is often used in memes to convey a moment of realization, skepticism, or when someone is about to deliver a hard truth or profound statement. The character''s authoritative and knowing look, combined with the reflective glasses hiding his eyes, makes it a perfect template for scenarios where someone is "seeing through" a situation or about to reveal something significant.

The image encapsulates the blend of cool detachment and intense focus that made "The Matrix" a cultural phenomenon, and its use as a meme template often plays on themes of reality versus illusion, knowledge versus ignorance, or simply reacting to surprising information.','/memes/Matrix-Morpheus.jpg',2,'{}','{"what if I told you",morpheous}',0.0,'[0.044758897,-0.026720949,0.02204268,0.026870294,0.005851771,-0.0321147,-0.029945942,-0.038164828,-0.043080192,0.052194875,0.0066510695,-0.005383048,0.031153386,0.01688198,-0.006595719,-0.0041311122,0.03109655,-0.012948441,-0.010367326,-0.007872108,-0.012304672,0.017141797,-0.08156453,-0.057829734,-0.021831207,0.039750766,-0.038047325,0.016126584,0.03628613,0.054003876,0.0187647,0.00895146,0.027205907,-0.03319338,0.005558932,-0.018316813,0.03308046,-0.033376496,-0.017018551,-0.01855411,0.02103658,-0.024068667,0.009276378,0.0036406445,-0.05675979,-0.027144978,-0.020129347,0.025867078,0.027697189,-0.015663637,0.002996584,0.005435331,0.03297593,0.02136098,-0.040201213,-0.032307796,-0.01873369,0.028690355,0.0046836636,-0.0010085986,0.025277294,0.0008273318,-0.005967332,-0.0053986744,-0.01866957,0.023590615,-0.02596533,0.005366488,-0.0113246385,-0.0089746965,-0.0009771102,-0.015183702,0.028161248,0.00665618,-0.024146365,-0.001202926,-0.031863153,-0.040282935,0.02627266,0.00020515284,0.009156554,0.041696835,-0.010904522,-0.030415105,-0.0011348838,4.510679e-07,-0.0028877798,0.057166997,0.011728644,-0.05794702,0.018815799,0.047461588,0.0094022,0.022710107,0.035399638,0.029744353,0.005991173,0.05728472,0.010280865,0.017053654,-0.039658688,0.084918804,-0.03357777,0.042925816,0.024909548,0.01361358,0.010621925,0.00023810958,-0.033798095,-0.030733762,0.03214645,-0.046370387,0.013021258,0.010753285,-0.044853024,0.040620416,0.013060976,0.061450943,-0.017497206,-0.022000039,-0.051228106,-0.03751813,-0.025763003,-0.02001475,0.0139160585,-0.02945594,0.02467471,0.014543039,-0.040329654,0.012406634,0.043454204,-0.023605257,0.030755501,0.029464