	 ('a9e6f1b3-57d8-4efa-91e2-c49f1a254d05'::uuid,'Aaaaand-Its-Gone','This meme template features a cartoon-style image from the animated TV show South Park. The scene depicts a character sitting at a desk in what appears to be an office setting. The character is a middle-aged man with a round face, dark hair in a simple style, and wide, somewhat blank eyes. He''s wearing a dark suit with a blue tie, typical office attire.

The man is positioned behind a large wooden desk, facing forward with his hands resting on a keyboard in front of a computer monitor. The desk is neat and organized, with a few office supplies visible, including a yellow desk lamp to the left.

Behind the character, we can see a large window that takes up most of the back wall. Through the window, there''s a view of a bright blue sky with a few small clouds and some green hills or mountains in the distance, suggesting a pleasant outdoor scene contrasting with the indoor office environment.

The room itself has a warm, tan-colored wall and what looks like green panels or lights along the ceiling, giving it a somewhat retro or dated office feel typical of South Park''s visual style.

The character''s expression is notably neutral or slightly confused, with raised eyebrows and a small, straight mouth. This blank or mildly perplexed look is often used in memes to convey confusion, discomfort, or a deadpan reaction to various situations.

The overall composition centers the character in the frame, making him the clear focal point of the image. The simple, flat animation style characteristic of South Park lends itself well to meme usage, as it''s easily recognizable and can be applied to a wide range of humorous contexts.

