In the first panel, we see a close-up of a muscular man with a stern expression. He has short dark hair and appears to be wearing a dark jacket. He''s looking slightly off-camera, as if speaking to someone. There''s a speech bubble next to him, left blank for meme creators to fill in.

The second panel shows a young woman with long blonde hair sitting in what looks like the passenger seat of a car. She has a concerned or worried expression on her face, looking back at the man. Again, there''s an empty speech bubble next to her for customizable text.

The third panel returns to the man, now shown from a different angle inside the car. He''s turned around in his seat, looking back with an expression of shock, disbelief, or confusion. His eyes are wide and his mouth is slightly open. The interior of the car is visible, including the rearview mirror and part of the windshield.

This template is set up for a classic joke format where the first two panels set up a conversation, and the third panel delivers a punchline or unexpected twist, as reflected in the man''s dramatic reaction. The blank speech bubbles allow meme creators to adapt this template to various humorous scenarios, often playing on the contrast between the calm setup and the exaggerated final reaction.','/memes/The-Rock-Driving.jpg',3,'{}','{"race to witch mountain blank"}',0.0,'[0.03518753,-0.013780588,0.014312153,0.014349211,0.01453063,-0.066586584,-0.03193661,-0.018353432,-0.0316476,0.033505183,0.036817946,-0.0016279859,0.025098471,-0.019264719,-0.021213457,0.0018249232,0.008464429,-0.01717851,-0.02631111,0.0029709393,-0.02703166,-0.01710862,-0.07452977,-0.0159799,-0.030337714,0.04825871,0.0055877664,0.030761126,0.045596927,0.017970996,0.01209701,-0.016330456,0.015615549,-0.04356141,0.01874253,-0.01483746,0.018586062,-0.02211458,-0.03664791,0.0059766467,0.015144429,0.00044820964,0.021332832,-0.005961853,-0.031736653,-0.036748428,-0.0073048584,0.0056850347,-0.01042864,-0.009659166,0.018224848,-0.04059746,0.02468996,-0.0005335244,-0.019118816,-0.037156533,-0.024943085,0.005235153,-0.011700088,0.020121492,0.0141563,0.011112459,-0.012226775,-0.01930191,-0.021256048,0.0140140625,-0.025111286,0.007185627,-0.027505022,-0.0012759902,-0.0053553777,0.025438052,-0.009407985,0.0028685208,-0.06371004,-0.006583419,-0.02043119,0.0035943377,0.030182244,0.012117392,0.041657794,0.06038503,0.026605902,-0.031056074,-0.018003376,-0.042218022,0.0076838783,0.018027447,-0.01891562,-0.045039788,-0.019466603,0.043955546,-0.012878751,0.0049459483,0.05047807,0.037648946,-0.031921864,0.01323919,0.003388747,-0.012299492,-0.020406252,0.057472803,-0.028112084,0.038411714,-0.034899972,0.004247097,0.050310444,0.0033377788,-0.04247053,-0.024598617,-0.025142187,-0.01598462,0.02358713,-0.025938967,-0.023070745,0.048339393,0.01522891,0.038239297,-0.039265364,0.005598607,-0.035462487,-0.02403015,-0.046498645,0.