	 ('f2f90063-d059-4076-bf8a-db2dd545214a'::uuid,'Dont-You-Squidward','This meme template features a close-up shot of SpongeBob SquarePants, the iconic yellow sea sponge character from the eponymous animated series. In this image, SpongeBob is portrayed with a sly, knowing expression that has become famous in meme culture.

SpongeBob''s face dominates the frame, showcasing his bright yellow color and characteristic porous texture. His eyes are half-lidded, giving him a smug, self-satisfied look. His buck teeth are prominently displayed in a wide, mischievous grin that stretches across his face. This particular expression is often used to convey a sense of devious pleasure, sarcasm, or an "I told you so" attitude in meme contexts.

The character is wearing his typical attire: a white collared shirt, red tie, and brown square pants, though only the upper portion is visible due to the close-up nature of the shot. On top of his head sits his signature white sailor hat.

The background of the image shows the interior of what appears to be the Krusty Krab, SpongeBob''s workplace in the show. A blue porthole or circular window is visible behind him, along with the green-tinted wall. On a shelf to the right, two bottles (likely condiment containers) can be seen, adding to the fast-food restaurant setting.

This particular image has become a widely recognized meme template, often used to express smugness, sarcasm, or a knowing reaction to various situations. The exaggerated facial expression of SpongeBob in this frame makes it versatile for a wide range of humorous or ironic captions in internet culture.','/memes/Dont-You-Squidward.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob grinning","spongebob smirk face","smug spongebob"}',0.0,'[0.048643768,-0.033184923,-0.0010780456,-0.0006822264,0.012844116,-0.022766935,-0.0029313813,-0.03602953,0.0035362418,0.030734085,0.020621518,-0.020847756,0.041314594,0.013853286,0.0078061153,-0.0448177,-0.021111224,-0.017486632,-0.051312864,0.019985143,-0.0038471844,0.0023064902,-0.033059664,-0.007354782,-0.005605923,0.05426144,0.011457151,0.013852371,0.04245737,-0.0040668966,-0.0050973105,0.021522895,-0.007400685,-0.032610532,0.013625936,0.010532659,0.025472086,-0.041613556,0.017364414,-0.046068702,0.038406495,-0.016118156,0.0077940817,-0.02234824,-0.010881716,-0.021255743,-0.01026054,-0.005493354,0.04059033,-0.014274045,0.019100664,0.01847655,0.011039738,0.023352452,-0.010959889,-0.044689577,0.004625875,-0.0069533824,0.024930762,0.02388456,0.028645994,0.00068367145,-0.026335908,-0.06237671,-0.029534668,-0.011684908,0.0091686705,-0.030735191,-0.006532219,0.008498788,0.009614661,0.0095182955,0.020096311,-0.025737735,-0.04608542,-0.020612067,-0.036421858,0.00058081973,0.023264326,0.01807262,0.044502597,0.06486088,0.018181866,-0.02656674,-0.0308531,0.009138237,0.043123018,0.048374277,0.02290219,-0.048557512,-0.067186706,0.08369166,-0.0046534548,0.021024017,0.0044052494,0.02070937,0.009923381,0.04759153,0.019393845,0.0024029403,0.001438281,0.068606295,-0.013476503,0.0400983,-0.011493558,0.020269021,0.037483122,0.0030490062,-0.072224915,-0.0109548215,0.03475819,0.020186165,0.04410143,-0.033810932,-0.0167456,0.01732094,0.009835592,0.08111059,-0.043883897,-0.005554301,-0.039636567,0.0010111206,-0.0009811267,-0.012691116,0.0020267202,0.008749138,0.0032456038,0.042031