	 ('28b82706-7a45-41b2-aad3-16bda8f54b95'::uuid,'Waiting-Skeleton','This meme template features a comical and somewhat eerie scene of a plastic or prop skeleton casually posed outdoors. The skeleton is seated on what appears to be a wooden bench or possibly a picnic table, with its bony arms resting at its sides and legs extended forward.

The skeleton''s posture gives it a relaxed, almost lounging appearance, as if it were a person taking a break or enjoying the sunshine. This juxtaposition of the macabre (a skeleton) with a casual, everyday pose creates the humorous core of the meme''s appeal.

The skeleton is anatomically detailed, showing a full rib cage, spine, pelvis, and limbs. Its skull is turned slightly to one side, giving it a contemplative or observant look. The jaw is closed, which somehow adds to the impression of a content expression.

The setting is outdoors, with a grassy lawn visible in the background. There''s a hint of foliage or perhaps dried plant matter to one side of the frame, suggesting a garden or natural setting. The lighting appears to be natural daylight, which adds to the incongruity of the scene – a symbol of death basking in the vitality of a sunny day.

The meme''s humor and versatility come from the skeleton''s pose and setting. It can be used to represent feelings of exhaustion, waiting, or giving up, but with a darkly comic twist. The image invites captions that play on themes of death, patience, relaxation gone too far, or humorously grim observations about life and its challenges.

