	 ('18c83b03-202c-4e24-8a83-48deaa579dcf'::uuid,'Monkey-Puppet','This meme template features two side-by-side images of the same cartoon monkey head, likely from a children''s TV show or animated series. The character has a distinctive appearance with a large, round head covered in reddish-orange fur or hair. The face is a lighter orange or tan color, with exaggerated features typical of cartoon styling.

The monkey''s eyes are particularly notable. They are large and white, with small black pupils. In the left image, the eyes are looking straight ahead, while in the right image, they are glancing to the side, creating a sense of a double-take or sudden realization.

The expression on the monkey''s face is neutral to slightly concerned, with a small mouth that appears somewhat tense. This subtle change in eye direction between the two images is the key element of the meme, often used to convey a moment of awkwardness, sudden understanding, or internal conflict.

The background of both images is blurry but suggests an outdoor setting with hints of blue sky and possibly greenery. The character appears to be wearing something green, visible at the bottom of the frame, though it''s not clear what exactly this represents.

The overall quality of the image is somewhat low, with a slightly pixelated or compressed look, which is common in memes that have been widely shared and reposted. This low-fi quality adds to the humor and relatability of the meme.

This template is often used to express reactions to uncomfortable situations or moments of realization, playing on the universal experience of those split-second changes in awareness or emotion. The simplicity and expressiveness of the character make it highly versatile for a wide range of humorous contexts.','/memes/Monkey-Puppet.jpg',2,'{}','{"monkey looking away","monkey puppet avoids eye contact","hiding in plain sight","awkward look monkey","monkey looking away meme","thanos wipeing out half of earth"}',0.0,'[0.03396832,-0.02982499,0.014579639,0.010523382,0.02322074,-0.05420124,-0.03348901,-0.01968764,-0.022457415,0.052710064,-0.0071989927,-0.009807381,0.028791003,0.018564658,-0.017465832,-0.006415232,-0.010869048,-0.026933886,-0.013571516,-0.0022388268,-0.0011843494,0.031577025,-0.058302086,-0.018356962,0.024757955,0.056173712,0.0073696743,0.0048034755,0.07794267,0.030823585,0.007744398,-0.0026381183,-0.0012476322,-0.052431878,0.017863367,-0.0010042925,0.048144687,-0.04207864,-0.008196062,-0.04082629,0.050126318,-0.0040948745,0.024060873,-0.047193605,-0.024839189,-0.013004171,-0.015424779,0.024954537,0.032014567,-0.0057898103,0.008483071,-0.027071951,-0.004316501,0.023637371,-0.034754027,-0.049371064,0.01611568,-0.031642236,0.0052914107,0.020648617,0.0513077,0.03899519,-0.0046425513,-0.07499458,-0.03535352,-0.007988775,-0.039953016,-0.018700052,-0.036435712,0.0028460212,0.009274973,0.034388922,0.013644373,-0.027501246,-0.051329512,-0.03628058,-0.015898207,-0.015069122,0.01600644,0.008442453,-0.0018086156,0.042689987,-0.009829207,-0.04419981,-0.0014471305,-0.0057621617,0.02312012,-0.0046500666,0.026893048,-0.047400724,-0.025979051,0.05809601,-0.0019648725,0.031423517,0.031035183,0.035788957,-0.007841411,0.026537996,-0.03658035,-0.00427259,0.004851435,0.031825177,-0.018398033,0.054285143,-0.028897263,-0.015611753,0.006453457,0.008753238,-0.038630348,-0.033699397,0.010333522,-0.022992862,0.016502699,0.0015772134,-0.018580811,-0.0005335963,-0.019017229,0.060314223