	 ('1c2422ec-843b-4604-b910-e972b32c1492'::uuid,'Ill-Just-Wait-Here','This meme template consists of two vertically stacked images, both featuring a character sitting in front of a computer monitor in a dimly lit setting.

In the top panel, we see a middle-aged man with a stern, concerned expression. He''s wearing a light-colored suit jacket and tie, suggesting a professional or business setting. The man''s face is illuminated from the side, creating dramatic shadows that emphasize his furrowed brow and tense jaw. He appears to be intently focused on something on the computer screen, which is visible in the foreground but its contents are not shown.

The bottom panel presents a startling contrast. In the same position as the man from the top image, we now see a grotesque, monstrous figure. This creature has pale, wrinkled skin stretched tightly over a skull-like face with sunken eyes and a gaping, toothy mouth. Long, stringy white hair falls from its head. The monster is wearing similar professional attire to the man above - a dark suit jacket and tie - creating an unsettling juxtaposition between its horrific appearance and the business-like setting.

This template is likely from a horror or science fiction film, playing on themes of transformation or revelation. The stark contrast between the two images suggests a shocking discovery or a sudden, terrifying change. In meme culture, this format is often used to humorously depict extreme reactions to information found online, or to show how prolonged computer use might figuratively transform a person.

The dramatic lighting, the focus on facial expressions (or lack thereof in the monster''s case), and the presence of the computer monitor in both frames make this a versatile template for expressing shock, horror, or drastic changes in perception based on newly acquired information.','/memes/Ill-Just-Wait-Here.jpg',2,'{}','{"waiting skeleton","still waiting",skull,"i''ll just wait here guy","skeleton waiting","skeleton still waiting","waiting indiana jones"}',0.0,'[0.02992066,-0.048560135,0.021080527,0.009509538,0.033309937,-0.055740125,-0.017681133,-0.013138322,-0.03341971,0.037433602,0.017643617,-0.02912232,0.028345225,-0.0014906691,3.4228975e-05,-0.0056493343,0.009774227,-0.028347736,-0.045589898,0.014336124,0.0021707683,0.0006785056,-0.06614174,-0.054552287,-0.031174226,0.057667173,0.01003932,-0.008431387,0.04911602,0.025500176,-0.011733791,-0.003771919,-0.003821622,-0.023554455,-0.0033855282,0.013310432,0.04201202,-0.06556472,-0.02340869,-0.029459435,0.045006696,-0.002094156,0.03392344,-0.036469374,-0.020030309,-0.026662357,0.00960361,-0.0053906026,0.027024357,-0.017122488,0.018813195,-0.008647166,-0.0023142095,0.025158811,-0.018647304,-0.055024598,-0.010033109,-0.007917572,0.0017929774,0.01420718,0.050017796,0.02509146,0.021964353,-0.031539034,-0.028688708,0.012404711,-0.01351226,-0.019254616,-0.018496618,0.03400713,-0.0023892634,0.03911539,0.018822921,0.033561125,-0.037983112,-0.024815744,-0.039331093,-0.031925816,0.030879416,0.018260965,0.011120889,0.037648134,0.0068812827,-0.007871288,-0.01647559,-0.031806324,0.014326746,0.038330883,0.017576622,-0.009028968,0.01576429,0.034568813,0.008659457,0.0033254332,0.01248097,0.057129737,-0.017179957,0.018010233,-0.014175995,0.013326772,-0.017217746,0.052154813,-0.040588047,0.048762113,-0.023288779,0.011518846,0.05670698,-0.011692779,-0.05390725,-0.03444209,0.029790372,-0.042013295,-0.001572661,0.012876527,-0.03785555,0.023057109,-0.0081650885,0.0396586,-0.04840609,-0.010702827,-0.03815852,-0.034584396,-0.010418257,-0