	 ('72445919-9e32-45cd-b44e-ad1286aca587'::uuid,'Grumpy-Cat','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a Siamese cat, famously known as "Grumpy Cat" due to its distinctively displeased facial expression. The cat has striking blue eyes that contrast sharply with its cream-colored fur, which darkens to brown around the face, ears, and paws - typical coloration for a Siamese breed.

The cat''s most notable feature is its seemingly permanent frown, created by the downward turn of its mouth and a slightly furrowed brow. This grumpy expression is what made this particular cat an internet sensation and perfect subject for memes expressing displeasure, sarcasm, or general negativity.

The image captures the cat in what appears to be a home setting, possibly sitting on a person''s lap or a piece of furniture. There''s a hint of denim fabric visible, suggesting the presence of a person just out of frame. The background is blurred but appears to be a warm, yellowish wall, creating a cozy domestic atmosphere that contrasts humorously with the cat''s unamused demeanor.

The cat''s fur looks soft and fluffy, especially around the neck area, giving it a cuddly appearance that again contrasts with its grumpy face. Its ears are perked forward, suggesting alertness despite the disgruntled expression.

This image became a wildly popular meme template, used to convey cynicism, disapproval, or a humorously negative reaction to various situations. The juxtaposition of the cat''s cute appearance with its perpetually unimpressed expression made it a perfect vehicle for comedy and relatable content across social media platforms.','/memes/Grumpy-Cat.jpg',2,'{}','{"grumpy cat happy","grumpy cat smile","angry cat","radioactive grumpy","happy grumpy cat"}',0.0,'[-0.024367213,-0.009397298,0.037044283,-0.005166453,0.026207933,-0.059127398,-0.024996452,-0.0006683064,-0.0060642813,0.04533933,-0.0007550017,-0.0025515652,-0.0067693377,-0.0049156523,-0.0025413742,-0.018530883,0.0057426435,-0.04582962,-0.016375232,0.019062243,0.008980022,-0.0013824623,-0.053205103,-0.016735792,0.028055353,0.1005263,-0.006783201,0.028638633,0.054245543,-0.00015621459,-0.0045460504,-0.010682325,0.011328229,-0.061334647,0.010231421,-0.00030310705,0.025815332,-0.020234441,-0.006100357,-0.019923147,0.03596186,-0.035904855,0.022080593,-0.051200956,0.0021350833,-0.018546794,-0.039547447,0.054007582,0.039467555,-0.038180575,-0.014379389,-0.03478346,0.014537848,-0.008469387,-0.028309835,-0.04325681,-0.022326767,0.0048833536,0.008828223,0.017019121,0.032233354,-0.002051197,0.002727983,-0.03839923,-0.02331204,0.0053934753,0.0034195955,-0.034777693,-0.0129206795,-0.0036886018,0.022999246,0.0128962025,-0.008333277,-0.014791717,-0.070653446,-0.044636317,-0.021097004,-0.037404966,0.0043427837,0.03625562,0.025757993,0.031807084,0.00060765736,-0.0027328169,-0.012676643,0.0072417753,0.025188645,0.06931305,-0.034756158,-0.014605133,-0.0030743894,0.059581235,0.016057532,0.058982443,0.007781774,0.027871449,-0.0005258324,0.03671075,-0.0024871929,0.0071452456,-0.010033082,0.032014154,0.009294358,0.05006134,-0.037376422,-0.015780423,0.025193153,-0.022709642,-0.041757844,-0.023252735,-0.016441531,-0.019049933,0.0017763246,-0.017132862,-0.02316795,0.023553288,-0.02810707,0.06599786,-0.059180602,-0.031294286,-0.027572017,-0.