	 ('a41032b1-d842-49c5-896b-49ae5d6130d8'::uuid,'Dr-Evil-Laser','This meme template features a scene reminiscent of a classic villain from spy or science fiction films. The central figure is a bald man wearing a high-collared gray suit, reminiscent of a stereotypical evil mastermind or antagonist character.

The man''s expression is one of exaggerated surprise or excitement, with his mouth open in an "O" shape and his eyes wide. He''s gesturing dramatically with both hands raised, fingers splayed out in a way that suggests he''s emphasizing a point or reacting to something with great enthusiasm.

In front of him is a large spherical object that appears to be a model of the moon or some other celestial body. It''s gray and pockmarked, adding to the sci-fi aesthetic of the scene.

The background is split diagonally, with a vibrant red section on the left and a stark white section on the right. This color contrast adds visual interest and a sense of drama to the image. The white section features riveted edges, suggesting a high-tech or spaceship-like setting.

The lighting in the scene is dramatic, creating sharp contrasts and shadows that enhance the theatrical nature of the character''s pose and expression.

