	 ('f72aadd9-45de-47d4-babb-ccc6a4693ea6'::uuid,'Maury-Lie-Detector','This meme template features a middle-aged man seated in a chair, likely on a television set stage. He''s wearing a dark suit jacket over a black shirt, giving him a formal yet approachable appearance. The man has a distinctive facial expression combining skepticism, slight confusion, and a hint of judgment, with his eyebrows slightly furrowed and his mouth in a subtle grimace.

The focal point of the image is an envelope or card that the man is holding in his hands. On this card, the word "Maury" is clearly visible, suggesting this is from the set of the Maury Povich show, a well-known American tabloid talk show famous for its dramatic reveals and confrontations.

The background of the image shows a brick wall, typical of many talk show sets that aim to create a casual, urban atmosphere. A portion of what appears to be a structural column is visible on the left side of the frame, adding to the studio setting aesthetic.

This particular meme template is often used to convey moments of revelation, skepticism, or when presenting surprising or controversial information. The man''s expression and the show''s reputation for dramatic reveals make it a perfect template for humorous or shocking statements in meme culture.

The composition of the image, focusing tightly on the man and the card he''s holding, emphasizes the moment of reveal or judgment, which is central to how this meme is typically used. The lighting is bright and even, typical of television studio lighting, which adds to the feeling of an "on-air" moment frozen in time.','/memes/Maury-Lie-Detector.jpg',2,'{}','{"The lie detector determined that was a lie. The fact that you X determined that was a lie. Maury Povich.",muary,"you are the father"}',0.0,'[0.04778704,-0.029007219,0.031317394,0.032825805,0.019119352,-0.06937859,-0.033659916,0.0027336613,-0.038259827,0.025980651,0.020613989,-0.02589359,0.039013483,0.02107092,-0.028745499,-0.0039497856,0.014450541,-0.031136382,-0.00649797,0.02321337,0.0106637655,-0.0048468616,-0.0733563,-0.040577415,-0.0208757,0.040647883,-0.016457096,0.050387584,0.039830156,0.00059873844,-0.011512909,-0.014878737,-0.005599069,-0.03345114,-0.011462741,3.637739e-05,0.02141059,-0.024202228,-0.03493086,-0.0329157,0.02852534,-0.027291458,0.027743746,0.008276028,-0.03372998,-0.03573134,-0.0010775747,-0.02395559,0.034170438,0.009559207,0.0034365773,-0.018434646,0.015047375,0.0017712229,-0.031040102,-0.028526865,-0.035936885,-0.00019727694,-0.006853584,-0.0054528574,0.030625915,0.0012094459,-0.0045104185,-0.036543164,-0.017036483,0.01391377,-0.005693147,0.0031207309,-0.019858794,-0.029687006,0.0047767176,0.01622343,0.023151338,-0.008142795,-0.048125558,-0.0016122016,-0.021184353,-0.017647283,0.019576872,-0.0023731785,0.030504245,0.03758376,0.025277158,-0.021327857,-0.034946974,-0.020349314,0.00797264,0.041371424,0.00696008,-0.023116082,-0.016087396,0.051414374,0.013001416,-0.006454479,0.02541566,0.043445554,-0.0035604842,0.027387368,0.033480093,0.028190805,-0.011638582,0.042866196,-0.05347212,-0.0015290729,0.021506064,0.020812593,0.08725275,-0.019899452,-0.06250954,-0.0341393,0.015183641,-0.03830572,0.007345346,-0.018665278,-0.04387779,0.046891633,-1.434427e-05,0.05567605,-0.046989687,0.0062075686,-0