	 ('3d43c8fb-5135-4caa-88ad-d2bb5b3bf6d2'::uuid,'Put-It-Somewhere-Else-Patrick','This meme template is a two-panel image from the popular animated TV show SpongeBob SquarePants. It features Patrick Star, the pink starfish character, in the foreground of both panels, surrounded by a crowd of diverse sea creatures.

In the top panel, Patrick is shown with a confused and slightly alarmed expression. His mouth is open, revealing his prominent teeth, and his eyes are wide and unfocused. He appears to be gesturing or pointing with one of his arms. Around him, we can see a variety of colorful characters with exaggerated expressions of shock, surprise, or concern. These include fish-like creatures in various hues such as yellow, pink, and light blue.

The bottom panel shows a change in Patrick''s expression. Here, he looks more assertive or explanatory, with his mouth open as if speaking. His arm is still raised, but the gesture seems more deliberate. The surrounding characters have shifted positions slightly, but still maintain their looks of surprise or attentiveness.

The background of both panels suggests an outdoor setting, with what appears to be wooden planks visible, reminiscent of a dock or boardwalk common in the show''s underwater city setting of Bikini Bottom.

This template is often used to depict scenarios where someone makes a controversial statement (top panel), followed by an attempt to explain or justify it (bottom panel), usually in a humorous or absurd context. The exaggerated expressions and the stark contrast between Patrick''s initial confusion and subsequent confidence make this a versatile and expressive meme format.','/memes/Put-It-Somewhere-Else-Patrick.jpg',2,'{}','{"patrick from spongebob","push it somewhere else patrick","patrick star"}',0.0,'[0.03506611,-0.029111521,0.005285851,-0.0043449127,0.035723668,-0.038766436,-0.00983577,0.011581263,0.014473497,0.038024105,-0.023374802,-0.007067608,0.017062845,-0.007879106,-0.020038104,-0.025774809,-0.0051154457,-0.03767585,-0.045414746,0.024594165,-0.010632123,-0.014708822,-0.037004907,-0.01764855,-0.016593544,0.06539087,0.010472348,0.019844642,0.05100786,-0.008111109,0.012833082,-0.019860258,-0.003477327,-0.02921671,0.014216678,-0.018478293,0.02971127,-0.05572397,-0.010370667,-0.038321257,0.018315895,-0.017232465,0.016893828,-0.016924981,0.0016784646,-0.013713825,-0.0066839303,0.01979941,0.012488231,0.016099652,0.01308165,-0.006643882,0.018970953,0.04016663,-0.035685334,-0.06517038,-0.013155156,-0.008665301,0.02220209,0.023223342,0.008389664,0.011627828,-0.025260882,-0.054980632,-0.030497292,0.0099658,-0.018244246,-0.045474153,-0.022644036,0.009621751,-0.034570348,0.031247394,0.012559724,-0.013864127,-0.044589654,-0.022533432,-0.052780975,-0.023440443,0.027115807,0.0032765977,0.028822217,0.041540388,0.02709839,-0.018456297,-0.022791922,-0.014860903,0.03280151,0.023414057,0.036532234,-0.045123026,-0.012993891,0.06308749,0.0032641422,-0.0030463266,0.026007911,0.040113375,-0.0020738675,0.024055732,0.0052436264,0.007128516,0.013290083,0.062233694,-0.029567717,0.05653075,-0.03590574,0.045605652,0.023862693,0.016727958,-0.02611015,-0.025180113,0.015168745,0.00812872,0.03879831,-0.011315029,0.024342407,0.036400367,-0.03189631,0.045009904,-0.054682262,-0.023603031,-0.05