The background shows a suburban or residential setting with bare trees, indicating it''s likely late fall or winter. There''s a hint of snow or frost on the ground, further emphasizing the cold weather theme. The sky is overcast, adding to the somber mood of the image.

The composition of the image is a medium close-up shot, focusing on the man''s upper body and face. This framing allows viewers to clearly see his facial expression and body language, which convey a sense of frustration or urgency.

The image has a slightly grainy or low-resolution quality, suggesting it may be a screenshot from a video. In the top right corner, there''s a white text overlay that says "Bernie," which appears to be part of the original media from which this image was taken.

This meme template is often used to express frustration, repetition, or the need to make repeated requests. The man''s expression and the winter setting create a mood of persistence in the face of challenging circumstances. The template is versatile and can be applied to various situations where someone feels they need to ask for something multiple times or explain a concept repeatedly.','/memes/Bernie-I-Am-Once-Again-Asking-For-Your-Support.jpg',2,'{}','{"bernie sanders commercial","bernie sanders 2020 campaign","asking for your financial support","once again bernie"}',0.0,'[0.010766549,-0.003922152,0.004135871,0.016558448,0.008662308,-0.023920998,0.0010778102,0.030416423,0.0015017869,0.077324696,0.008618454,-0.033146083,0.038937375,0.004446383,0.0070497864,-0.043473374,-0.009287727,-0.014941666,-0.028326236,0.037190605,-0.0183306,0.0011703855,-0.044631995,-0.047878858,-0.0039328528,0.038501997,-0.03623669,0.014709755,0.060477983,0.030330988,0.029906655,-0.012298065,-0.034180943,-0.05743361,-0.00026218258,-0.0135732535,0.026460249,-0.06305521,0.0020877246,-0.018297715,0.027950352,-0.03904417,0.013207786,-0.026434474,-0.031873353,-0.06927414,-0.050843373,0.007378664,0.032851744,-0.01749685,0.012759358,-0.016750356,0.019931657,-0.00426242,0.027363675,-0.0048076436,-0.01767981,0.028315993,-0.01548062,0.0027471427,0.031430814,0.007891141,0.010164332,-0.02675293,-0.006342292,0.010545484,-0.020705352,0.011490036,-0.022445489,-0.00021565633,-0.015070418,0.013935823,0.01807739,-0.008416265,-0.019600017,0.017187256,-0.038516857,-0.020739371,-0.005418371,0.03270007,0.016129455,0.027350029,-0.0076793493,0.0069258013,-0.016571349,-0.02585494,0.0020094712,0.033379197,0.007436092,-0.019492045,-0.017602125,0.04845167,-0.005725968,0.033833697,0.006538671,0.047149684,0.008380567,0.02634762,-0.0033880891,0.012120096,-0.0087273875,0.07707449,-0.0073515708,0.043806113,-0.055921305,0.005725429,0.012613582,0.00014331046,-0.08083444,-0.010059935,-0.009704559,-0.017755855,0.01619085,0.004