	 ('d6e01077-8431-4d46-b2c9-4308a69b4e11'::uuid,'Boardroom-Meeting-Suggestion','This meme template is a four-panel comic strip that depicts a classic office meeting scenario that takes an unexpected turn. 

The first panel shows a typical boardroom setting with four characters: a person leaning over the table (presumably the boss or meeting leader), two employees sitting at the table, and the back of another person''s head visible in the foreground. The background is a soft pink, giving a slightly surreal feel to the corporate environment.

In the second panel, we see a close-up of the three employees. The two on the left are speaking enthusiastically, with animated expressions and gestures. The employee on the right, however, has a more pensive or bored expression, resting their head on their hand.

The third panel dramatically shifts the scene. It''s split into two parts: on the left, we see an extreme close-up of the boss''s face, now contorted in anger with bulging eyes. On the right, we see the pensive employee from before, now looking concerned or worried.

The final panel zooms out to show the pensive employee being forcibly ejected from a tall office building, flying through the air against a backdrop of a blue sky, green field, and distant mountains. This absurdist conclusion creates a stark contrast with the mundane office setting of the earlier panels.

The art style is simple but expressive, using bold lines and exaggerated facial expressions to convey emotion. The color palette shifts from soft pinks in the office to vibrant outdoor colors in the final panel, emphasizing the dramatic turn of events.

This template is often used to humorously illustrate situations where an unpopular or unconventional idea is met with extreme overreaction, playing on the absurdity of corporate culture and group dynamics.','/memes/Boardroom-Meeting-Suggestion.jpg',4,'{}','{"throw a guy out the boardroom window","board room meeting","boss throwing employee","company meem template","any ideas?","man getting thrown out window"}',0.0,'[0.024688846,-0.053206004,0.02675451,0.006428395,0.038806535,-0.07492365,-0.036939174,-0.021145696,-0.00032491164,0.04050453,0.010389669,0.025185099,0.029737262,0.0078549255,0.008520767,-0.01147178,-0.0158459,-0.005490886,-0.011552387,0.037541352,-0.018259626,-0.035448283,-0.08818013,-0.0341334,-0.018283252,0.060117573,0.0034525637,0.006050954,0.077955976,0.027467404,-0.020183573,-0.028464451,-0.014682122,-0.060271114,0.01627446,-0.0018023214,0.010079364,-0.04256082,-0.041147266,-0.022080084,0.005913858,-0.013072462,0.018614424,-0.046966825,-0.009528325,-0.031149937,-0.0008077918,0.026774045,0.027956536,-0.018464124,0.025761202,0.015317927,-0.0023836622,0.015589959,-0.023584893,-0.04062349,-0.020689372,-0.02067701,0.005682935,0.033914465,0.016822135,0.024173837,0.03630649,-0.036073364,-0.014532162,0.024416069,-0.030042982,-0.026577516,-0.018139197,0.0017656302,-0.033339012,0.024782429,0.012276533,-0.0054339063,-0.0509462,-0.0034231974,-0.0043065883,-0.011118299,-0.00045239172,0.0041228696,0.031980366,0.04261839,-0.037236035,-0.0028369015,-0.016155144,-0.008424146,0.053070486,0.062280975,0.024525637,-0.029001802,0.004638511,0.045162987,-0.016609984,-0.008922836,0.01842258,0.043849006,-0.03889344,0.04394273,-0.004236514,0.0060952213,-0.037737492,0.042145655,-0.0516774,0.027200941,-0.049758166,-0.00030068314,0.093400024,0.013063928,-0.009017356,-0.04398465,-0.0123145385,-0.008347183,0.02134495,0.0073606744,-0.013773548,0.024232743,0.039221425,0.051959336,-0.040850367,-0.004382504,-0.020922927,-0.032080337,-0.032389436,0.012432394,-0.010488134,-0.0005269359,0