The man''s facial expression is particularly noteworthy - he has a slight smirk and his eyes convey a sense of confidence or smugness, as if he''s just thought of something particularly clever or is in on a secret. This combination of the gesture and expression makes the image perfect for memes about outsmarting situations or having a clever solution to a problem.

