	 ('091d1195-3199-451c-b49d-b8ca4d72de9e'::uuid,'See-Nobody-Cares','This meme template consists of two related images, likely screenshots from a movie or TV show, depicting an interaction between two men at what appears to be a tropical resort or beach restaurant.

In the top image, we see a wider shot of an outdoor dining area. There are several tables with umbrellas, and patrons can be seen in the background. In the foreground, two men are seated at a small round table. On the left is a slender man wearing a red polo shirt and a straw hat with sunglasses. On the right is a larger man wearing a colorful Hawaiian-style shirt with a floral print. The larger man appears to be speaking animatedly, with his arm outstretched in a gesturing motion.

The bottom image is a closer view of the same two men, now standing and continuing their conversation. The setting has shifted slightly, with palm trees visible in the background, suggesting they''ve moved closer to the beach. The man in the red polo is now facing the camera, looking attentively at the larger man. The larger man is still animated in his expression and body language, holding what looks like a beverage in one hand while gesturing with the other.

The contrast between the two men''s appearances and demeanors is striking and likely contributes to the comedic potential of this template. The casual, vacation-like setting adds to the overall tone, suggesting a lighthearted or humorous context for whatever conversation or situation is unfolding between these characters.

This template is often used to represent enthusiastic explanations or passionate arguments, with the larger man typically embodying the role of someone eagerly sharing information or opinions, while the other man represents a listener or audience.','/memes/See-Nobody-Cares.jpg',2,'{}','{"Jurassic Park Dennis","see? no one cares","see? nobody cares"}',0.0,'[0.028774073,0.00024412991,0.0184121,0.010160762,0.018190075,-0.057110243,-0.035435572,0.008487366,-0.0012172131,0.024302064,0.04581799,0.021707492,0.012915723,0.0026422618,-0.016025504,-0.012218492,0.014578067,-0.025127685,-0.03591149,0.024312507,-0.015748696,-0.00031776694,-0.04176549,-0.009370985,-0.013773442,0.058312338,0.0011892454,0.025758622,0.076340005,0.01871346,0.014919315,0.0045489967,0.011337178,-0.015506988,0.013352338,0.009525085,0.03955003,-0.0525788,-0.045913544,-0.058654524,0.013444176,-0.0069480045,0.024713134,-0.016097175,-0.013337945,0.00888568,-0.008904679,-0.031206312,0.0071190917,-0.0026776197,0.0208499,-0.0041275234,0.009102791,0.031505994,-0.04412399,-0.009833386,-0.04319936,-0.001840282,0.028976502,0.015152438,-0.0021442927,0.016756935,-0.02597321,-0.06745836,-0.01274072,-0.0030650534,0.013020382,-0.013451539,0.011020809,-0.021682447,0.015051887,0.028020015,0.02134104,0.010381302,-0.02513136,-0.012913541,-0.0007372674,-0.010090078,0.02217484,0.003745138,0.050530564,0.0779144,-0.009926168,-0.013191372,-0.048182335,-0.011416031,0.056185037,0.017752372,0.032788172,-0.012866627,-0.011043405,0.045512874,-0.016158044,-0.008398897,-0.0017962587,0.042970665,-0.009417806,0.030783186,-0.014657736,0.011247855,0.0073613357,0.06322304,-0.0362454,0.017049609,-0.05984878,0.03305049,0.051208884,0.01629502,-0.035501886,-0.031195285,-0.0036593024,0.005986939,0.0021058153,-0.019711891,-0.023184158,0.039131425,0.025990095,0.015767239,-0.051659163,-0.02134678,-0.05478355,0.00587118,-0.0071503767,0.023111489,0.0018855932,-0.015484673,0.025358448,0.038675316,-0.062287293,0.0334653,0.007162412,-0.03121845,-0.0008