	 ('9ea54edd-a25c-43a9-9914-d0e27d090438'::uuid,'Confession-Bear','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a black bear, specifically an Asian black bear or "moon bear," known for its distinctive white crescent marking on its chest (though not visible in this image). The bear''s face is the central focus, positioned slightly above center in the frame. Its expression is notably anthropomorphic and melancholic, giving it a distinctly human-like quality of sadness or disappointment.

The bear''s dark, round eyes gaze directly at the camera with a soulful, almost pleading look. Its snout is prominent, with a glistening black nose. The bear''s mouth is slightly downturned, creating the impression of a frown or pout. This expression is key to the meme''s appeal, as it conveys a sense of dejection or resigned disappointment that resonates with human emotions.

The bear''s fur is a rich, dark charcoal color, appearing thick and plush. Its rounded ears are just visible at the top of the frame, adding to its cuddly yet forlorn appearance. The bear''s forepaws are visible, clinging to what appears to be a thick tree branch or log. The contrast between the bear''s dark fur and its lighter-colored claws is striking.

The background is blurred but suggests a natural, possibly forested environment. The soft focus on the surroundings keeps the attention firmly on the bear''s expressive face.

