	 ('cd961f9c-bb4a-4855-9f4e-5843e062bf9c'::uuid,'Hard-To-Swallow-Pills','This meme template consists of two panels arranged vertically, both featuring illustrations of hands in a soft, pastel art style against a gentle gradient background.

In the top panel, we see a hand holding a large white medication bottle. The bottle has a simple label that reads "Hard to swallow pills". Another hand is pointing at this label with its index finger, drawing attention to the text. The hands are rendered in a realistic style with subtle shading and detail, giving them a three-dimensional quality.

The bottom panel shows an open palm facing upward, holding three small round pills. Two of the pills appear to be typical white tablets, while one has markings visible on its surface. Another hand enters the frame from the right, with its index finger apparently about to pick up or interact with one of the pills.

The overall composition creates a visual metaphor, with the "Hard to swallow pills" in the top panel being represented literally by actual pills in the bottom panel. The soft color palette and clean, minimalist style give the image a calm, almost clinical feel, which contrasts with the often difficult or uncomfortable truths that this meme template is typically used to represent.

This template is frequently used online to humorously or pointedly present ideas, facts, or opinions that people might find difficult to accept or acknowledge, mirroring the concept of a "hard to swallow pill" in a literal and figurative sense.','/memes/Hard-To-Swallow-Pills.jpg',1,'{}','{"hard pills to swallow"}',0.0,'[-0.009170991,-0.039626367,0.031982843,0.020871,0.032900296,-0.063022725,-0.028598266,0.0052988315,-0.022203784,0.042062942,-0.002607894,0.007927914,0.04103676,0.011196443,-0.017888803,0.034471054,0.011831969,-0.022472166,-0.012930676,0.012070759,-0.009999514,0.026009912,-0.08325916,-0.048119005,-0.031890206,0.025006514,0.018094962,0.029597772,0.06059783,0.018925069,-0.018851051,0.0058150445,0.021910597,-0.046539057,0.009570512,-0.013230042,0.018559217,-0.04194556,0.00050643296,-0.047846302,0.047030635,-0.021087535,0.026271405,-0.0100932885,-0.009028565,-0.0073228,-0.00688396,-0.0069722002,-0.0014906891,-0.023326747,0.02133103,-0.008098844,0.026893085,0.008980069,-0.05047321,0.0020901302,-0.013460715,-0.056127027,0.0027817541,0.0046427613,0.028107222,0.0032967872,-0.0033960775,-0.051202733,-0.02103246,0.02071391,-0.032340042,-0.013692176,-0.038265638,-0.035344616,-0.020770466,0.027542405,-0.014099337,-0.021709068,-0.04309745,-0.024333868,0.0016832851,0.008328625,0.032412764,0.02761131,0.02981276,0.053369533,-0.0064898343,-0.012631945,-0.032831345,0.038557757,0.016691167,0.028698618,0.032155607,-0.038384456,0.011060098,0.044199232,-0.01914464,-0.018356984,-0.010007208,0.029685326,-0.030346587,0.028181871,0.00024198357,0.010449471,-0.003545433,0.04135151,-0.009477528,0.040756058,-0.029479172,0.01767836,0.058357157,-0.007648122,-0.034524597,-0.022288509,0.004401821,-0.02913196,-0.0025672081,-0.01484123,-0.00014739887,0.011598425,0.0113637615,0.03541473,-0.048396733,0.04751002,-0.026849043,0.012507664,-0.013441861,0.004419966,-0.0044439505,0.019513434,0.014244852,0.029618833,-0.05255812,-0.0052354145,0.030114895,-0.0043021226,0.021605657,0.012037062,-0.00