	 ('3d475333-ca40-4fd0-91e6-a4dcfe27953a'::uuid,'Mugatu-So-Hot-Right-Now','This meme template is a scene from a movie or TV show, set in what appears to be a theater or cinema. The image focuses on a group of characters in the audience, with two particularly eye-catching figures in the foreground.

In the center, there''s a man with bleached blonde, curly hair wearing a flamboyant red and blue outfit with silver fringe details. His expression is one of exaggerated surprise or excitement, with his mouth wide open. He''s holding a small white fluffy dog, also dressed in red, adding to the eccentric nature of his appearance.

Next to him is a woman with jet-black hair in a blunt bob cut, wearing a red outfit that appears to be made of latex or leather. She has striking makeup, including bold red lipstick, and is wearing an elaborate red necklace. Her expression is serious, almost scowling, providing a stark contrast to the man''s excited demeanor.

Behind them, we can see other audience members. There''s a woman with blonde hair wearing an animal print top, looking amused. To her left is a man in a dark jacket, appearing more reserved. On the far right, partially out of frame, is another blonde figure.

The contrast between the exuberant man, the stern woman, and the more typical audience members behind them creates a visually striking and humorous juxtaposition. This image is often used in memes to represent extreme or opposing reactions to a situation, with the blonde man typically embodying enthusiasm or naivety, while the dark-haired woman represents skepticism or disdain.

The theatrical setting and over-the-top styling of the main characters give the image a campy, comedic feel, making it versatile for various meme contexts where extreme or conflicting emotions are being portrayed.','/memes/Mugatu-So-Hot-Right-Now.jpg',2,'{}','{"Mugatu from Zoolander","Will Farrell",mugato}',0.0,'[0.023842204,-0.044676833,0.016781524,0.00016909541,0.01661272,-0.06545988,-0.014237021,-0.006763444,-0.036703575,0.05420405,0.016904801,-0.0007456211,0.026426014,0.020119056,-0.0016120167,0.0035298648,-0.008376821,-0.049200635,-0.042480733,0.035427794,-0.035198595,0.012955488,-0.07317767,-0.01679148,-0.00413577,0.067722365,0.024793305,0.0040222188,0.053755935,0.008649823,0.011930005,0.019171799,0.0015163524,-0.015445674,0.02713085,-0.01964414,0.012025495,-0.041917372,-0.040672608,-0.05425083,0.029080562,-0.019010842,0.01781473,-0.012343237,-0.031172734,-0.0006858131,0.022364946,0.005238458,0.021621585,5.724743e-05,-0.0023205823,-0.041526977,-0.0052418006,0.027665867,-0.021422993,-0.046044018,-0.003573768,-0.0003034648,0.02187212,0.02726989,0.035323367,-0.0046577966,-0.022985531,-0.027194344,-0.017645588,-0.0006691138,-0.014852964,-0.016219608,-0.041338317,-0.02013886,0.049041174,0.009494066,-0.010415295,-0.011160936,-0.051372107,-0.025501808,-0.033656955,-0.009930974,0.019784538,0.02040845,0.03257543,0.041260034,-0.00041274558,-0.027559025,-0.0047830306,-0.019455569,0.011312224,0.035076465,-0.005914369,-0.02022318,-0.02003314,0.040224243,-0.017764723,0.009362728,-0.013024794,0.02889641,0.008855239,0.003258097,0.0045124115,-0.010491785,-0.03643944,0.057856746,-0.045884036,0.04795697,-0.057249393,0.021712221,0.039272066,0.021712458,-0.061794132,-0.03366718,-0.009499313,-0.03391285,0.024717415,-0.0053031896,-0.029129583,0.051768214,0.014239999,0.04851285,-0.05201691,-0.016372679,-0.013989053,-0.0027912508,-0.031914838,-0.03691463,0.018173508,-0.023497017,0.045647137,0.03622114,-0.027264966,0.021195525,0.011597843,-0.030037181,0.015995534,0.039237294,-0.0408301