	 ('09ef1d5e-348b-47a1-9a5b-5a2d0caf8a6d'::uuid,'Expanding-Brain','This meme template consists of four vertically stacked panels, each showing a progressively more intense or "enlightened" depiction of a human brain.

The first panel shows a basic X-ray-like image of a skull in blue outline against a black background. The brain is visible but not particularly detailed or active-looking.

In the second panel, the image becomes more detailed and vibrant. It shows a side profile of a head with the brain highlighted in bright blue. The brain appears more active, with small points of light scattered throughout, suggesting neural activity.

The third panel intensifies further. The brain is now shown in a pinkish-white color, glowing brightly within the outline of a head. The neural activity appears even more pronounced, with the brain seeming to radiate light and energy.

The fourth and final panel represents the pinnacle of this progression. It shows a teal-colored brain that appears to be exploding with energy. Bright white lines radiate outward from the brain in all directions, suggesting an extreme level of mental activity or enlightenment. The background is a deep blue, making the glowing brain stand out dramatically.

This meme template is often used to represent increasing levels of knowledge, understanding, or "wokeness" on a topic, with each successive image representing a higher state of awareness or intelligence. The visual progression from a simple X-ray to an energy-radiating brain effectively communicates this concept of mental expansion or enlightenment in a visually striking and easily understandable way.','/memes/Expanding-Brain.jpg',4,'{}','{"levels of intelligence","expanding brain template","brain expanding","expanding brain meme","mind expansion",4-expanding-brain-meme,"enlightement meme","expanding mind","big brain"}',0.0,'[-0.00073012087,-0.030335039,0.009226329,0.0020774,-0.0030109228,-0.04345884,-0.0262904,0.0067440737,-0.03221866,0.06502105,0.008158107,0.0024880809,0.040611453,-0.0060614645,-0.016860623,-0.0022376955,-0.03409367,-0.044157445,-0.04785137,0.013837171,-0.020364434,0.015768792,-0.084260434,-0.0073352857,-0.022774346,0.050058246,0.013267303,0.015969098,0.05692074,0.031109184,-0.00020250792,-0.032025088,0.040303215,-0.071392655,-0.00853928,0.011853053,0.01864093,-0.0579123,-0.014641061,-0.011529514,0.0074115135,-0.008910526,0.008312966,-0.036925513,-0.044879247,-0.02631612,-0.016631594,-0.021821646,0.022138318,-0.0076367585,0.011583615,-0.023853973,0.023889905,-0.013088344,-0.011884252,-0.030297315,-0.015063112,-0.016162721,-0.032490276,0.027153539,0.05144259,0.030460488,0.01979924,-0.039707307,-0.017083567,0.027018348,-0.023161484,-0.02447705,-0.042219073,-0.019037722,-0.031190451,0.024882998,-0.022036793,-0.023802536,-0.020594861,-0.005269962,0.0022388157,-0.010656667,0.0010873318,-0.03046394,0.025550745,0.028819026,-0.015792402,0.01855197,0.0036609608,-0.019074367,-0.0078740865,0.0066351225,0.026928946,-0.055063143,0.011998056,0.031818587,0.012711532,0.004243126,0.026242224,0.027049037,-0.02828368,0.038538415,0.0021620423,0.015019634,-0.016268995,0.05900312,-0.037547473,0.040934235,-0.05433484,-0.009591766,0.028659856,0.027938543,-0.012674388,-0.