	 ('d9db3a65-5a68-4173-8b3c-58d41bb87725'::uuid,'Running-Away-Balloon','This meme template consists of two panels stacked vertically, depicting a humorous and slightly absurd scenario with simplistic cartoon characters.

In the top panel, we see a white, stick figure-like character with a round head, wide eyes, and a large open-mouthed smile. This character is reaching out with both arms towards a large, bright yellow circle on the right side of the frame. The character appears excited and eager to grasp or interact with the yellow object. The background is a light blue color, giving the scene a simple, clean appearance.

The bottom panel shows the same scene but with an unexpected twist. The white character is still reaching for the yellow circle, maintaining the same posture and expression. However, a new character has appeared: a large, pink blob-like figure on the left side of the frame. This pink character has small eyes and a subtle smile, giving it a calm, almost bemused expression. The most striking element is that the pink character has extended what appears to be an arm or appendage around the white character, grasping it from behind in an intimate or possessive manner.

The white character now has a single tear or sweat drop on its face, suggesting sudden discomfort or surprise at the pink character''s presence and action. The background in this panel is a slightly darker shade of blue, emphasizing the change in the situation.

This template is often used to represent scenarios where someone is enthusiastically pursuing a goal or desire (represented by the yellow circle), only to be unexpectedly interrupted or hindered by an unforeseen factor (symbolized by the pink character). The comic timing between the two panels and the stark visual contrast between the characters make this a versatile and effective meme format for expressing frustration, surprise, or the interference of unexpected elements in one''s plans.','/memes/Running-Away-Balloon.jpg',5,'{}','{"big yellow ball and pink guy","me vs my hopes and dreams","good grades and success","cant reach"}',0.0,'[0.014862653,-0.025759827,0.0095869545,0.018965764,0.016691199,-0.053934578,0.0107613625,0.0070705735,-0.00759401,0.07784258,0.00081764394,0.010328337,0.029979767,0.003125458,-0.031826135,0.005008333,-0.006443974,-0.037079446,-0.012382746,0.028790789,-0.026956296,0.005980943,-0.06265395,-0.018102823,-0.01675331,0.07271034,0.0032445337,-0.004339877,0.05511077,0.012617131,-0.020623473,0.0040646973,0.007670927,-0.05294439,-0.002053872,-0.026980791,0.020837102,-0.04101467,0.013028849,-0.037235323,0.031552076,-0.0125723,0.034553945,-0.035810564,-0.027168347,-0.015370418,-0.017028982,0.0040653236,0.0304338,-0.026914114,0.008050329,-0.024551144,0.0052624745,0.0046287915,-0.027951172,-0.012452374,-0.019662937,-0.030917233,-0.0038720954,0.020952685,0.016006846,0.017742665,-0.00047958878,-0.05719862,-0.03806308,0.0031344139,-0.033558697,-0.0165468,-0.014283576,-0.002199182,0.008948131,0.022840243,-0.019927017,-0.05033053,-0.056793854,0.0088064335,-0.02345888,-0.015360529,0.009015521,-0.0007120717,0.05634717,0.057375945,-0.013816077,-0.025709854,0.0016772295,-0.009980315,0.03283697,0.02336543,0.009485485,-0.04593521,-0.021613948,0.047839206,-0.015329777,0.015136459,0.025615634,0.030695619,-0.033560004,0.04306297,-0.0051398627,0.0053528603,-0.027106673,0.06210856,-0.0289093,0.017318279,-0.056119204,0.002415986,0.05092634,0.0082398765,-0.033215795,