	 ('2aa23bcb-8e35-475a-a375-404844686364'::uuid,'UNO-Draw-25-Cards','This meme template consists of two side-by-side images that create a humorous contrast related to the popular card game UNO.

On the left side, we see a close-up of a hand holding a large, oversized UNO card. This card is black, which is not a standard color in the UNO deck, making it immediately stand out. The card displays the text "OR draw 25" in a handwritten style, implying a custom or joke card that presents an extreme version of the game''s "Draw 2" or "Draw 4" penalty cards.

On the right side of the image, we see a man sitting at a table, looking slightly frustrated or resigned. He''s holding a large fan of UNO cards in his hands, suggesting he has drawn the 25 cards rather than completing the implied action on the left card. The man is wearing a dark long-sleeved shirt and appears to be in a casual indoor setting, possibly a home or office break room. There''s also a can of soda on the table in front of him, adding to the casual atmosphere.

The juxtaposition of these two images creates the meme''s humor: the absurd choice between doing something undesirable (implied by the left image) or facing the consequence of drawing 25 cards (shown in the right image). This template is often used to joke about difficult choices or situations where all options seem unpalatable.

The meme plays on the shared cultural understanding of UNO rules and the often dramatic moments in the game when players must draw multiple cards. It exaggerates this familiar scenario to an comedic extreme, making it relatable and funny to a wide audience familiar with the game.','/memes/UNO-Draw-25-Cards.jpg',2,'{}','{"do something you don’t like or draw 25 cards","uno dilemma","uno or draw 25","draw 25","do something you don''t like or draw 25","draw 25 meme",sprite}',0.0,'[0.0010773785,-0.01629431,0.014904485,0.018899167,-0.02046487,-0.048376374,-0.049470723,0.009179334,-0.00859919,0.061655242,0.024626322,0.025160698,0.039875925,0.012850261,-0.031132147,0.023866652,-0.020135354,-0.022702312,-0.018561786,0.009599985,-0.009996991,-0.017555304,-0.060357038,-0.048828483,0.0038296771,0.020648878,0.001361942,0.037806347,0.06342157,0.013649288,-0.002540307,-0.009916333,0.010946138,-0.06716938,-0.009436708,-0.008933495,0.042269096,-0.026126796,-0.030476315,-0.025769113,0.015230247,-0.03379696,0.034176413,-0.010211019,-0.03255904,-0.027874116,-0.029327467,-0.02326755,0.03728032,-0.011700133,-0.0017916696,-0.027220342,0.008586437,0.0021617825,-0.01832531,-0.012867336,-0.045959953,-0.023310093,0.0038563136,0.033829074,0.025048943,-0.034547955,0.005674941,-0.038036413,-0.019767812,0.0017880155,-0.023696704,-0.022239717,-0.024002872,-0.023364194,-0.002164349,0.010165113,-0.024766037,-0.013653717,-0.039914295,0.03347955,0.008621158,-0.031146796,-0.032464493,0.0048293336,-0.0031780656,0.044169866,-0.026298353,-0.014339765,-0.037636053,-0.03692414,0.04423718,0.015601436,0.021708276,-0.058038138,0.0046789995,0.06496689,-0.0042760363,0.02025445,0.03408822,0.050131664,-0.0043753353,0.039849006,0.006435245,-0.0002744733,0.0061930954,0.019537263,-0.008724507,0.021154063,-0.029094912,0.006180826,0.025161123,0.004582327,-0.009833078,-0.04618412,-0.0031133525,-0.025820328,0.017631918,-0.0071391524,-0.045595724,0.014177878,-0.010555058,0.038832076,-0.04585697,-0.014522429,-0.008203398,0