	 ('1d5e8dcb-3629-4259-b459-872de987b8e2'::uuid,'10-Guy','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a young man with a distinctive facial expression that has become iconic in internet culture. The image has a slightly grainy quality typical of early digital photography.

The subject is a young adult male with short, dark hair that appears slightly tousled. His face dominates the frame, capturing his expression in detail. The most striking feature is his facial expression, which can be described as a forced, uncomfortable smile. His eyes are slightly narrowed, and his brow is somewhat furrowed, giving the impression of internal conflict or discomfort despite the attempt to smile.

The lighting in the image is warm, likely from indoor lighting, casting a slightly yellow tone on the subject''s skin and the wall behind him. The background is simple - a plain wall that appears to be painted in a light, neutral color.

The young man is wearing what looks like a dark-colored tank top or sleeveless shirt. The edge of a blue object, possibly a drink container, is visible in the lower left corner of the frame.

This image has become a popular meme template known as "10 Guy" or "Really High Guy." It''s often used to express confusion, misunderstanding, or the kind of convoluted logic that might occur when someone is under the influence or extremely tired. The slightly dazed expression and forced smile make it particularly suited for captions describing nonsensical thoughts or actions.

