	 ('1628b2c8-7fd3-4a97-976b-d3295e9c610a'::uuid,'Third-World-Success-Kid','This meme template features a candid photograph of young children in what appears to be a rural African setting. The central focus is on a small child, likely a toddler, who is captured mid-motion in an energetic, dancing-like pose. The child''s expression is one of intense determination or excitement, with a slightly furrowed brow and open mouth, giving the impression of great enthusiasm or effort.

The child is wearing only a small red garment, possibly a loincloth or diaper, which stands out against their dark skin. Their arms are bent at the elbows and their legs are in a wide stance, suggesting movement or a dance-like action. The posture is dynamic and full of life, conveying a sense of joy and uninhibited expression.

Surrounding this central figure are parts of other children''s bodies, visible at the edges of the frame. This gives the scene a communal feeling, as if the central child is part of a larger group or celebration. The background shows a dusty or sandy ground, typical of a dry, rural environment, with some grass or vegetation visible in the distance.

The lighting in the image is natural and bright, suggesting it was taken outdoors during daylight hours. The colors are warm, dominated by earthy tones of brown and orange from the soil, contrasting with the deep black skin tones of the children.

This image has become a popular meme template due to the expressive and energetic pose of the central child, which often gets humorously paired with various captions or situations where someone might display similar enthusiasm or determination. The raw, unfiltered emotion and the child''s uninhibited body language make it a versatile template for expressing excitement, triumph, or intense engagement with a situation.','/memes/Third-World-Success-Kid.jpg',2,'{}','{"happy african child","african kids dancing"}',0.0,'[-0.010360233,-0.0017531762,-0.0063984604,0.019166917,0.012514873,-0.04152334,-0.030740894,-0.011841022,-0.011725213,0.014300838,-0.0042161983,0.0050694263,0.018938601,0.018795885,-0.012287952,-0.004259277,0.0043204846,-0.03756534,-0.025185043,-0.0033876554,-0.02861157,-0.001433231,-0.084200114,-0.02187515,0.06065315,0.065975145,0.00280379,3.754081e-05,0.05251669,0.040259954,-0.02812018,-0.0061604925,0.009440451,-0.022777239,-0.004425822,0.006837829,0.040668927,-0.040093023,-0.010981931,-0.035146628,0.022725847,-0.023092402,0.040147927,0.009023705,-0.029053347,-0.022374429,0.022786394,-0.0027762733,0.06491556,0.03360638,0.01937895,0.009812744,0.016014474,0.019521747,-0.0489786,-0.032227006,0.00925323,-0.023943838,0.008629707,0.022018954,0.022831915,0.011870035,0.013508285,-0.06764987,-0.05428117,-0.0068978234,-0.01698852,0.0087015685,-0.026514966,-0.045447312,0.013627893,0.018796278,-0.015915208,-0.014601555,-0.027973726,0.00091202254,-0.057440184,-0.01665816,0.03118553,0.021798566,0.04525059,0.0367389,0.025527207,-0.0366115,-0.02615176,0.00045975234,0.014714017,0.020890499,0.01470504,-0.021584665,-0.005320574,0.052552726,-0.031737804,-0.007374392,0.021486543,0.04129986,-0.0036835803,0.029267026,-0.02043746,0.027199296,0.011350521,0.026375059,-0.013528021,0.055754423,-0.049684584,0.006827573,0.013163781,-0.041031193,-0.034006897,-0.01774437,-2.9423927e-05,-0.0226284,-0.0064279954,-0.02026115,-0.024664095,0.032337993,0.01381884,0.051451687,-0.036288045,-0.0