	 ('f636c72a-6529-46e4-b1d0-f85ac470f9b6'::uuid,'First-World-Problems','This meme template features a close-up, emotionally charged image of a woman in a moment of distress or sorrow. The frame is tightly focused on her face, capturing intense feeling and vulnerability.

The woman''s eyes are closed, and her hand is raised to her forehead in a gesture that suggests she''s overwhelmed or trying to compose herself. Tears are visible on her cheek, glistening in the warm lighting that illuminates her skin. Her dark hair falls across part of her face, adding to the sense of dishevelment and emotional turmoil.

The image is shot with a shallow depth of field, keeping the woman''s face in sharp focus while the background blurs into a soft, neutral tone. This photographic technique draws all attention to the subject''s expression and the details of her emotional state.

The lighting in the image is soft and warm, creating gentle shadows that accentuate the contours of her face and the texture of her skin. This lighting adds a layer of intimacy and rawness to the scene, making the viewer feel as if they''re witnessing a private moment of vulnerability.

This template is often used in memes to express feelings of deep sadness, regret, or emotional pain. Its power lies in the universality of the human experience it captures – a moment of unguarded emotion that many can relate to. The image''s composition and emotional weight make it a versatile template for conveying complex feelings in a visually striking and immediately understandable way.','/memes/First-World-Problems.jpg',2,'{}','{fwp,"woman crying","crying woman","sad woman","crying lady"}',0.0,'[0.014153915,-0.0330284,0.0030920005,0.0058717728,-0.008414888,-0.070511565,-0.023217136,-0.023467125,-0.004752375,0.03216307,-0.021654364,-0.01232386,0.038017455,-0.0046103722,0.008645774,-0.0029216753,0.034850862,-0.017992128,-0.024670586,0.025003782,-0.021616682,-0.016922565,-0.07324442,-0.029591843,-0.008902992,0.05903814,0.021760894,-0.0027891167,0.0526172,0.019929364,-0.05021197,0.034172177,-0.007596153,-0.042396817,0.017120197,-0.026942875,-0.00076208625,-0.05101825,-0.03618166,-0.021732764,0.045160837,-0.01151129,0.033659246,-0.025251536,-0.020736504,-0.023235135,-0.005874276,-0.0025961683,0.043094162,-6.476951e-05,0.0043337527,-0.03210249,0.014146521,0.022925965,-0.014664366,-0.016678423,-0.0009802894,-0.010565447,-0.0032390042,0.008827526,0.042286463,0.00045875437,-0.022344323,-0.025346007,-0.028477931,-0.0012407586,-0.027444037,-0.014729433,-0.021303345,-0.041561946,0.0123389205,-0.0142542245,0.0072727795,-0.019852612,-0.03986033,-0.011382564,-0.021224277,-0.030317102,0.026876865,0.01582982,0.009290464,0.03237993,-0.008797413,0.015317606,0.002072428,-0.023822475,-0.018562056,0.014894517,0.008808797,-0.034568924,-0.012801021,0.050163105,-0.012721051,0.031830806,-0.0058898577,0.031319503,0.0042369687,0.016669588,-0.012577425,0.0292651,-0.034302425,0.048113193,-0.011475293,0.058809996,-0.031540845,0.013108327,0.021744752,0.01267446,-0.012452463,-0.06218699,-0.0018271082,-0.0319787,-0.036470126,-0.0026324848,-0.027833717,0.042121947,-0.014941226,0.044406362,-0.054