	 ('d9c07d81-9528-4166-acac-08438aae2a13'::uuid,'Be-Like-Bill','This meme template features a minimalist stick figure design set against a stark white background, creating a high-contrast, clean aesthetic. The image is framed by a thin black border, giving it a polished, contained look.

The central figure is a basic stick person, drawn with simple black lines. It consists of a circular head, a vertical line for the body, two angled lines for arms, and two longer angled lines for legs, creating a classic stick figure pose. The face of the figure is equally simple, with two small dots for eyes and a curved line forming a smile, conveying a cheerful, friendly expression.

What makes this image stand out is the addition of a detailed, realistic winter hat perched atop the stick figure''s head. The hat is a light gray or beige color, likely meant to represent a knit or wool texture. It has a snug, fitted style around the head and a small fold or brim at the bottom edge. The hat is topped with a vibrant red pom-pom, adding a pop of color to the otherwise monochromatic image.

The juxtaposition of the highly detailed, three-dimensional hat against the two-dimensional simplicity of the stick figure creates a humorous and visually interesting contrast. This contrast is often used in memes to highlight the addition of a single complex or sophisticated element to an otherwise basic scenario.

The stick figure''s cheerful expression, combined with its jaunty hat, suggests a sense of contentment or pride in this small fashion statement. This template could be used for memes about small improvements, simple joys, or the impact of minor changes on one''s outlook or appearance.

The overall composition, with the figure positioned slightly to the right of center, leaves ample space for text to be added, making it a versatile template for various meme concepts related to style, happiness, or simple pleasures.','/memes/Be-Like-Bill.jpg',2,'{}','{"bill the stick figure with a hat","this is bill"}',0.0,'[0.0027306215,-0.01872188,0.0043395762,-0.03316716,0.023119995,-0.05027603,-0.00033168512,0.0165687,-0.009228498,0.029654032,0.0111661395,0.018095346,0.04324738,-0.013794866,-0.016939549,0.020419272,-0.00040880003,-0.0017849046,-0.027623313,0.021058662,-0.02005415,-0.0019770877,-0.093207926,-0.031094495,-0.023833476,0.054643523,-0.019552162,-0.0012830539,0.07040334,0.032686356,-0.004208151,0.0005476204,0.010892396,-0.07876711,-0.013290736,-0.03225349,0.012168506,-0.047767613,0.01109826,-0.0056734798,0.04670648,-0.03270975,0.012993215,-0.005480342,-0.014802338,-0.026386987,-0.031634003,-0.0024677294,0.043614727,-0.036050595,0.021250335,-0.0118988855,0.037023783,0.013589993,-0.013558534,-0.0069654216,0.009253876,-0.027954211,-0.003223107,0.015592783,0.03529794,0.014696823,0.030005649,-0.051076785,-0.046231933,0.0044298577,-0.004045141,-0.015726134,-0.02382513,-0.004590839,-0.003291376,0.004628518,-0.00576852,-0.029149944,-0.02605188,0.025525352,-0.021918138,-0.040057354,0.017967243,0.027893629,0.019064493,0.049178477,-0.009863658,0.0022978329,-0.020478774,0.010597419,-0.006210444,0.021125184,0.035476778,-0.044522706,-0.019710775,0.035995245,-0.002272413,0.020304572,0.031322435,0.04160109,-0.014146349,0.056138653,-0.0251255,0.014695636,-0.017750585,0.07407548,-0.01470187,0.035713874,-0.03238797,-0.02597126,0.0051100343,0.008026299,-0.043904893,-0.015094757,0.008295456,-0.004172663,0.00044426252,0.016058696,-0.028486082,0.02674557,0.021316895,0.0416175,-0.035058167,-0.023753036,-0.03041332,-0.0015082016,-0.03519209,0.0065092077,-0.023901472,-0.012513087,0.002366887,0.033257816,-0.013250863,0.02356925,0.0176507,-0.0028665925,0.023828039,0.04235378,-0.