	 ('20f25a8b-df3b-4c69-b4aa-f8500e1fdccd'::uuid,'Two-Buttons','This meme template consists of two vertically stacked panels, creating a sequential narrative in a comic-style format.

The top panel shows a close-up view of two large, white rectangular buttons or panels mounted on what appears to be a control board or wall. Each white panel contains a prominent red circular button in its center. The red buttons are rendered with a slight shadow, giving them a three-dimensional appearance. A hand, visible only by its index finger, is shown reaching out to press one of the red buttons.

The bottom panel depicts the aftermath of the button press, focusing on a man''s face and upper body. The man is wearing a red shirt and is shown in a state of extreme distress or panic. His facial features are exaggerated in classic cartoon style, with wide, bulging eyes, a grimacing mouth, and profuse sweating indicated by multiple droplets flying from his face. His left hand is raised to his forehead in a gesture of dismay or regret.

The man''s expression conveys a sense of immediate regret or horror at the consequences of his action (presumably pressing the button in the first panel). The exaggerated style of the drawing emphasizes the comedic nature of the situation, making it ideal for meme usage where the buttons can represent difficult choices and the bottom panel shows the often regrettable outcome.

The artwork has a clean, simple style with bold lines and a limited color palette dominated by shades of blue and red. The bottom right corner of the image contains a watermark or signature reading "JAKE-CLARK.TUMBLR", indicating the original artist or source of the illustration.

This template is particularly effective for memes about difficult decisions, unintended consequences, or moments of instant regret, allowing users to label the buttons and contextualize the man''s reaction in various humorous scenarios.','/memes/Two-Buttons.jpg',2,'{}','{"2 red buttons","choice button","which button","daily struggle","hard choice to make","the daily struggle",decisions,"source decision button","what do i choose?","two blank buttons choice","press button hard choice"}',0.0,'[0.01612431,-0.034051016,-0.0057754912,0.008832235,0.015265751,-0.07188757,-0.02300922,-0.019406626,-0.012966577,0.07396563,0.012554298,0.019029869,0.027337505,-0.002479949,0.003214156,0.007823596,0.008475689,-0.018553667,-0.006790082,0.0051748343,-3.6233134e-05,-0.008192876,-0.07384999,-0.06807271,-0.0378754,0.01803025,0.00059892505,0.009119416,0.05003942,0.0323328,0.00035177305,0.0037242572,0.010193459,-0.05064439,0.012272063,0.005377598,0.023623046,-0.05313301,-0.018458594,-0.046260525,0.043968223,-0.037758857,0.022328395,-0.024082888,-0.024069972,-0.028827973,-0.031977292,0.021287693,0.022230798,0.0010714616,-0.010572979,-0.0050657075,0.0022554058,0.010022867,-0.018896068,-0.033171333,-0.039601322,-0.06781427,-0.0032676843,0.018790547,0.032257035,-0.0006993972,0.006014335,-0.069086656,-0.015525511,0.004921445,-0.032113694,-0.0055424417,-0.046416517,-0.007290593,0.0004425458,0.023001429,-0.0057268976,-0.016445728,-0.03364485,0.005727749,-0.023799637,-0.040354617,0.01721691,0.010328476,0.014467996,0.04491061,0.005265365,-0.017749151,-0.028161714,-0.025127769,0.0392763,0.017440218,-0.013358627,-0.038385652,0.0065587126,0.04064624,-0.0017875758,0.015099863,0.03910119,0.022020925,-0.0057733213,0.042400997,-0.02915625,-0.00051651226,0.022631701,0.025784971,-0.050663386,0.02587091,-0.03462327,0.004923986,0.058897763,0.0056427373,-0.04359584,-0.035648685,0.019432003,-0.02330375,-0.004863831,-0.01802428,-0.027309071,0.05069171,0.014951179,0.036931604,-0.038550828,-0.012919623,-0.045726