	 ('b23efc34-24b2-43c0-87da-40d0cea3a0f3'::uuid,'Jack-Sparrow-Being-Chased','This meme template features a dynamic scene from the popular "Pirates of the Caribbean" film franchise. The image captures a pivotal moment of high energy and excitement.

In the foreground, we see a flamboyantly dressed pirate character running through shallow water. He''s adorned in classic pirate attire - a loose white shirt, dark vest, and a red bandana wrapped around his head. His long, dark hair is adorned with various trinkets and beads, flying wildly as he runs. The character''s facial expression conveys a mix of determination and perhaps a hint of panic.

The pirate is caught mid-stride, creating a dramatic splash in the water around his feet. His arms are outstretched, adding to the sense of urgency in his movement. It appears he''s fleeing from something behind him.

In the background, we can see a large group of indistinct figures. These appear to be a horde of other characters, likely in pursuit of the main pirate. Their presence adds to the tension and excitement of the scene.

The setting seems to be a beach or shoreline, with a hazy, neutral-toned background that allows the action in the foreground to stand out vividly.

