	 ('811adbc2-fcc9-4bf9-9302-db45de916cad'::uuid,'Star-Wars-Yoda','This image features the iconic character Yoda from the Star Wars franchise. Yoda is a small, elderly alien creature known for his wisdom and mastery of the Force. In this close-up portrait, we see Yoda''s distinctive features in vivid detail.

Yoda has wrinkled, green skin with a texture that suggests both age and his alien nature. His large, expressive eyes are a warm brown color, conveying a sense of depth and ancient knowledge. His pointed ears, a hallmark of his species, stick out prominently from the sides of his head.

Yoda''s head is topped with wispy strands of white hair, adding to his appearance of great age and wisdom. His facial expression is gentle and slightly bemused, with the hint of a subtle smile playing at the corners of his mouth.

He is dressed in simple, rough-spun robes of a light beige color, befitting his humble and ascetic lifestyle. The clothing appears well-worn and frayed at the edges, emphasizing Yoda''s detachment from material concerns.

The background of the image is dark and out of focus, placing all emphasis on Yoda''s face and upper body. This creates a sense of intimacy and draws the viewer into Yoda''s wise and slightly mysterious gaze.

This image is often used in memes to convey wisdom, unexpected cleverness, or to humorously attribute sage-like qualities to mundane or ironic statements. The combination of Yoda''s alien appearance and his reputation for cryptic, backwards-structured speech makes him a rich source for internet humor and cultural references.','/memes/Star-Wars-Yoda.jpg',2,'{}','{"master yoda"}',0.0,'[0.03301579,-0.0026235888,0.017824035,-0.039449885,-0.0016933467,-0.006702501,-0.0042452747,-0.007957364,0.0026411416,-0.0012968873,0.005628252,-0.008853438,0.0114096,0.0009954959,-0.01931617,4.4620276e-05,0.00095039245,0.004438145,-0.04219299,-0.0009900833,-0.011437001,0.022875251,-0.06796859,0.013771832,0.03487927,0.04013919,-0.01562328,0.019139118,0.033140715,0.0013828509,-0.03804522,0.019374577,-8.467858e-05,-0.06734235,-0.015745524,-0.0034327137,0.02417134,-0.05124599,-0.0032932125,-0.04629792,0.04303896,-0.027919307,-0.0102673145,-0.026210854,-0.037406165,-0.0011680352,-0.014635316,-0.026116904,0.0028204545,-0.039033245,0.0050016255,-0.025619522,0.0028717087,0.023325346,0.019805307,-0.025889052,0.018170068,0.011733818,0.016148927,0.018694477,0.036967374,0.003497445,-0.003941135,-0.031855457,-0.06310469,0.029010797,0.002139431,0.0059749503,-0.0032485262,0.05202333,0.005842626,0.038770996,0.022368753,-0.010759619,-0.055454325,-0.023825258,0.010862171,0.0037771263,0.04518328,0.008748253,0.016718715,0.07030181,-0.040851805,0.004872992,-0.0075314953,-0.010585403,-0.0028702696,0.03148074,-0.013019484,-0.055569623,0.0021529233,0.07396748,0.0044335853,0.03562224,0.03084605,0.007029154,-0.029797783,0.017749414,0.00835155,0.015874095,-0.014616845,0.016248658,-0.016684154,0.034827437,-0.026293783,-0.020002805,-0.0147289,0.00028344983,-0.014605072,-0.034406476,0.060394485,-0.008412989,0.0069048163,-0.002220281,-0.020270368,-0.01438588,-0.02882568,0.04293655,-0.061703194,-0.031844813,-0.040785786,-0.011877255,-0.0025269946,0.016147662,0.006620247,-0.020755718,-0.023338065,0.03111636,0.005691308