	 ('0d07a13b-a3a3-40bc-8f48-23f51103b356'::uuid,'Disaster-Girl','This iconic meme template features a young girl in the foreground with a striking juxtaposition of chaos in the background. The girl, positioned in the right foreground, has shoulder-length brown hair and is looking directly at the camera with a mischievous smirk. Her expression is eerily calm and slightly pleased, contrasting dramatically with the scene behind her.

In the background, a house is engulfed in flames. The fire is intense, with bright orange flames visible through the windows and smoke billowing into the grey sky. The structure appears to be a single-story home, typical of suburban architecture. Firefighters can be seen in the mid-ground, their dark silhouettes stark against the bright flames. A fire truck is partially visible, identified by its number "38" and distinctive red color.

The setting seems to be a residential area, with the road visible in the foreground and hints of other houses or structures in the periphery. The overall atmosphere is one of emergency and destruction, making the girl''s calm demeanor all the more unsettling and darkly humorous.

This image has become a popular meme template often used to represent situations where someone remains calm or even pleased while chaos unfolds around them. It''s frequently captioned to comment on personal indifference to larger problems or to humorously depict causing mischief. The stark contrast between the child''s expression and the dramatic background has made this image a versatile and widely recognized meme in internet culture.','/memes/Disaster-Girl.jpg',3,'{}','{"evil girl fire","girl house on fire","house fire child","girl fire house","house burn little girl orphan","house burning"}',0.0,'[-0.023318492,-0.023001058,-0.01468839,0.044625126,0.030266196,-0.040000062,-0.040410332,0.007105439,0.014479346,0.02724924,0.011175297,0.0152230635,0.03294239,-0.010426987,-0.010248255,-0.0011105557,-0.017652543,-0.00025009582,-0.025181036,-0.007057296,0.024220595,-0.01481912,-0.07303851,-0.045678686,-0.009495295,0.043040022,0.02619869,-0.028391622,0.038433194,0.030968986,-0.028498711,-0.025769468,-0.022081014,-0.04534334,-0.0027712127,0.0097926995,0.04208747,-0.033444237,-0.024330383,-0.024379756,0.01163838,-0.0091721695,0.059111223,-0.030512555,-0.009950954,-0.024377063,-0.02200934,0.031581897,0.04957688,0.03541809,-0.0013795815,-0.022724574,0.055101015,0.024179379,-0.030367043,-0.023007665,0.002951727,0.015241591,0.028345957,0.03509082,0.024413615,-0.0069827233,-0.012890949,-0.035623178,-0.03866597,0.017406302,-0.00028354675,-0.012835839,-0.036988527,-0.00824805,-0.00038470278,0.026069993,-0.029914606,0.017785639,-0.027308494,0.021325259,-0.051675826,-0.00042014034,0.02623251,0.02564119,0.010626096,0.023657903,0.0092040915,-0.02656575,-0.022166738,-0.016691675,0.008236549,0.030820284,-0.017908897,-0.03661059,-0.016051294,0.04688396,-0.00088068395,0.012128414,0.008105014,0.037192784,0.0011787717,0.050351057,0.009210393,0.008174564,-0.0015350773,0.03591184,0.00770058,0.03852877,-0.055302966,-0.017018273,0.00972932,-0.029327402,-0.032036766,-0.029676234,-0.037049234,-0.