	 ('118d08f4-e50b-43bb-8377-db2825803fa4'::uuid,'Evil-Toddler','This meme template features a close-up shot of an adorable Asian toddler sitting on grass, exhibiting pure, unbridled joy. The child''s expression is the focal point of the image, showcasing a wide, infectious smile that causes their eyes to squint almost completely shut. Their chubby cheeks are pushed up, emphasizing the genuine delight radiating from their face.

The toddler is wearing a red and white plaid button-up shirt, giving them a casual, cute appearance that contrasts charmingly with their exuberant expression. Their hands are slightly raised and positioned in front of their chest, suggesting excited movement or gesticulation that accompanies their laughter.

The background is softly out of focus, showing a grassy area with hints of water in the distance, implying an outdoor setting like a park or backyard. This natural backdrop adds to the wholesome, cheerful atmosphere of the image.

The lighting appears natural, highlighting the child''s face and adding to the warm, joyful mood of the photograph. The composition is simple yet effective, centering on the child''s expressive face and allowing their happiness to dominate the frame.

