	 ('31e8ce5a-cffe-458a-a0cb-36765651f767'::uuid,'Evil-Kermit','This meme template features a juxtaposition of two iconic green characters, creating a humorous and somewhat ominous visual contrast. On the left side of the image is Kermit the Frog, the beloved Muppet character known for his friendly demeanor and optimistic outlook. Kermit is shown in his typical bright green felt texture, with his distinctive white collar and large, expressive eyes visible in profile.

Directly beside Kermit, on the right side of the image, is a darker, more sinister version that appears to be Kermit as well, but cloaked in a black hood reminiscent of a Sith Lord from Star Wars or a mysterious dark entity. This "Dark Kermit" is mostly obscured by the hood, with only the green of his face barely visible within the shadowy confines of the cloak.

The background of the image is a muted, dark grey, which enhances the dramatic contrast between the two figures. The lighting in the scene is low and atmospheric, giving the entire image a moody, almost noir-like quality.

This template is often used to represent the duality of decision-making, with the regular Kermit symbolizing one''s conscience or good intentions, while the hooded version represents temptation, bad ideas, or the "evil" inner voice. The stark visual contrast between the familiar, friendly Kermit and his dark doppelganger creates a powerful and instantly recognizable meme format that resonates with themes of inner conflict, moral dilemmas, and the struggle between right and wrong choices in everyday situations.

The image''s composition, with the two figures facing each other in profile, suggests a confrontation or internal dialogue, adding to its effectiveness as a template for expressing conflicting thoughts or impulses in a humorous way. This meme has become a popular way for internet users to humorously illustrate the internal struggles and temptations faced in various life situations.','/memes/Evil-Kermit.jpg',2,'{}','{"kermit me to me","kermit inner me","sith kermit","kermit dark side"}',0.0,'[0.02163536,-0.05283904,0.022687608,0.022024898,-0.016356632,-0.07850332,-0.03627366,0.00434387,-0.06310086,0.056433376,-0.0041097654,-0.017531667,0.054637127,0.0042317095,-0.010182535,0.030199384,-0.012224682,-0.019758033,-0.011275394,-0.022072604,0.0038229316,0.014914237,-0.058425006,-0.0027351317,-0.0027871365,0.05676225,-0.010494861,0.009608905,0.071818314,0.004892827,0.01642234,0.011040733,0.02392556,-0.05664274,-0.0042784917,-0.00692258,0.012676133,-0.033719916,0.0055460185,-0.01706827,0.02763783,-0.025305869,0.01520216,-0.04072904,-0.022291377,-0.0034902731,-0.022376768,0.011555081,0.01602203,-0.012998408,0.0024738796,-0.012266946,0.016869482,-0.00476101,-0.033807337,-0.01362167,-0.0058416687,-0.01415926,-0.015660476,0.01651397,0.024959171,-0.009227909,0.011210534,-0.06016958,-0.020831214,-0.012837852,-0.028816815,0.002359246,-0.034594335,0.0009281621,0.0022660678,0.026669502,-0.014350592,0.0005698549,-0.013106181,-0.011548515,-0.028615313,-0.011177014,0.0198209,0.011329908,0.017494285,0.016128007,-0.022677034,-0.012392159,-0.024652923,-0.0151097635,-0.0057320683,0.024280615,0.02113892,-0.020138768,-0.0050971066,0.074432425,-0.0022358147,0.016140709,0.014772294,0.038171157,0.008608179,0.02306183,-0.031410962,-0.0043242704,0.0034404274,0.014853824,-0.04400993,0.04753248,-0.04330619,-0.016464528,0.040245045,0.010246306,-0.03190874,-0.007495386,0.019783545,-0.028550765,0.03542595,-0.011948549,-0.024327544,0.017043218,0.00051407283,0.06340991,-0.045955624,0.00453083,-0.0361366