	 ('cec20f8f-f8c4-43cb-890d-0c069835661f'::uuid,'I-Should-Buy-A-Boat-Cat','This meme template features a humorous and surreal scene of a cat posed as if it were a human having a morning routine. The image is set in what appears to be a bright, sunlit room with white curtains visible in the background, creating a soft, domestic atmosphere.

The focal point of the image is a tabby cat sitting upright at a table, positioned as if it were reading a newspaper. The cat is wearing a blue collar or necktie, giving it a comically professional appearance. Its paws are placed on the table, one seemingly holding the newspaper open.

In front of the cat is a white coffee mug on a saucer, completing the illusion of a person starting their day with coffee and the news. The newspaper appears to be a broadsheet, folded open as one would typically read it.

The composition of the image is framed to emphasize the absurdity of the scene, with the cat occupying the right side of the frame and the newspaper and coffee mug on the left. The lighting suggests early morning, with a soft glow filtering through the curtains.

This meme template plays on the anthropomorphization of pets, particularly cats, imagining them engaging in human activities. It''s often used to comment on morning routines, work life, or current events, with text typically added to either the newspaper or as captions to represent the cat''s thoughts or reactions to the "news."

The image''s quirky nature makes it versatile for various humorous contexts, allowing for creative captions that contrast the serious pose of the "businessman" cat with absurd or relatable situations. The cat''s slightly aloof expression adds to the comedic effect, as if it''s seriously contemplating whatever is supposed to be in the newspaper.','/memes/I-Should-Buy-A-Boat-Cat.jpg',2,'{}','{"sophisticated cat","fancy cat","newspaper cat","cat suit 1","morning realisation cat","cat newspaper","investment cat newspaper"}',0.0,'[0.020303212,-0.011539231,0.02314336,-0.0020358441,0.0033801538,-0.049197774,-0.011433092,0.00897664,0.01624504,0.05693185,-0.0038531816,0.011850002,0.0053719305,0.026452878,-0.028662901,-0.028533377,-0.0036323962,-0.027864372,-0.011151518,0.028286014,-0.001373176,0.025255969,-0.08894997,-0.032717012,-0.016501447,0.06499897,-0.005152662,0.0031029617,0.05774305,0.030961215,0.023592588,-0.0045838407,0.019704608,-0.036571786,0.012792377,0.00039469078,0.03832944,-0.030700764,0.016603393,-0.023642072,0.05423475,-0.044319987,0.053303048,-0.035280015,-0.011420984,-0.025706256,-0.023518424,0.015067407,0.041528195,-0.024742974,0.015651623,-0.020682923,0.011416036,-0.0036272355,-0.02971142,-0.0028362346,-0.051688462,-0.017358145,0.012090159,0.026581263,0.026681757,0.016001143,0.0016263758,-0.045032755,-0.0115865,0.015588679,-0.002057741,-0.0039278567,-0.03280624,-0.031154629,-0.017710505,0.024382545,-0.011471846,0.0023833043,-0.057148065,-0.026118768,-0.030905355,-0.028023286,-0.010624487,0.05162529,-0.0097767925,0.010488278,-0.0106823975,-0.025229156,-0.026663153,0.0067348913,0.024309672,0.050542943,0.0043295193,-0.04094273,0.026815703,0.04379607,0.0116174035,0.004325259,0.004668591,0.03337315,-0.03586043,0.06307144,0.009750105,0.03718745,-0.028762517,0.04392862,-0.022728512,0.024361791,-0.03206156,-0.0075938455,0.036910854,-0.04713218,-0.052288167,-0.008751152,-0.016963191,-0.002660619,0.007040749,0.008676961,-0.0054982686,0.037853207,0.013699069,0.0698