	 ('0f8e63e4-a010-4f7e-a5f5-4e7192622091'::uuid,'Batman-Slapping-Robin','This meme template is derived from a classic comic book panel, featuring the iconic superhero Batman in a humorous interaction. The image is styled in the bold, simplified aesthetic of vintage comics, with vibrant colors and strong outlines.

The scene depicts Batman, recognizable by his distinctive pointed-ear cowl and gray costume, engaged in what appears to be a heated argument or confrontation with another character. Batman is shown from the side, his arm outstretched as if he''s just delivered a slap to the face of the other figure.

The recipient of Batman''s apparent slap is seen from behind, wearing a yellow outfit. This character''s posture and the motion lines around their head suggest they''ve just been struck, adding a dynamic element to the static image.

The background is a solid, bright red color, typical of the bold palettes used in older comic books. Above the characters are two empty speech bubbles, leaving room for custom text to be added - a key feature of this meme format.

This template is often used online to humorously depict scenarios where one party (represented by Batman) is forcefully correcting or chastising another (the slapped character). The empty speech bubbles allow meme creators to insert their own dialogue, making the template highly versatile for a wide range of jokes or commentary.

The exaggerated, almost slapstick nature of the interaction, combined with the serious demeanor typically associated with Batman, creates a perfect canvas for ironic or absurdist humor. This juxtaposition of the grave superhero engaged in such a comically mundane act of violence is a large part of what makes this image so memorable and widely used as a meme template.','/memes/Batman-Slapping-Robin.jpg',2,'{}','{"batman and robin","shut up hater"}',0.0,'[0.010463766,-0.0052501895,0.0344237,-0.004238799,-0.0172117,-0.07624896,-0.020055173,-0.03296712,-0.0046308064,0.045081504,-0.005783793,0.028197223,0.04908096,-0.0073009273,0.0099006025,-0.0032604355,-0.03225283,-0.00285342,-0.020103417,0.028978467,-0.0033356715,-0.009195113,-0.073073424,-0.03556395,-0.002442445,0.038862757,-0.016064944,0.0077070515,0.054460607,0.0319888,0.004428732,-0.016921466,0.03370243,-0.049448412,0.009146306,-0.036836054,0.007505131,-0.046475697,-0.000793814,0.022504278,0.028622828,-0.020471107,-0.0009055545,-0.0068031773,-0.018681593,-0.011766766,-0.011848419,0.023499671,-0.007845228,-0.04201871,-0.0025833694,-0.018954217,0.018006394,0.01780792,-0.030926507,-0.044286918,-0.021424003,-0.013459067,0.01269678,0.00730893,0.033922773,-0.03491691,0.0022093898,-0.04159594,-0.038168233,-0.014985777,-0.022961948,0.022977162,-0.007898869,0.01558083,-0.006990017,0.054086525,0.009824434,-0.03587155,-0.072961055,-0.0140655935,-0.017473554,-0.04036842,0.013525388,0.0060703503,0.014789798,0.052864548,0.011703272,-0.027766066,-0.0076251826,-0.036091797,0.032542404,0.020212356,0.011954801,-0.04000248,0.005307289,0.07435213,0.0150356665,0.051059987,0.029510688,0.035640668,-0.014542603,0.06312344,-0.003651323,0.017078511,0.0014412627,0.0666486,-0.049576234,0.04571694,-0.0054528913,-0.0027228012,0.028324947,-0.040667903,-0.012054727,-0.007795934,0.011683354,0.0057720696,0.031555586,-0.016947048,-0.020971032,0.0035481108,0.01997118,0.050448112,-0.016657256,-0.016605789,-0.00013057028,-0.021355163,-0.037859857,-0.0