	 ('a7dbe41f-a047-49ad-b7f3-24d9502c10b6'::uuid,'Captain-Picard-Facepalm','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man in what appears to be a futuristic or sci-fi setting, likely from a television series or film. The subject is seated and wearing a distinctive red uniform with a high collar, suggestive of a military or official rank in a space-faring organization.

The most striking aspect of the image is the man''s pose: he has his right hand covering his face, palm pressed against his forehead in a classic "facepalm" gesture. This body language typically conveys frustration, exasperation, or embarrassment. The man''s head is bald, and only part of his face is visible behind his hand.

The background is neutral and somewhat out of focus, showing what seems to be the interior of a spacecraft or advanced facility, with light-colored walls and subtle geometric patterns. The lighting is even, giving the scene a clean, institutional feel.

This image has become an iconic representation of secondhand embarrassment, disbelief, or reaction to something profoundly disappointing or foolish. The "facepalm" gesture is universally recognized and transcends language barriers, making this meme template particularly versatile for expressing reactions to various situations.

The framing of the shot, focusing tightly on the subject''s upper body and face, emphasizes the emotional impact of the gesture. The bold red of the uniform contrasts sharply with the muted background, drawing all attention to the man''s reaction.

This meme template is frequently used online to react to news, comments, or situations that are viewed as particularly misguided, illogical, or worthy of derision. Its popularity stems from its ability to succinctly convey a complex emotional response through a single, powerful image.','/memes/Captain-Picard-Facepalm.jpg',2,'{}','{"star trek face palm",pickard}',0.0,'[0.027433543,-0.03400603,0.030286707,0.045012776,0.026377728,-0.056630205,-0.022076929,-0.03157207,-0.018187081,0.021926284,0.018740866,-0.007913277,0.01917873,-0.00287572,-0.004280127,-0.024651743,0.02863113,-0.022702657,-0.023423439,-0.010817087,-0.020643946,-0.006561167,-0.072559044,-0.04582808,-0.008407653,0.06281845,0.008412945,0.02556944,0.047465313,0.035589755,-0.0019817404,-0.01012174,0.0029590917,-0.04046884,0.004898844,-0.0154394,0.038145248,-0.049269024,-0.043839227,-0.034056142,0.044173144,-0.012305701,0.01788418,-0.034047563,-0.014790832,-0.00241731,0.0034691151,0.003928012,0.032558523,-0.0010437076,0.002366816,0.007904277,-0.022927327,0.03701457,-0.03691442,-0.046676237,-0.019958,-0.0037072995,-0.005381294,0.02488883,0.060753092,0.007231629,-0.023607709,-0.020562818,-0.02634352,0.01361188,0.0086515425,-0.0009328443,-0.032753352,0.009783988,-0.0056859227,-0.009759697,0.02767801,-0.023846392,-0.02990629,-0.00961754,-0.028370587,0.00021143896,0.026346466,-0.014098973,0.04320411,0.08639479,-0.004672176,-0.019946741,0.0037830032,-0.004929996,0.045359395,0.05810227,0.0045202305,-0.04441163,0.005851239,0.0553685,-0.02486283,0.010776363,-0.014056814,0.031549495,-0.023565149,0.06341072,-0.02008597,-0.00482518,-0.023086427,0.07267272,-0.037864216,0.045922644,-0.027108777,0.012857287,0.017490586,-0.00335622,0.003454519,-0.032576974,0.015389465,0.0017549812,-0.0035131436,-0.017928012,-0.024638202,0.012195821,-0.014845732,0.021674592,-0.028340196,0.011784797,-0.039522447,-0.023133634,0.0140846055,-0.0011265824,-0.01657823,-0.012480301,0.03792263,0.026281394,-0.013802766,0.003635031,0.01448157,-0.041995