	 ('4be9b281-3163-48b2-8759-4d82a4f264aa'::uuid,'Grandma-Finds-The-Internet','This meme template features an elderly woman sitting at a computer, peering intently at the screen with a look of surprised confusion. The image captures a moment of technological bewilderment that resonates with many people''s experiences of older generations encountering modern technology.

The woman has short, curly white hair and wears glasses, which she''s adjusting with one hand as she leans in close to the monitor. Her expression is one of wide-eyed astonishment, with her mouth slightly open, suggesting she''s seen something unexpected or perplexing on the screen. She''s wearing a light blue blouse with a white collar, giving her a neat, grandmotherly appearance.

The setting appears to be a home office or living space, with a yellow wall visible in the background. The warm lighting and intimate framing create a sense of peeking into a private moment of discovery or confusion.

This image has become a popular meme template to humorously depict situations where someone, particularly from an older generation, encounters something surprising, confusing, or shocking online. It''s often used to represent reactions to new internet trends, social media phenomena, or any scenario where there''s a generational gap in understanding technology or current events.

The power of this meme lies in its relatability and the gentle humor it evokes. It taps into the universal experience of navigating an increasingly digital world, especially for those who didn''t grow up with such technology. The woman''s exaggerated expression makes the image versatile for a wide range of captions and contexts, allowing it to be adapted to many different humorous scenarios.','/memes/Grandma-Finds-The-Internet.jpg',2,'{}','{}',0.0,'[0.019281786,-0.038411982,-0.01396342,0.03794025,0.0004509918,-0.039519932,-0.008793341,0.009402899,0.012397931,0.04735188,0.0040066084,-0.01571236,0.0554239,0.012324657,0.00090110657,-0.0027964802,0.004749551,0.005145652,-0.02625439,0.020506993,0.0009836992,0.016566578,-0.08050708,-0.04326756,-0.039550535,0.052752957,0.003999064,0.019661885,0.06654837,0.018767036,0.007048646,0.007609414,-0.027207367,-0.03819974,-0.0058169197,-0.0139162615,0.015263886,-0.032189894,-0.05261042,-0.046933983,0.016563062,-0.020223012,0.021414144,-0.022895094,-0.049834058,-0.033268057,0.010870462,-0.01207365,0.040567804,-0.0035495388,0.018321458,-0.02771781,-0.007175436,0.011015065,-0.009955755,-0.046991087,-0.028514335,-0.014759189,-0.012036911,0.015613005,0.05260577,0.018906094,0.014838317,-0.042017415,-0.004318463,0.02608588,-0.0017603227,-0.007584246,-0.030660233,0.0029130294,0.011853854,0.008812895,-0.014822906,-0.030306883,-0.06388723,0.013830902,-0.024547681,0.028714703,-0.027204026,0.019389948,-8.21564e-05,0.015434865,-0.031147745,-0.015077226,-0.010140068,-0.030878205,0.020401191,0.033074893,0.0042210277,-0.025626779,-0.0012147725,0.036171652,-0.009098794,0.019867696,0.012345706,0.047761366,-0.006102347,0.023954557,0.005214697,0.031536803,-0.021509409,0.03852915,-0.014833203,0.058524676,-0.022245482,0.010307708,0.024183739,-0.006896323,-0.05013142,-0.045857728,-0.0029713244,-0.025166957,-0.006838954,0.011111783,-0.023847086,0.044082016,-0.006551895,0.04398825,-0.03487423,-0.0105907405,-0.08080761,-0.017573465,-0.033522666,-0.011890526