	 ('90c53d2e-3478-4d5d-8669-c54a519edb24'::uuid,'Doge','This image features the iconic "Doge" meme, which has become one of the most recognizable and beloved meme templates on the internet. The subject is a Shiba Inu dog, a Japanese breed known for its fox-like appearance and spirited personality.

The close-up shot focuses on the dog''s face, capturing its distinct features in vivid detail. The Shiba Inu has a golden-tan fur coat that appears soft and fluffy, gradually transitioning to a cream color around its muzzle and cheeks. Its pointed ears are perked up, giving the dog an alert and attentive expression.

What makes this image particularly memeable are the dog''s eyes and subtle facial expression. The Shiba Inu''s eyes are large, round, and dark, seeming to gleam with a mix of curiosity and mild concern. They''re slightly widened, giving the dog an innocent, almost surprised look that people often interpret as confusion or gentle judgment.

The dog''s mouth is closed, but there''s a slight upturn at the corners that creates the impression of a subtle, knowing smirk. This ambiguous expression is part of what makes the image so versatile for meme creation – it can be interpreted as smugness, skepticism, or quiet amusement depending on the context.

The background of the image is blurred but appears to be a warm, yellowish tone that complements the dog''s fur color. This soft focus keeps the attention squarely on the Shiba Inu''s expressive face.

The "Doge" meme became wildly popular for its use with superimposed text in broken English, often using the Comic Sans font. However, even without text, this image has become instantly recognizable in internet culture, often used to convey a range of emotions from mild confusion to ironic detachment.','/memes/Doge.jpg',2,'{}','{"Shiba Inu","ironic doge"}',0.0,'[0.019206835,0.008422189,0.01341104,0.0037174115,0.0027211565,-0.013812414,-0.006654991,-0.0044093523,0.010458531,0.046202406,0.0002680729,0.022357354,0.026365837,0.022762386,-0.033566356,-0.005200626,0.007157165,-0.030836029,-0.053142436,0.002534037,0.0059487596,0.01116906,-0.06681767,-0.029427784,0.03869821,0.062981986,0.025611259,-0.004306811,0.064845584,0.010368064,0.0007707,0.044902507,0.0066284975,-0.048558205,0.0010237416,-0.041951105,0.009180607,-0.0152644,-0.011290391,-0.043585155,0.060458455,-0.020231739,0.04549711,-0.026990337,-0.05294278,-0.016708586,-0.06571192,-0.01348754,0.014365129,-0.022816403,0.015221134,0.025187397,0.010267792,0.010900259,-0.018464768,-0.029366732,-0.008049875,-0.035203107,-0.020589925,0.0018269047,0.03967326,0.008342956,0.032640297,-0.03495192,-0.0329728,0.019614944,-0.02982438,-0.016093887,-0.021687327,0.012884861,0.025887689,-0.003370322,-0.037587322,-0.022183869,-0.037760478,-0.015293619,-0.0049645444,0.012561585,0.002081754,0.019094693,0.017941045,0.037794214,0.012429697,-0.033770904,-0.014070163,-0.031021906,0.033921357,0.036466096,0.009130572,-0.0023050215,-0.027354991,0.060516514,-0.008703498,0.01945047,-0.0006775871,0.02602189,0.011702988,0.021174071,0.012264258,0.009099692,-0.024896108,0.03456645,-0.01171474,0.04462031,-0.039574586,-0.0052216984,-0.0059230747,0.011711586,-0.035197895,-0.014879455,0.0013395958,-0.04687414,-0.0053705927,0.00731777,-0.008840503,0.0019447444,-0.040181022,0.0923887,-0.04636535,-0.010259364,-0.06922059,-0.015756318,-0.005975587,0.015017447,0.007847594,-0.012392195,-0.0064850296,0.043992054,-0.025248723,0.030755524,0.005527032,-0.02698627