	 ('7ae32236-5fab-46d0-b85b-27877c396d51'::uuid,'Futurama-Fry','This meme template features a close-up portrait of an animated character from the popular TV show Futurama. The character has distinctive spiky orange hair that stands up in a flame-like shape, with two points at the front resembling small horns. His face is drawn in a simple, cartoonish style with a prominent nose and jutting chin.

The character''s expression is one of skepticism or suspicion, with his eyes narrowed and his brow slightly furrowed. His mouth is drawn in a straight line, giving him a deadpan or unimpressed look. This expression has made the image particularly useful for memes expressing doubt, confusion, or a questioning attitude.

The character is wearing a red jacket or shirt over a white collar, visible at the neck. The background is a muted blue-gray color with diagonal lines suggesting a wall or interior setting, which is typical of the show''s futuristic aesthetic.

The image is cropped to focus solely on the character''s face and upper body, emphasizing his expression and making it ideal for reaction memes. The animation style is distinctively that of Futurama, with bold outlines and flat colors characteristic of the show''s visual design.

This particular frame has become iconic in internet culture, often used to convey a moment of suspicion, disbelief, or when someone is trying to process information that seems dubious or confusing. The character''s skeptical look has made this image a go-to reaction for many online users when they want to express doubt or a "not sure if..." sentiment in a humorous way.','/memes/Futurama-Fry.jpg',2,'{}','{"Not sure if X or Y","Skeptical Fry","blue futurama fry","not sure if...","confused fry","not sure if - futurama fry",suspicious}',0.0,'[0.051013906,-0.044095393,0.016990583,0.027752412,0.03915864,-0.061566908,0.005117505,0.00023859338,-0.013130356,0.07020816,0.019417308,-0.021781215,0.07047904,0.01580012,-0.036244623,-0.023627872,0.019210389,-0.00031689188,-0.010833393,0.014232756,-0.019839242,0.0153330555,-0.06583168,-0.010504417,-0.021250013,0.0369296,-0.0015582343,-0.030825807,0.044281963,0.007100189,0.006235237,-0.027553339,-0.033548865,-0.041612063,-0.0059973574,0.0012218893,0.033766612,-0.018942151,-0.029788462,-0.05602332,0.040041808,-0.019626452,0.010275957,-0.029094918,-0.03258635,-0.032474473,-0.036011852,-0.000791502,0.010942172,0.0057526524,-0.0013323572,0.006429314,0.016040329,0.021503186,-0.03050609,-0.06729127,-0.0063366434,0.017510168,-0.004119908,0.028742988,0.03726089,0.033015985,-0.017848242,-0.035443366,-0.03838214,0.039358377,-0.031468954,-0.010589429,-0.018955665,0.016676078,0.017394004,0.02826156,0.007454698,-0.0013179507,-0.06855684,0.00469969,-0.009992906,-0.017386753,0.04947642,0.007374434,0.03541961,0.045682088,-0.045737375,-0.034093853,0.0105699785,-0.013893159,0.022982236,0.03276376,0.0087915035,-0.038490575,-0.014195161,0.048002597,0.007310739,0.011856668,0.015230366,0.026032142,-0.015769457,0.064795926,-0.0054625636,-0.0067796474,-0.016388137,0.06278902,-0.027255738,0.01988597,-0.012214147,0.0081942445,0.006861275,0.008235774,-0.034305364,-0.030476553,-0.0061613075,-0.022320978,-0.006497256,0.0010571455,-0.044212,0.01424888,-0.0183673