	 ('5c219c9e-3bbd-422a-8efc-8b6ffefee8cd'::uuid,'And-everybody-loses-their-minds','This meme template features a close-up shot of a character in clown-like makeup, clearly inspired by the iconic portrayal of the Joker from the Batman film franchise. The image is framed in a cinematic widescreen format, suggesting it''s a still from a movie.

The character dominates the frame, wearing stark white face paint with exaggerated red lipstick smeared across their mouth, extending into a gruesome smile. Their eyes are heavily shadowed, giving them a sunken, intense appearance. The character''s hair appears disheveled and tinged green, though it''s mostly out of frame.

They are wearing a white collared shirt or jacket, which contrasts sharply with the dramatic makeup. The character''s expression is one of exasperation or frustration, with their eyes tightly closed and their mouth slightly open as if in mid-speech or exclamation. Their hands are raised on either side of their face, fingers splayed, in a gesture that suggests they''re trying to explain something emphatically or express extreme emotion.

The background is blurry and muted, focusing all attention on the character''s expressive face and hands. The lighting is dramatic, creating shadows that enhance the character''s unsettling appearance.

This image is often used in memes to express frustration, exasperation, or the feeling of trying to explain something obvious to someone who doesn''t understand. It captures a moment of intense emotion that resonates with many online users when trying to convey complex feelings or situations in a visually striking and instantly recognizable way.','/memes/And-everybody-loses-their-minds.jpg',2,'{}','{"Heath Ledger Joker from The Dark Knight","joker lose mind"}',0.0,'[0.0345591,-0.038146887,-0.015497103,-0.0070447735,0.013745833,-0.08590949,-0.008303164,-0.018949023,-0.023704616,0.046780124,-0.00043664384,-0.01755282,0.06117987,-0.02086228,0.016953256,-0.0008272672,-0.00094817416,-0.025993232,-0.026027115,0.027263762,-0.011365789,0.02663086,-0.0589997,-0.05915597,0.0055071544,0.040642377,0.007924129,-0.010485153,0.02208514,0.018183373,-0.016065856,0.002218983,0.0038274545,-0.053528197,0.026174765,0.012044537,0.028066615,-0.05691219,-0.0061888467,-0.021055626,0.047321435,-0.015345111,0.01105407,-0.018752556,-0.0224239,-0.01726873,-0.04311555,0.0023643563,0.015428043,-0.016585095,-0.016789876,-0.04022569,0.011909111,0.021717723,-0.018263934,-0.0470079,0.006154677,0.014072598,0.0035093792,0.0007613981,0.0524927,-0.009792941,0.008544357,-0.049762294,-0.048178602,0.009815088,-0.020618722,0.0109149525,-0.02422905,0.013765693,0.0009795971,0.038403805,0.016827986,-0.0045716353,-0.08121583,-0.036091704,-0.033863686,-0.045734152,0.03301379,0.010406827,0.01626312,0.031440556,-0.009813775,-0.011827731,-0.034641735,-0.017500501,0.01941726,0.024927447,0.0066212974,-0.03242933,0.0041310275,0.06962805,0.014627776,0.05516511,0.008246816,0.058581598,-0.008827027,0.03642922,0.0025607082,0.015273574,0.0043172045,0.04151901,-0.04466048,0.06435044,-0.017261166,0.011376493,0.025893364,0.0056868335,-0.032370776,-0.017970907,0.026848044,-0.033273086,0.02395214,-0.015226527,-0.0426888,0.011103473,-0.0002866712,0.048613172,-0.049640298,-0.021726726,-0.007856433,-0.0382909,-0.030483702,-0.033278