	 ('42bf06d3-fdb9-47a1-97a2-86dc7a8e79c6'::uuid,'Mocking-Spongebob','This meme template features a comical scene from the popular animated TV series SpongeBob SquarePants. The image captures SpongeBob in a moment of exaggerated, comical distress or confusion.

SpongeBob, the main character, is depicted in his iconic yellow, porous appearance resembling a kitchen sponge. His usually square shape is distorted, with his face stretched and contorted into an expression of bewilderment or shock. His large, bulging blue eyes are wide open and slightly misaligned, enhancing the sense of disorientation.

SpongeBob''s mouth is open in an oval shape, suggesting he might be in mid-exclamation or gasp. His body is twisted at an odd angle, with one arm raised awkwardly, adding to the overall impression of confusion or alarm. His other arm is barely visible, contributing to the off-kilter composition.

The background hints at the familiar setting of SpongeBob''s pineapple house, with a hint of blue wall and what appears to be part of a picture frame or window in the upper right corner. The floor is a simple green, typical of the show''s underwater scenes.

This particular frame likely comes from a moment in the show where SpongeBob is reacting to something unexpected or shocking, captured at the peak of his exaggerated response. The extreme facial expression and body language make this image perfect for memes expressing confusion, surprise, or an over-the-top reaction to various situations.

The image''s low resolution and slightly blurred quality add to its charm as a meme template, giving it a nostalgic feel reminiscent of early 2000s animation and internet culture. This template is often used to convey feelings of intense bewilderment, shock, or comical overreaction in online conversations and social media posts.','/memes/Mocking-Spongebob.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob mock","spongebob chicken","retarded spongebob","sarcastic spongebob","spongebob stupid","spongebob derp","spongebob bird","spongebob mocking face"}',0.0,'[0.039252315,-0.016754413,-0.0010284651,0.008795629,0.02091683,-0.021241654,0.008552567,-0.018732648,0.018633813,0.04123591,0.016954504,-0.023827696,0.03405561,0.00801386,-0.012245558,-0.012774327,-0.026355863,-0.0428691,-0.048054136,0.031921573,0.007867378,-0.028541554,-0.030519182,-0.018078486,-0.025554506,0.05442676,0.013110182,-0.0061647925,0.04428244,0.0006276487,0.019747263,0.00055544457,-0.016121995,-0.031315506,0.032879174,0.012656693,0.036911473,-0.064355955,-0.003833199,-0.041515015,0.031897034,-0.038194768,0.021023246,-0.0147623615,-0.010924532,-0.016129449,-0.014796474,0.007171173,0.024435896,-0.00784184,0.031140368,-0.011866937,0.01952402,0.040109925,-0.023749761,-0.050231818,-0.013752818,-2.5857476e-05,0.004929319,0.010044,0.020008987,0.018463288,-0.019847084,-0.05879541,-0.03236516,-0.002911515,-0.01789742,-0.042813063,-0.014914941,0.00415687,-0.017938772,0.018243728,0.015475028,-0.029822856,-0.042480927,0.0074225706,-0.050838567,-0.020076968,0.016087921,0.004545038,0.026631774,0.05248998,0.0226057,-0.04810095,-0.0154049685,-0.03658161,0.043655097,0.024256468,0.018475793,-0.040652834,-0.032457154,0.07737895,0.0250849,0.03292086,0.0011094153,0.029433865,0.010472326,0.048625816,0.034981098,0.007825163,0.010790448,0.065768436,-0.0013621901,0.046376165,-0.010601572,0.02806586,0.022384655,0.03148171,-0.05954218,-0.021498766,0.029336913,-0.0050355396,0.028541338,-0.025764218,-0.022844044,0.020629473,-0.006656343,0.07144458,-0.0540