	 ('75f4c3db-1217-4906-a364-33592a5bd979'::uuid,'Back-In-My-Day','This meme template features a close-up portrait of an elderly man with a stern, confrontational expression. He is dressed formally in a dark suit, white shirt, and dark tie, topped with a black bowler hat, giving him the appearance of someone from an earlier era, perhaps the early to mid-20th century.

The man''s face is the focal point of the image, showing deeply etched wrinkles that speak to his advanced age. His eyes are narrowed and intense, peering over a pair of small, round spectacles that sit low on his nose. His mouth is set in a grimace, with his lips pulled back slightly, adding to his disapproving demeanor.

Most notably, the man is pointing his finger directly at the viewer in an accusatory or admonishing gesture. This pointing finger, combined with his stern expression, creates a sense of being scolded or lectured by a strict authority figure.

The background is a plain, neutral color, keeping all attention on the man''s expressive face and gesture. The lighting highlights the contours of his face, emphasizing his aged features and the intensity of his expression.

This image is often used in memes to represent moments of accusation, judgment, or when invoking the voice of an older, more conservative generation criticizing modern behaviors or attitudes. The combination of the man''s age, formal attire, and confrontational pose makes it a powerful template for expressing disapproval or for humorously personifying outdated or curmudgeonly viewpoints.','/memes/Back-In-My-Day.jpg',2,'{}','{"grumpy old man pointing"}',0.0,'[0.03668009,-0.030111311,0.015370119,0.019709101,0.004549154,-0.019832859,-0.035623543,-0.01574861,-0.007630548,0.04186648,0.01093025,-0.03571985,0.05070441,-0.012951349,0.028864708,-0.0033940363,-0.00035858905,-0.0018254493,0.0069091674,0.021458602,0.008400838,0.009242243,-0.05253312,-0.06589875,0.016468424,0.06651225,-0.03646438,0.029632842,0.04504105,0.0075925537,-2.4194309e-05,-0.0031781443,-0.011455614,-0.048687186,-0.020885564,-0.041879736,0.02682283,-0.0871888,-0.0013592703,-0.0136602465,0.035769053,-0.0432214,0.028532932,-0.0054415953,-0.030312475,-0.028488925,-0.015641434,-0.0047333036,0.00022058094,-0.005611959,0.012004151,-0.011941176,0.019531935,0.05011399,0.0025996985,-0.03862516,-0.014985539,-0.009675381,0.00027619596,-0.0040151933,0.024015903,-0.016359698,0.008321043,-0.05258389,-0.043357164,0.0026653046,-0.020935273,-0.0072307503,-0.023433981,-0.008205251,-0.010277737,-0.005850209,0.03425211,0.0117981,-0.05435418,0.017603733,-0.04315011,-0.019411664,0.041632988,0.006076862,0.021996602,0.02051587,-0.011107674,-0.020041091,-0.011709494,0.025004081,0.02452602,0.041038565,0.00673612,-0.034166917,0.0061600087,0.06342128,-0.041447,0.035320964,0.020796146,0.027177421,-0.007424794,0.040201455,0.019962505,-0.005334947,-0.020997647,0.05266241,-0.016124131,0.040314585,-0.04455891,0.009211351,0.006927498,0.005492507,-0.045967877,-0.022771586,0.038717315,-0.023777047,0.0012884132,-0.02655445,-0.060563844,0.033927135,-0.013516582,0.03080641,-0.034261595,0.009967534,-0.020868272,-0.0011073326,0.0057187593,-0.000