	 ('bef1fb9c-6733-47f4-850a-d7b68300b882'::uuid,'Say-That-Again-I-Dare-You','This meme template features a intense and iconic scene from a well-known 1994 crime film. The image shows a man in a black suit and tie, with a distinct afro hairstyle, in a confrontational pose. He''s holding a handgun pointed directly at the viewer, creating a sense of immediate tension and drama.

The man''s facial expression is stern and determined, with furrowed brows and a slight grimace, conveying a mix of anger and resolve. His other hand is raised, palm open, in a gesture that could be interpreted as a warning or a pause.

The setting appears to be indoors, with a light-colored wall or door visible in the background. The lighting creates a contrast between the dark suit and the brighter background, drawing focus to the man''s intense expression and the threatening gesture with the gun.

This image has become a popular meme template due to its dramatic composition and the intense emotion it conveys. It''s often used online to express extreme disagreement, frustration, or to humorously overreact to mundane situations.

The power of this meme lies in the juxtaposition of the serious, high-stakes scenario depicted in the original film scene with often trivial or everyday situations it''s applied to in meme form. This contrast creates humor and allows users to express exaggerated emotions in a recognizable, culturally significant format.','/memes/Say-That-Again-I-Dare-You.jpg',2,'{}','{"Samuel L Jackson","pulp fiction"}',0.0,'[0.045591325,0.00127341,0.010381589,0.05648382,-0.0068085515,-0.07516984,-0.050363023,-0.0061699688,-0.0071174074,0.04588436,0.006099446,-0.0065123034,0.017545313,-0.0060040154,0.025324149,0.044336416,0.009673321,-0.016803613,0.0032465036,0.02008096,0.020872837,-0.027522875,-0.067316175,-0.07646463,0.014668805,0.0565099,-0.01485747,0.012833187,0.041503377,0.036890805,0.01622189,0.00658838,-0.0010315272,-0.036974702,-0.004542472,-0.01582211,0.0459856,-0.056115538,-0.009877146,-0.0023958615,-0.00026041086,0.0020793062,0.04712541,-0.011693524,-0.04332074,-0.024363972,-0.021835523,0.00041764777,0.0051811766,-1.6535889e-05,0.008521916,-0.010171533,0.04254445,0.031126877,-0.046048217,-0.027764475,-0.03057821,-0.01799804,0.015711548,0.018537384,0.047453202,-0.015661074,-0.012474639,-0.032049645,-0.034540806,0.016874395,-0.013036499,-8.567119e-05,-0.033055715,-0.0259496,0.004394348,0.011912562,0.035004284,0.05005014,-0.027289433,0.0050933063,-0.05745515,-0.04256431,0.02733232,-0.027280414,-0.0023718015,0.028413426,0.0075011356,-0.04364069,-0.028491547,-0.0090157315,0.030048467,0.005384779,0.021712193,-0.037790436,0.0048193657,0.06481598,-0.050341796,0.003916407,0.010895296,0.061678413,-0.0064316904,0.029574772,0.0009290855,0.033662528,-0.026745347,0.058919307,-0.05305177,0.034765605,-0.027355574,0.013767259,0.04618021,-0.019402038,-0.017318686,-0.0251446,0.036900073,-0.008254994,0.002937605,-0.007203796,-0.05296161,0.026490781,-0.009479842,0.038778745,-0.0192231,-0.0022982548,-0.03428699,-0.006331306,0.027508209,-0.034260042,-0.0029361479,-0.02584922,0.015443598,0.03628