	 ('ce525514-25a6-48c6-95c5-02cd71c65879'::uuid,'Leonardo-Dicaprio-Cheers','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man in a formal black tuxedo and bow tie, holding up a champagne glass in a toasting gesture. The man has a charismatic and mischievous expression, with a broad smile and slightly squinted eyes that convey a sense of knowing satisfaction or celebration. His hair is styled in a classic 1920s look, slicked back and parted to the side.

The background of the image is blurred but suggests a glamorous party setting, with twinkling lights or perhaps fireworks creating a festive atmosphere. This backdrop adds to the overall feeling of luxury and celebration.

The image is taken from a scene in the 2013 film adaptation of "The Great Gatsby," set in the Roaring Twenties. This context gives the meme a sense of opulence, excess, and jazz-age decadence. The character''s expression and gesture make it a perfect template for expressing congratulations, sly acknowledgment, or ironic celebration in meme form.

The composition of the image draws focus to the man''s face and the raised glass, making his expression the central element. The warm tones of his skin contrast with the dark tuxedo and the sparkling background, creating a visually striking image.

This template is often used to convey a sense of smug satisfaction, mock celebration, or sarcastic approval in various online contexts. Its popularity stems from the universally recognizable gesture of toasting combined with the character''s cheeky, knowing look.','/memes/Leonardo-Dicaprio-Cheers.jpg',2,'{}','{"The Great Gatsby party with Jay Gatsby","great job"}',0.0,'[0.0035201341,-0.023277637,0.025459537,0.034793947,-0.040654726,-0.043347184,-0.0036743921,0.005250651,0.010103879,0.004973378,-0.027395496,-0.007658674,0.036931034,-0.011034438,0.011964446,1.9672654e-05,-0.0137743335,-0.038124394,-0.032671038,0.032169525,0.013116143,-0.0017955018,-0.08900971,-0.07271814,0.05119504,0.0692608,-0.017684722,0.049286887,0.07015983,0.03094928,0.02365229,0.04216603,-0.028015988,-0.038440328,0.006661827,-0.018809063,0.019509746,-0.034509756,-0.01513709,-0.01355772,0.024857316,-0.0013111061,0.039883394,-0.0037320182,-0.03363072,-0.008746618,0.0055025453,-0.047443096,0.00911298,-0.020292582,-0.031903002,-0.03942167,0.014113294,0.028967563,0.012474207,-0.0017316327,-0.041535553,-8.204328e-05,0.0061319955,0.019675836,0.056844693,0.012656222,-0.026185188,-0.04301839,-0.040445607,0.028713062,-0.003035107,0.00288526,-0.01725141,-0.03504332,-0.03702493,-0.0051750345,0.032134652,0.029495027,-0.036609456,-0.00096972473,-0.032349974,-0.012942807,0.012710859,0.0011401123,0.027624385,0.010425724,-0.013916903,-0.012769798,-0.022039913,-0.030808302,0.038591426,0.036138773,0.026268754,-0.03044222,-0.015575032,0.04714509,0.020364406,0.0057949405,0.0073133344,0.037531007,-0.011948515,0.046382423,0.0008209499,0.023296773,-0.04389657,0.019868257,-0.03685055,0.039358743,-0.0040797717,0.014784013,0.041439753,-0.002338327,-0.028422896,-0.033829525,-0.0061222054,-0.016246827,0.009808225,-0.021556988,-0.074437715,0.04016635,0.0012297075,0.01973543,-0.040831372,0.007624319,-0.004464928,-0.012972931,0.015091173,-0.030006394,-0.028182125,-0.022536106,0.0046739816,0.046290766,-0.0629819,0.0163265,0.0136