	 ('1cbecb09-9a6d-48c5-8ab3-a1a34a5adc07'::uuid,'But-Thats-None-Of-My-Business','This meme template features Kermit the Frog, the iconic Muppet character, in a pose that has become famously associated with internet meme culture. The image shows Kermit from the chest up, holding a glass of tea and looking off to the side with a somewhat smug or knowing expression.

Kermit''s distinctive bright green fabric texture is clearly visible, showcasing his fuzzy puppet construction. His round white eyes with black pupils are characteristic, with one eye visible and slightly squinted, adding to his expression of mild disdain or judgment.

The frog is holding a clear glass filled with what appears to be iced tea. The tea has a rich amber color, and a Lipton tea bag tag is visible hanging over the rim of the glass, clearly identifying the brand. This detail adds to the casual, everyday nature of the scene.

The background is slightly out of focus, suggesting an indoor setting, possibly a kitchen or living room. This blurred background keeps the focus squarely on Kermit and his beverage.

The composition of the image is tight, with Kermit filling most of the frame. This closeness allows viewers to clearly see his expression and the details of the tea, which are central to the meme''s concept.

This image has become a popular meme template often used to convey a sense of passive-aggressive judgment, gossipy attitude, or a "but that''s none of my business" sentiment. The act of sipping tea has become synonymous in internet culture with observing drama or sharing opinions on controversial topics while maintaining an air of detachment.

The high quality of the image, likely a still from a Muppets production, lends itself well to meme creation, allowing for clear visibility of Kermit''s expression even when text is added to the image.','/memes/But-Thats-None-Of-My-Business.jpg',2,'{}','{"Kermit the frog","kermit drinking lipton iced tea","kermit frog tea","kermit lipton","kermit drinking tea"}',0.0,'[0.0185276,-0.03795814,0.026084924,0.0310059,0.0015754452,-0.06889578,-0.02677,0.015963262,-0.028258715,0.032685455,-0.013972273,-0.011105333,0.04769894,0.017989961,-0.013895694,0.00053566095,0.007560946,-0.018245213,-0.007240028,-0.020694384,0.013333423,0.028130637,-0.026515488,-0.0030858067,0.0074301306,0.050499883,-0.01553542,0.022057438,0.070304915,-0.010199835,0.014184352,0.03449081,0.0089337565,-0.052311152,0.002645326,-0.0034655088,0.02171766,0.01122058,-0.0047828746,-0.044712275,0.022535868,-0.015247735,0.047990866,9.12767e-05,-0.004086434,0.01598951,-0.015903,0.010106305,0.044941247,0.002586008,0.015300104,0.0026258146,-0.00043756707,0.0014859469,-0.030485718,-0.037823323,-0.014698438,-0.031748794,-0.0088081,0.04645529,0.021119965,-0.0014610217,0.009285895,-0.032437723,-0.018509364,-0.017468218,-0.025921278,0.00385936,-0.025042843,-0.010031936,0.0012917181,0.01919458,-0.011622246,0.01932379,-0.044014048,-0.034000944,-0.007381303,0.024057731,0.009208064,0.018174255,0.0047069807,0.027298389,-0.0010644556,-0.019355265,-0.008677509,-0.022019254,-0.012523127,0.028705759,-0.003361775,-0.02684935,-0.016856909,0.08222089,-0.029415855,-0.0017442979,0.00064775685,0.029167162,-0.0057080714,0.025626121,-0.006688868,0.013315573,-0.008285988,0.011676862,-0.012966592,0.045283157,-0.03501388,-0.0062661716,0.050657943,-0.021775186,-0.047752436,-0.01699679,-0.008999957,-0.0056027845,0.01912704,-0.02213007,-0.03397888,0.0027600485,-0.0054375837,0.052599143,-0.061078604,0.024096012,-0.034541883,-0.02944471,-0.0051962733,0.007037802,-0.008384373,-0.017240148,-0.0032172552,0.03908418,-0.042707734,0.043677315,0.025517