	 ('e4b5a4a5-606b-417f-bfae-fd24e444574a'::uuid,'Finding-Neverland','This meme template is a three-panel image sequence, likely from a film or TV show, depicting an emotional interaction between an adult man and a young boy.

In the first panel, we see a close-up of the boy''s face. He appears to be around 8-10 years old, with short dark hair and a pale complexion. His expression is one of wide-eyed concern or anxiety, looking up at something off-screen. He''s wearing what seems to be a dark jacket or suit, suggesting a formal setting.

The second panel shows the adult man, who is wearing a dark suit and tie, indicating a formal or professional context. He has a somber, empathetic expression on his face as he looks down, presumably at the boy (who is out of frame in this shot). The man''s appearance suggests he might be in a position of authority or mentorship to the child.

In the final panel, we see a wider shot of both characters sitting on a park bench. The setting is outdoors, with trees visible in the background, creating a serene, green environment. The man is embracing the boy, who is leaning into him. This gesture conveys comfort, protection, and emotional support.

The progression of the images suggests a narrative of the boy experiencing some distress or worry, the man recognizing and acknowledging the boy''s feelings, and finally offering physical comfort and reassurance.

This template is often used in memes to represent situations where someone is seeking or receiving emotional support, validation, or comfort from another person, especially in scenarios where a more experienced individual is consoling someone less experienced or more vulnerable. The stark emotional contrast between the first and last panels makes it particularly effective for conveying themes of mentorship, parental guidance, or unexpected sources of understanding and compassion.','/memes/Finding-Neverland.jpg',3,'{}','{"Johnny Depp And Little Kid Crying","dad and son cry"}',0.0,'[0.036978066,-0.024358924,0.03542097,0.043665573,0.035345983,-0.06296761,-0.017540757,-0.011328349,-0.0035786678,0.021844503,-0.009930689,0.0019661565,0.008233863,0.0056413165,-0.016707044,-0.002659962,0.014285043,-0.011887459,-0.028931385,0.017282687,-0.0011914459,0.019956468,-0.06051682,-0.04774583,-0.011079612,0.045799367,0.001441216,0.015241798,0.03811471,0.03128806,-0.0056083105,0.003488645,-0.00892008,-0.026426654,-0.012877343,-0.00082912244,0.042168956,-0.054835305,0.005110505,-0.023090651,0.031321738,-0.0053942166,0.043354187,-0.015657933,-0.03433969,-0.019798296,-0.0045948518,0.0016333872,0.013959692,-0.011195331,0.01054514,-0.02743178,0.047370475,0.030644031,-0.019004302,-0.016750976,0.018989602,-0.0021289012,0.009991029,0.014241599,0.021078477,-0.005246365,-0.013328777,-0.037165727,-0.024396151,0.01708093,-0.036883574,-0.0021452517,-0.01060358,0.0036193626,-0.010636741,0.027773794,0.012558162,0.025156483,-0.018596869,0.020117432,-0.03062847,-0.0037311371,0.047297228,0.0067748534,0.035155017,0.0688769,0.009028668,-0.0147667425,-0.009893796,-0.03398816,0.021742538,0.028578157,0.02999976,-0.029730417,-0.021109415,0.048072573,0.003642045,-0.006319776,-0.0022820854,0.06053625,-0.018827183,0.033717602,-0.009582331,-0.0019543252,-0.005373026,0.04548535,-0.017376702,0.032791376,-0.04977671,0.011535877,0.04764796,-0.009608703,-0.026787084,-0.026022857,0.009655763,-0.0129441805,-0.00180736