	 ('b5c5d87a-dd95-467b-bc5a-59d21581617f'::uuid,'Brace-Yourselves-X-is-Coming','This meme template features a prominent figure from what appears to be a medieval or fantasy-themed production, likely a popular television series or film. The image shows a man in profile, facing to the right of the frame. He has a stern, contemplative expression with furrowed brows and a full beard, giving him a rugged, weathered appearance.

The man is dressed in attire befitting a northern or winter setting. He wears a thick, dark cloak or coat with a large fur collar that drapes over his shoulders. The fur is distinctively striped, suggesting it might be from an animal like a wolf or wild dog. This clothing choice evokes a sense of harshness and survival in a cold climate.

In his hands, the man firmly grasps what looks to be the hilt of a sword, though only the top portion is visible. This detail, combined with his attire and demeanor, suggests he is a warrior or leader in a challenging environment.

The background of the image is plain white, which is typical for many meme templates as it allows for easy editing and addition of text. This stark contrast emphasizes the character and his outfit, drawing full attention to his serious expression and posture.

The image is cropped to focus on the upper body and face of the man, which is a common technique in meme templates to highlight facial expressions and emotional conveyance. The lighting in the image is natural and even, adding to the somber and realistic tone of the scene.

