	 ('475be777-353e-4176-84a0-17b1bddc6ca3'::uuid,'Marked-Safe-From','This meme template features a minimalist design centered on a single, simple icon. The focal point of the image is a small flag symbol, depicted as a blue triangle attached to a thin vertical line. This icon is commonly associated with marking locations or indicating status in digital interfaces.

The flag icon is positioned at the top of the image, slightly off-center to the left. It''s rendered in a flat, two-dimensional style with a solid blue color for the triangular flag part and a thin black line for the pole. The simplicity of this icon makes it instantly recognizable and versatile for various contexts.

Below the flag icon, there is text, but as per your instructions, I won''t describe the specific wording. The text is presented in a plain, black font against the white background, creating a stark contrast that draws the eye.

