	 ('cc128d4c-74c1-4cf6-a1cd-142b79495d2e'::uuid,'Aint-Nobody-Got-Time-For-That','This meme template features a close-up shot of a woman with a very expressive face. She appears to be outdoors, with a light green tiled or brick wall visible in the background. The woman has dark skin and short dark hair, partially covered by a light-colored headband or scarf with a pinkish tint.

Her facial expression is the focal point of the image, conveying a mix of surprise, disbelief, and perhaps a touch of exasperation. Her eyes are wide open, eyebrows slightly raised, and her mouth is open as if she''s in the middle of speaking or reacting to something shocking or unbelievable.

The woman is wearing a brightly colored top, visible only at the shoulders, which appears to be yellow with some blue detailing. This adds a vibrant touch to the image, contrasting with the muted background.

