	 ('3b8032e2-95d9-48c8-a207-ca17c6dc4edf'::uuid,'Left-Exit-12-Off-Ramp','This meme template consists of two stacked images that create a humorous contrast between a road sign''s directions and a driver''s actual behavior.

The top image shows a standard green highway sign mounted on an overpass. The sign indicates "LEFT" in yellow text at the top, with "EXIT 12" below it in white. The main part of the sign displays two arrow symbols: a straight arrow pointing upward and a right-turning arrow branching off from it. This sign clearly instructs drivers to keep left for the through lane or take a right turn for the exit.

The bottom image, seemingly taken from a dashcam or following vehicle, shows a blue classic car (possibly from the 1960s or 1970s) on a curved road. The car is dramatically drifting, with its rear end swinging out to the left, creating a cloud of tire smoke. This maneuver is taking place on what appears to be an exit ramp, with yellow arrow signs visible on the right side of the road indicating a sharp right turn ahead.

The humor in this meme template comes from the juxtaposition of the clear, lawful instructions on the road sign and the reckless, tire-screeching behavior of the driver below. Instead of simply following the sign''s direction to exit right, the driver has chosen to drift dramatically, technically going left (as per the "LEFT" instruction) but in an extremely exaggerated and dangerous manner.

This template is often used to humorously represent situations where someone technically follows instructions or rules, but does so in an unexpected, over-the-top, or rebellious way. It can be applied to various scenarios in life where people find creative or unorthodox ways to interpret and follow directions.','/memes/Left-Exit-12-Off-Ramp.jpg',2,'{}','{"car drifts off highway","sharp turn on road","car drift meme","left exit ramp 12","swerve meme","swerving car","road meme","no u car skid","car exiting"}',0.0,'[-0.006591122,-0.005525551,0.004444803,0.011846794,0.004534308,-0.063939035,0.008327247,0.021455018,-0.0090540955,0.07552924,0.012375162,0.030442411,0.03749664,-0.0269461,-0.014081396,0.018928725,0.0032985385,-0.012911891,-0.047479656,0.03871896,-0.013146764,-0.042165402,-0.024927186,-0.0346871,0.006343506,0.031401824,0.031418692,-0.013757756,0.055652343,0.033938296,0.027226996,-0.0014217952,-0.016224582,-0.059909344,-0.010713044,-0.005241668,0.026649807,-0.029352082,0.014666196,0.0085197445,-0.0066753216,-0.016507603,0.009320059,-0.04514411,-0.018982194,-0.058552347,-0.035398886,-0.009371515,0.017125102,0.0025434198,-0.010154293,-0.0018104976,0.02394022,-0.033898998,-0.02433956,0.0021591242,-0.026639778,0.0045489618,-0.010888428,0.03743546,0.05349825,-0.020822413,0.014358646,-0.048362605,-0.04397757,0.004160001,0.008743489,0.016077787,-0.037314724,-0.0035238343,-0.05080231,0.029566944,0.012918142,-0.012077731,-0.042345792,0.025625706,-0.01728765,0.017099554,-0.015620413,0.0070551983,0.013366224,0.037730005,-0.007355069,-0.023200717,0.0013175013,0.019248815,0.008363475,0.0432276,0.030858088,-0.020036161,0.004355504,0.031930856,0.0056966133,-0.0019125689,0.028378677,0.05014692,-0.023696763,0.039059956,0.012679034,-0.010340077,-0.015699962,0.054667015,-0.0054160203,0.029845456,-0.03336819,0.0074232863,0.036271952,-0.003964915,-0.066152066,-0.027841065,-0.019318542,-0.030696264,0.035882387,-0.006905428,-0.013039058,0.018527752,0.0043966747,0.04295241,-0.0259160