	 ('a4d83f71-1dec-43df-ac88-d4661330ecca'::uuid,'This-Is-Where-Id-Put-My-Trophy-If-I-Had-One','This meme template features two panels showing a cartoon character, likely from an animated TV show, in contrasting emotional states.

In the top panel, we see a man with an exaggerated, wide grin and bulging eyes. He has black hair styled in a pompadour and wears a white shirt with a black tie, suggesting a formal or professional setting. His arm is outstretched, gesturing towards something off-screen. The background shows what appears to be a museum or gallery setting, with spotlights illuminating a display area cordoned off by velvet ropes and brass stanchions. There''s a sense of excitement and pride in his posture and expression.

The bottom panel shows the same character in a drastically different emotional state. His face is contorted into an expression of extreme frustration or rage. His teeth are bared in a grimace, eyes squeezed shut, and he appears to be yelling or screaming. His hands are raised and clenched, emphasizing his intense reaction. The background remains the same, implying a sudden and dramatic shift in the character''s mood or situation.

The stark contrast between the two expressions – from gleeful presentation to enraged reaction – is what gives this template its comedic potential. It''s often used to represent situations where initial excitement or confidence quickly turns to frustration or disappointment. The exaggerated cartoon style amplifies the emotional impact, making it a versatile template for expressing extreme mood swings or unexpected turns of events in various contexts.','/memes/This-Is-Where-Id-Put-My-Trophy-If-I-Had-One.jpg',2,'{}','{"this is where i would put my trophy","timmy turner`s dad","this is where i would put my thropy if i had any","here''s where i would put my trophy... if i had one"}',0.0,'[0.016361764,-0.015950754,0.014224758,0.0032791824,0.012279149,-0.075973324,-0.022398455,-0.031469703,-0.012302078,0.04759941,-0.007013614,-0.0074143894,0.02721041,-0.013675841,0.008488402,0.006020089,-0.020119889,-0.040946513,-0.025960991,0.05328621,0.009807737,-0.013381834,-0.06316235,-0.03331124,0.0018350563,0.06414651,-0.010876411,0.01318602,0.032979034,0.030684529,0.029072102,0.0047010765,-0.031603564,-0.05273202,0.032810774,0.0030738455,0.027917381,-0.093678445,-0.0001460369,-0.037003987,0.02559568,-0.026339233,0.013510948,-0.037295066,-0.015700765,-0.028077852,-0.0042255158,-0.0012897574,0.03371474,-0.03031117,-0.0017374291,-0.033056937,0.020177038,0.047065854,-0.026380705,-0.054214954,-0.015294063,-0.012897154,0.007658288,0.017038519,0.052609425,0.018814232,-0.015764467,-0.05091624,-0.056550607,-0.0041494784,-0.041721124,-0.012359227,-0.06743985,0.004906152,-0.0029406715,0.020231599,0.052108936,-0.003932498,-0.073153704,3.734991e-05,-0.04019422,-0.015458139,0.03204153,-0.0008813332,0.021075014,0.03002237,-0.016189877,-0.0059418855,-0.00921422,-0.0154598,0.032014217,0.015923059,0.009527601,-0.03003326,-0.0008879868,0.050162084,-0.019692732,0.014885525,0.01421739,0.05013903,0.0059580873,0.03432994,-0.0131846955,0.0020679925,-0.013314724,0.041910816,-0.04038782,0.037775584,-0.04984