	 ('8d460770-7579-4f01-95e1-88e6f5be4f8c'::uuid,'X-All-The-Y','This meme template features a simple yet expressive cartoon character known as the "All the Things" or "X All the Y" meme. The character is drawn in a basic stick figure style with a distinctive large, circular head and tiny body. The head dominates the image, with exaggerated features including huge, round eyes and an enormous gaping mouth showing a row of teeth, giving an impression of extreme excitement or enthusiasm.

The figure is colored in bright hot pink, standing out starkly against a vibrant yellow background that resembles an explosion or burst of energy. This yellow burst emphasizes the character''s apparent excitement and adds a sense of dynamic action to the static image.

The character''s arms are outstretched, with one arm raised high, holding what appears to be a broom or similar long-handled object. This posture, combined with the character''s wide-open mouth, conveys a sense of triumphant exclamation or unbridled enthusiasm.

The simplicity of the drawing style contrasts with the intensity of the emotion being portrayed, which is part of what makes this meme template so versatile and popular. It''s often used to express overwhelming excitement, determination, or the desire to do something to an extreme degree.

The image''s composition draws the viewer''s eye immediately to the character''s face, making the emotional impact immediate and unmistakable. The bold colors and simple lines make it easily recognizable even when reduced in size, contributing to its effectiveness as a meme template across various digital platforms.','/memes/X-All-The-Y.jpg',1,'{}','{"all the things","all of the things","what do we want"}',0.0,'[0.013190833,0.0009460683,0.022589529,0.010484312,0.027987365,-0.04936931,0.03241322,0.001195458,0.013623338,0.05323747,0.0064782426,-0.0011508568,0.03455325,-0.024682323,-0.012726532,0.009718113,-0.011404823,-0.03622517,-0.011396273,0.0411459,-0.016901853,-0.01659601,-0.07114638,-0.042920712,-0.0029695742,0.04838061,-0.020112135,0.00693871,0.0618271,0.023625884,-0.018888231,0.005597941,-0.0018111378,-0.04353051,-0.025552537,-0.03128846,0.01650717,-0.044815864,0.01070716,-0.04256379,0.03396495,-0.017422574,0.03216726,-0.013882796,-0.016391117,-0.022995254,0.002923316,-0.010728522,0.042011026,-0.042230934,0.022943532,-0.008722062,-0.0006811484,0.039039172,-0.028772011,-0.020393435,-0.022613322,-0.014013231,0.020298883,0.017396552,0.016895315,0.021197727,-0.005947779,-0.061555374,-0.04166783,-0.011300078,-0.027281526,-0.039116934,-0.004309745,4.04139e-05,0.008001638,0.017884921,-0.014489203,-0.05188817,-0.060087163,0.023984428,-0.02513327,-0.01682787,0.017318359,0.0063970885,0.033400483,0.038897533,-0.02220133,0.007644466,-0.015074532,0.004616319,0.020026142,0.020272054,0.018835925,-0.03908057,-0.014252777,0.032684404,0.01956552,0.020016754,0.052036233,0.009850666,-0.0033203082,0.037904136,-0.014347828,-0.0055408184,-0.019668896,0.05384302,-0.028861148,0.024420355,-0.028197408,0.012481077,0.029292226,0.027789786,-0.022624219,-0.07077303,0.022556413,-0.020290118,0.025300983,-0.019029485,-0.017414497,0.034559168,0.015305433,0.06295371,-0.05109972,-0.015056696,-0.0352014,-0.009613504,-0.026583629,-0.00094373536,-0.007965382,-0.018648217,-0.011728019,0.015700532,-0