	 ('9821b4e7-91ee-4a64-b889-0ab36885abd9'::uuid,'Success-Kid','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a young toddler boy set against a distinctive geometric background. The child is wearing a white and green baseball-style shirt and has light-colored hair. His expression is what makes this image particularly meme-worthy - he has a determined, slightly furrowed brow and is making a fist with one hand, held up near his chest in a gesture of triumph or resolve. This expression conveys a sense of satisfaction, determination, or even smug confidence, which is often humorously juxtaposed with various captions in meme usage.

The background of the image is divided into several triangular sections of different shades of blue and purple, creating a stylized, almost retro feel. This color-blocked background is characteristic of many advice animal style memes, which use similar geometric patterns to frame their central images.

The combination of the child''s expression and pose with the stylized background creates a versatile template. It''s commonly used to express feelings of minor victory, stubborn persistence, or childish logic applied to adult situations. The contrast between the serious, adult-like expression on a young child''s face and the simplistic, colorful background adds to the humorous potential of the image.

This meme is widely recognized in internet culture and has been used extensively to convey a wide range of sentiments, often related to small personal triumphs or ironically applied to trivial accomplishments. Its enduring popularity stems from the universally relatable nature of the child''s expression and the flexibility with which it can be applied to various situations through different captions.','/memes/Success-Kid.jpg',2,'{}','{"Motivation Baby","Motivation Kid","Success Baby"}',0.0,'[-0.00019438501,-0.026502177,0.022045787,0.015852483,0.01944045,-0.023502205,0.00046386098,-0.008215581,0.009357664,0.04229607,-0.03086807,-0.0005221483,0.011017143,0.02960336,0.009397285,0.006560931,0.010780321,-0.035963103,-0.023860583,0.03101187,-0.014934552,0.036100715,-0.07192341,-0.019191178,0.026169619,0.057261482,0.017148737,0.011686707,0.06188871,0.018054344,-0.014990241,0.01871375,-0.01948376,-0.017078672,-0.01865728,-0.023610359,0.02380833,-0.037590157,0.005699688,-0.022957388,0.037338346,-0.040318586,0.043552067,-0.01623035,-0.043540616,-0.036632206,-0.0200311,-0.016789675,0.047504768,-0.0104335705,0.015619681,-0.022712031,0.029298676,-0.0058863056,-0.02840959,-0.007782893,0.024416253,-0.018845344,0.0070797224,0.032088786,0.03510124,-0.013533229,-0.003877448,-0.04236444,-0.033175815,-0.03819648,-0.008786925,-0.010182324,-0.014556369,-0.0021245684,-0.01369048,0.021337641,-0.009237472,-0.022979874,-0.035257228,-0.002509586,-0.024201462,-0.0073662326,0.010112363,0.02194939,0.0119135035,0.072169505,0.0085669765,-0.034821313,-0.024040448,-0.012716744,0.017413057,0.052088663,0.01260132,-0.03320473,0.011500884,0.06172092,-0.020336453,0.0055250255,0.02645754,0.048220526,0.0017614466,0.047063988,-0.011941763,0.009586082,0.005138859,0.027739132,-0.01753748,0.026640367,-0.075544275,0.009665897,0.025069755,-0.020643875,-0.042730514,-0.014888563,0.022267,-0.0127286315,0.0020163334,-0.032018445,-0.047504045,0.044625707,0.001693623,0.056968592,-0.03101304,-0.022202615,-0.027794704,0