	 ('03edc177-9067-4b67-8a75-4488410e57b0'::uuid,'Y-U-No','This image depicts a popular internet meme known as "Y U No Guy" or "Y U No" meme. It features a crudely drawn, black and white stick figure character with a distinctive large, round head set against a solid blue background.

The character''s face is the focal point of the image, displaying an intense, exaggerated expression of frustration or anger. The eyes are wide and bulging, with the left eye noticeably larger than the right, conveying a sense of wild-eyed intensity. The nose is drawn with sharp angles, contributing to the overall agitated appearance.

The mouth is open wide in what appears to be a shout or exclamation, revealing clenched teeth. This gives the impression that the character is mid-yell, emphasizing the emotional outburst the meme typically represents.

The character''s body is minimally drawn, with just a hint of a collar or shirt neckline visible. One arm is raised and bent at the elbow, with the hand outstretched in a gesture that seems to accompany the verbal outburst.

The simplistic, almost childlike quality of the drawing contrasts sharply with the extreme emotion it conveys, which is part of what makes this meme so striking and widely recognizable. The blue background serves to make the black and white figure stand out prominently.

This meme template is typically used to express frustration, disbelief, or to pose rhetorical questions in a comically exasperated manner, often with text added above and below the image in the classic meme format.','/memes/Y-U-No.jpg',2,'{}','{fixed,"why u no"}',0.0,'[0.012368929,-0.018741842,0.005237145,-0.009802222,0.023518337,-0.041869618,0.022926813,0.025281183,-0.011920017,0.06652454,-0.018775268,-0.0068214363,0.04668493,0.0036305413,-0.008242079,-0.0044482024,0.0041776467,-0.008149759,0.002971122,0.034952924,-0.012202518,-0.0048962897,-0.05914311,-0.034938242,0.009337202,0.04926424,-0.019636448,-0.0058703506,0.034609325,0.0174802,-0.005466905,0.003782118,-0.04877435,-0.064378634,0.0049395342,-0.011572057,0.034914516,-0.06616341,-0.0069707166,0.005948515,0.026676584,-0.042797882,0.014800702,-0.007977811,-0.008353455,-0.02973197,-0.04907622,0.016428431,0.013431257,-0.014914814,0.0018829897,-0.017296648,0.017612092,0.03703275,-0.028406948,-0.037467863,0.022367526,-0.019929335,0.018553011,0.026923984,0.04395651,0.00034714883,0.0153483655,-0.025000691,-0.05250679,-0.013474546,-0.053041723,-0.015116752,-0.021013873,0.021449074,-0.008540282,0.040330052,0.021134714,-0.014831273,-0.04588318,0.03761448,-0.027047567,-0.031013256,0.020048708,0.022542087,0.025613515,0.055594165,-0.010569581,-0.008351643,-0.028282788,0.0030985686,0.013852219,0.011481028,0.008094615,-0.0269016,-0.0115868095,0.045045797,-0.027329097,0.026083613,0.0348002,0.034224804,-0.008754195,0.03995219,-0.004917609,-0.03725072,0.011981424,0.05471321,-0.034878474,0.04959399,-0.0495737,-0.012163906,0.040561818,0.016911218,-0.045985114,-0.030708378,0.0020189271,0.0017316218,0.02710092,-0.005955699,-0.03461609,0.004703473,-0.017725227,0.042165507,-0.046269957,-0.026783073,-0.015991725,0.021812564,-0.025155574,-0.0167504,0.0041651134,-0.015824575,0.008570504,0.02585213,-0.019020488,0.03037859,0.022443855,-0.024850968,-0.010970196,0.048645314,-0.0128713185,0.025867142,0.023716059,0.018257648,0.040277086,-0.041