	 ('ecdf6ce2-2935-4e17-98b6-fcbd2e9edcee'::uuid,'Imagination-Spongebob','This meme template features the iconic character SpongeBob SquarePants from the popular animated TV series. The image shows SpongeBob''s upper body and face, with his signature square shape, bright yellow color, and porous texture clearly visible. He''s wearing his usual white shirt and red tie, hinting at his lower body even though it''s out of frame.

SpongeBob''s expression is one of wonder and joy. His large blue eyes are wide open, giving him an innocent and excited look. His buck-toothed smile is prominently displayed, adding to his cheerful demeanor. His arms are raised on either side of his head, palms facing outward, in a gesture that suggests amazement or celebration.

The most striking element of this image is the vibrant rainbow arching over SpongeBob''s head. The rainbow is composed of the traditional ROYGBIV colors (red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet) and is adorned with small white stars or sparkles along its length. This rainbow adds a magical, fantastical quality to the image.

The background behind SpongeBob and the rainbow is a muted, olive-green color, which makes the bright colors of SpongeBob and the rainbow pop even more vividly.

This template is often used to express feelings of happiness, wonder, or childlike amazement. The combination of SpongeBob''s excited expression and the magical rainbow creates a sense of whimsical joy that''s perfect for memes about positive experiences or naive enthusiasm.','/memes/Imagination-Spongebob.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob rainbow","nobody cares","bob esponja tpm"}',0.0,'[0.037401643,-0.023137962,-0.0022427542,-0.0034098767,0.009693048,-0.011401439,0.007648904,-0.021181582,0.013774114,0.034845028,0.009857867,-0.0008887348,0.036503974,-0.0060093054,-0.009687874,-0.051980942,-0.028843006,-0.045934662,-0.060806815,0.01394688,-0.012869563,-0.00033273088,-0.037901342,-0.023891201,-0.018835824,0.054647274,0.00061332376,0.014453514,0.050238002,0.01206846,0.021346396,0.012566596,0.0047281445,-0.041354902,0.043003414,0.01779012,0.007977174,-0.040389493,0.009178736,-0.042309597,0.041409045,-0.032238036,0.0030357384,-0.033156727,-0.027437361,-0.02803469,-0.02477665,0.005168003,0.02989211,-0.016911058,0.0143876085,0.0016974633,0.0354993,0.031314578,-0.022303332,-0.026021356,-0.004964698,-0.014711062,0.018598253,0.010426451,0.007085177,0.018028764,-0.034329057,-0.07584504,-0.034766626,-0.00093393563,-0.014438649,-0.032571122,-0.015428548,-0.024917074,-0.009209982,0.020980833,0.0024925673,-0.0340159,-0.03278094,-0.017008007,-0.053387593,-0.023146184,-0.005256139,0.017303245,0.028551582,0.027878258,0.013780431,-0.015083477,-0.020592557,-9.756633e-05,0.024391705,0.035019834,0.028005138,-0.046889648,-0.043040022,0.07502896,0.011521639,0.026133917,-0.0037618729,0.041424762,0.007514342,0.05455757,0.023216859,0.017959341,0.030880751,0.05399224,-0.013581773,0.038947675,-0.017565722,0.029931786,0.020550048,0.04099669,-0.025534268,-0.018627897,0.045398183,0.005131484,0.033165455,0.007683688,0.013309127,0.018874068,-0.004104964,0.0711232,-0.056499932,-0.024677403,-0.04545919,0.012504957,-0.01646131,-0.014164329,0.009223209,0.018171385,0.0056482935,0.050579302,-0.023095226,0.01292720