	 ('375ee80a-4a62-40fc-ae1e-aff845f8f787'::uuid,'Spongebob-Ight-Imma-Head-Out','This meme template features a scene from the popular animated TV series SpongeBob SquarePants. The image captures SpongeBob''s living room in his iconic pineapple house under the sea.

The background is a distinctive bright blue wall with a bamboo-like pattern, characteristic of the show''s underwater aesthetic. On the left side of the frame is a wooden door with a circular porthole window, reminiscent of a ship''s door, fitting the nautical theme.

In the center of the image, SpongeBob is seated on a red armchair. However, he''s not sitting normally - he''s perched atop a red and white striped life preserver or swim ring. SpongeBob''s expression is one of mild discomfort or resignation, with half-lidded eyes and a slight frown, conveying a sense of reluctance or weariness.

To the right of SpongeBob is a small side table with a purple shell-shaped lamp, adding to the underwater decor. On the wall above, there''s a framed picture of Gary the snail, SpongeBob''s pet.

The composition of the scene creates a sense of SpongeBob preparing to leave, suggested by his position on the life preserver as if it''s a makeshift seat or preparation for going out.

At the bottom of the image, text reads "IGHT IMMA HEAD OUT" in all caps, which has become a popular phrase associated with this meme format. This text is typically replaced or modified by meme creators to fit various scenarios where someone is about to leave a situation.

The overall tone of the image, with SpongeBob''s tired expression and unusual seating arrangement, lends itself well to humorous captions about reluctantly leaving or escaping from uncomfortable or undesirable situations.','/memes/Spongebob-Ight-Imma-Head-Out.jpg',1,'{}','{"Ight Imma Head Out","aight imma head out","spongebob aight","alright I''m out","spongebob getting out of chair"}',0.0,'[0.033304483,-0.025884911,-0.0046009077,-0.0029157747,0.027636677,-0.027744338,-0.0023340639,0.013428507,0.030133791,0.00729756,0.03600406,0.025558652,0.0034980837,0.0150142405,-0.008058536,-0.022166098,-0.014871698,0.002736332,-0.08239114,0.018674599,0.010020947,-0.009640934,-0.023952806,-0.014105173,-0.0035286644,0.022791354,0.044694792,0.034242798,0.036607966,0.017226525,0.03425437,0.0051602083,0.0054089082,-0.030217696,0.022589099,-0.019718515,0.04666796,-0.046015333,0.009911025,-0.049785767,-0.003342728,-0.009431721,0.01397366,0.007938555,0.010454543,-0.021143971,-0.015174797,0.02302658,0.043177515,0.012873536,0.016539605,0.011284424,0.023856683,0.039768014,-0.0121905655,-0.03049756,-0.03250252,0.03005243,0.022096314,0.027282558,0.016607134,-0.020102851,-0.047562752,-0.043403726,-0.040662404,-0.004674512,0.016181247,-0.021068271,-0.018760964,0.0024974204,0.0060706967,0.026943495,0.042376626,-0.011879226,-0.030035995,-0.0057042274,-0.037947707,0.024879485,0.0127101615,0.0413257,0.039891403,0.050412185,0.039605893,-0.043451637,-0.021675231,-0.035602145,0.021028,0.04601085,0.028082086,-0.04245115,-0.023848403,0.077368274,-0.015741615,0.016515382,0.003711598,0.030558325,0.014273021,0.06526135,0.04153665,-0.020830885,-0.0061616036,0.060847297,-0.02678295,0.034252826,-0.0015700444,0.032468487,0.029011779,0.02316075,-0.0681006,-0.013553366,0.017205648,0.0009839482,0.033300262,-0.007388462,-0.011583397,0.045614637,-0.051039718,0.054488614,-0.045319024,0.0011355004,-0.020849599,0.0037915553,0.002219737,-0.036663562,0.0014934414,-0.011734769,0.023410598,0.025337424,-0.032829624,0.0177