	 ('322bb292-cd77-4e96-9672-d89e2ab81dcf'::uuid,'Drake-Hotline-Bling','This popular meme template features two contrasting images of a man set against a vibrant yellow background, creating a distinct visual structure for expressing preference or rejection.

In the top panel, we see a close-up of the man with a disapproving expression. He''s wearing a bright red puffy jacket and has a closely shaved head and beard. His face is turned slightly away from the viewer, with his eyes nearly closed and brow furrowed in a look of distaste or rejection. His hand is raised near his face in a gesture of refusal or pushing away, emphasizing the negative reaction.

The bottom panel presents a stark contrast. The same man is now shown with a pleased, almost blissful expression. His eyes are closed, and he''s sporting a warm smile, conveying satisfaction or approval. He''s still wearing the same red jacket, but now we can see he has on a yellow shirt underneath with a black logo (resembling the Air Jordan symbol). His posture is more open and welcoming, with one hand visible making a pointing or presenting gesture.

The juxtaposition of these two images creates a format perfect for memes about preferences, where the top image represents something disliked or rejected, while the bottom image represents something approved or preferred. The bright colors (yellow background, red jacket) make the template visually striking and easily recognizable.

This template has become iconic in meme culture, often used to humorously compare two options or ideas, with the bottom panel always representing the more favored choice. Its simplicity and clear body language make it universally understandable and highly versatile for a wide range of topics and jokes.','/memes/Drake-Hotline-Bling.jpg',2,'{}','{drakeposting,drakepost,"drake hotline approves","drake no yes","drake like dislike","drake faces"}',0.0,'[0.026056072,-0.038940273,0.032268558,0.013268507,-0.011130316,-0.058729824,-0.01749191,0.0058885836,-0.023436349,0.057051398,0.017634206,-0.009803309,0.048272166,0.0018010666,-0.011629121,-0.021752538,-0.002299036,-0.026489813,-0.055348326,0.017533489,-0.010315995,0.003483155,-0.06620757,-0.027276225,-0.0149302455,0.05395984,-0.021831036,-0.015905414,0.07227195,0.00029274807,-0.0020679107,-0.008530904,0.0068344786,-0.044000845,-0.009994563,-0.01822023,0.010873272,-0.057017557,-0.0058676642,-0.03869416,0.055287156,-0.017675236,-0.017821746,-0.049204227,-0.04175035,-0.035028722,-0.02886188,-0.0027996353,0.014808305,-0.026744833,0.0009007456,-0.024049386,0.015805677,0.010003653,-0.041273277,-0.041085884,-0.010569545,0.009095205,0.008148911,0.0405338,0.032528263,0.0345188,-0.026208635,-0.059844404,-0.0075460393,-0.011868127,-0.035713106,0.007796091,-0.031454846,-0.017422263,0.003569362,-9.140277e-05,0.019377714,-0.033904903,-0.036498304,-0.010764708,-0.016708653,-0.04191942,0.0029878996,-0.022428988,0.03042456,0.06443329,-0.013300343,-0.0050274786,-0.009740741,0.0005905498,0.044816878,0.047156867,0.010661332,-0.01601698,-0.03555451,0.05439861,0.01885811,0.0028187486,0.011581637,0.028032849,-0.0073337634,0.028142283,-0.0152121885,-0.009988859,-0.0032331347,0.05472578,-0.0061305063,0.013178232,-0.043218724,0.009997397,0.04066433,-0.009157055,-0.041638795,-0.029460551,0.015650276,-0.025963128,-0.018929219,3.2671203e-05,-0.027176129,0.03551503,0.016570656,0.05269422,-0.03980964,-0.025009172,-0.05143662,-0.0054607866,-0.026818499,