	 ('c582281b-06a3-4d9a-baf9-cc66992eceff'::uuid,'Steve-Harvey','This meme template features a man in a professional setting, likely a television studio or talk show set. He is an African American male with a bald head and a distinctive mustache. His expression is animated and engaging, with raised eyebrows and a wide, enthusiastic smile showing his teeth. 

The man is wearing a dark pinstriped suit jacket, which gives him a polished, formal appearance. This is contrasted with a vibrant lime green tie that adds a pop of color and draws attention to his chest and face. In his breast pocket, there''s a hint of a blue pocket square, further accentuating his dapper style.

His body language is open and expressive. Both of his hands are raised to about shoulder height, palms facing upward and fingers slightly spread. This gesture often accompanies explanation or emphasis in conversation, suggesting he''s in the middle of making a point or reacting to something with surprise or excitement.

The background of the image is somewhat blurred, but you can make out warm lighting and what appears to be floral arrangements, typical of a television set backdrop. The overall atmosphere suggests this is a still from a lively discussion or interview.

