	 ('e86d9060-605f-468d-ac24-d6f4b63a2b43'::uuid,'The-Scroll-Of-Truth','This meme template is a four-panel comic strip featuring a green, alien-like character with a brown hat. The artwork has a hand-drawn, watercolor style with vibrant colors and expressive characters.

In the first panel, we see the character standing in a crystal-filled cave next to a red treasure chest partially submerged in water. The background is filled with blue-green crystals, giving it a magical, underground atmosphere.

The second panel shows the character excitedly holding up a yellow scroll with a radiant glow around it. The character''s expression is one of pure joy and triumph, with a wide smile and raised arms.

The third panel focuses solely on the scroll, which is now unrolled but completely blank. It''s held by green hands at the top and bottom of the frame.

In the final panel, we see the character running away in frustration, arms flailing, through shallow water. The scroll is still visible, trailing behind them as they flee.

This comic template is designed to set up an expectation of a great discovery or revelation, only to humorously subvert it with disappointment. The blank scroll in the third panel acts as a versatile space where different punchlines or messages could be inserted, making it adaptable for various meme contexts.

The artist''s signature "Robotatertotcomics" is visible in the first panel, crediting the original creator of this amusing and relatable comic strip template.','/memes/The-Scroll-Of-Truth.jpg',1,'{}','{"I''ve finally found it... after 15 years",nyehhh}',0.0,'[0.02462097,-0.007275323,0.012588428,-0.01114605,0.0028642411,-0.026767312,0.0019279453,0.02002281,-0.0016408828,0.039076593,0.013506258,0.026075134,0.014982533,-0.015155434,-0.017976247,-0.008543631,0.010069077,-0.011856713,-0.011806093,0.018824453,0.0009536894,-0.020420581,-0.051720608,-0.0005900936,-0.009005014,0.04017184,0.03542352,0.026040452,0.07764861,0.04278418,0.03171295,0.00038856838,-0.002611499,-0.08613421,0.016855044,0.029104661,0.0016869982,-0.017600652,-0.011327986,-0.04364318,0.0020330155,-0.025795538,0.027588697,-0.00016743345,-0.013773654,-0.0054926067,-0.023395061,0.009082382,0.012770941,-0.035170715,0.02532573,-0.019851223,-0.0068946667,0.0092640575,-0.002863296,-0.0017673923,-0.010045285,-0.02466163,0.012971175,0.026539974,0.043716542,0.0036845384,0.03167139,-0.02262469,0.016264817,0.041060016,-0.019589614,-0.01648744,-0.035911337,0.016375292,-0.039148103,0.028725093,0.026997706,-0.05338594,-0.065522194,0.004519115,-0.010596308,-0.013746985,-0.012498905,0.023117853,0.017378863,0.025238922,-0.011067826,-0.017372694,-0.0017346798,-0.027206002,0.01989736,0.03935436,0.0028501428,-0.06501018,0.02106831,0.053069733,0.011907126,-0.0048653358,0.040607344,0.02947845,-0.04625708,0.051779628,0.0012259528,0.012876451,-0.041275393,0.045317702,-0.053737342,0.028732644,-0.018034115,0.0054194597,0.029239247,-0.0112828035,-0.024746878,-0.027572885,0.007857496,0.002769988,0.0074042943,-0.010399354,-0.039444987,0.026866075,9.219362e-05,0.016336888,-0.017047945,-0.017374111,-0.035103887,-0.03929176,-0.043293677,-0.014708161,-0.010946731,-0.049523633,-0.0076713264,0.03669843,-0.017195672,0.024910692,-0.0009839556,-0.012992909,-0.01101988,0.021148564,-0.032363396,0.01938453,0.008124537,0.042654775,0.018786712,-0.