	 ('2282ba59-e611-417e-a123-45b1b854722e'::uuid,'Look-At-Me','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a man with dark skin and short, tightly curled hair. The image has a slightly washed-out, vintage quality to it, suggesting it may be a still from an older film or television show.

The man''s facial expression is the focal point of the image. He has an intense, wide-eyed stare directed straight at the camera, conveying a sense of shock, surprise, or disbelief. His mouth is slightly open, and he appears to be holding up two fingers in a ''V'' shape near his chin, though the hand itself is mostly out of frame.

The lighting in the image is soft, coming from the left side, which creates some subtle shadows on the right side of his face. He appears to be wearing a yellowish or light-colored shirt, though only the collar is visible in the frame.

The background is blurry and indistinct, suggesting a shallow depth of field that keeps the focus squarely on the man''s expressive face. There''s a hint of what might be a window or light source behind him, adding to the overall atmospheric quality of the shot.

