	 ('59ea5d06-2939-4722-a454-4f813f366c15'::uuid,'Sad-Pablo-Escobar','This meme template consists of three images, seemingly from the same character or storyline, depicting a man in different contemplative or solitary poses. The images appear to be from a TV series or film set in a past era, likely the 1980s or early 1990s, based on the clothing and settings.

In the top image, we see a man with curly hair and a mustache sitting on a yellow swing or porch swing outdoors. He''s wearing a light blue short-sleeved shirt and has a pensive expression, gazing off to the side. The background shows a grassy area, suggesting a backyard or park setting.

The bottom left image shows the same man, or a very similar-looking character, sitting alone at a small kitchen table. The scene is dimly lit, creating a moody atmosphere. He''s wearing a light-colored t-shirt with some green detailing. The kitchen appears dated, with old-fashioned appliances visible in the background.

The bottom right image depicts the man standing alone by an empty swimming pool. He''s wearing a white polo shirt and blue jeans, hands at his sides, again with a contemplative stance. The pool is clearly unused, with leaves or debris visible, adding to the sense of isolation or neglect.

The combination of these three images creates a powerful visual narrative of loneliness, introspection, and perhaps melancholy. The character''s consistent solitude across different settings emphasizes themes of isolation and inner turmoil. This template is often used in memes to express feelings of sadness, loneliness, or deep thought, allowing users to superimpose text that contrasts with or amplifies the emotional tone of the images.','/memes/Sad-Pablo-Escobar.jpg',3,'{}','{"pablo escobar waiting","man waiting","waiting man","lonely man","narcos waiting","narcos bored","narcos alone","forever alone","coronavirus sports"}',0.0,'[0.019117136,-0.026561337,0.00818319,-0.0017244554,0.0012279127,-0.056054357,-0.020905117,0.011143342,0.020791214,0.036383115,0.02112263,-0.017502122,0.015664695,-0.0038500351,-0.027050084,-0.009439111,-0.010629691,-0.015595518,-0.063441716,0.02269718,-0.003227236,0.0066713337,-0.0474525,-0.023209868,0.006388769,0.044029556,-0.023058686,0.043595575,0.035326257,0.032245208,0.032502595,-0.034709085,-0.009102798,-0.031993214,0.0009603491,0.019947618,0.014873053,-0.053607583,-0.005921271,-0.029079331,0.0066006216,-0.011961923,0.03238626,-0.026916517,-0.013588706,-0.027527474,-0.0030288147,-0.023529273,0.037023988,-0.0008913467,0.0112796705,-0.036632355,0.03274986,0.012944713,0.012864164,-0.032544877,0.006573061,0.02003557,0.010191304,0.007636565,0.007511697,0.017759727,-0.027275685,-0.049833123,-0.027383797,0.0038198114,0.0015967732,0.015577153,0.008903163,-0.024588736,-0.011740959,0.005842343,0.0109504815,-0.002651445,-0.026362348,0.0037882747,-0.01586274,-0.015042565,0.02326961,0.008172656,0.0092688305,0.058924537,-0.020218402,-0.0075211767,-0.042512823,-0.0734725,0.0029507538,0.035868812,0.030131664,-0.02058514,-0.033929028,0.06330929,0.00051214645,0.0101475725,0.0030236878,0.022524027,0.012492789,0.025974836,0.020047706,0.00922568,0.019340497,0.034515563,-0.026124837,0.022000432,-0.04509716,-0.0042333393,0.027431305,-0.0024080845,-0.0588734