	 ('a4c50686-cb49-4619-8707-de9fbf8eafeb'::uuid,'Skeptical-Baby','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a baby with a distinctively skeptical or unimpressed expression. The infant appears to be less than a year old, with smooth, pale skin and very little hair. The baby''s face dominates the frame, capturing the viewer''s attention immediately.

The most striking aspect of the image is the baby''s facial expression. Their eyebrows are slightly furrowed, creating small creases on their forehead. The eyes are wide and alert, looking directly at the camera with an intense, almost judgmental gaze. The baby''s mouth is pursed, with the lower lip slightly protruding, adding to the overall look of doubt or disapproval.

The baby is wearing what appears to be a brown or tan colored outfit, possibly a sweater or onesie, visible at the bottom of the frame. This earthy tone contrasts with the baby''s fair complexion and adds a touch of warmth to the image.

The background is slightly out of focus, suggesting an indoor setting, possibly near a window due to the soft, natural lighting that illuminates the baby''s face from one side, creating subtle shadows and adding depth to the image.

This meme template is widely known as the "Skeptical Baby" or "Unimpressed Baby" meme. It''s often used to express doubt, judgment, or a lack of being impressed by something, mirroring the baby''s facial expression. The image''s power comes from the incongruity of seeing such a complex, adult-like expression on an infant''s face, which makes it both humorous and relatable for many viewers.

The high-quality, clear image allows for easy addition of text above and below the baby''s face, making it a versatile template for various meme scenarios where skepticism or judgment is the primary sentiment being conveyed.','/memes/Skeptical-Baby.jpg',2,'{}','{"sceptical boy"}',0.0,'[-0.0036028596,-0.034235433,0.016825484,-0.010693015,0.033331823,-0.039610513,-0.0017832527,-0.0055906717,-0.0036082717,0.0457765,0.008860899,-0.015725521,0.05321603,0.0013975359,-0.009638704,0.005208278,0.016548174,-0.01889198,0.00360879,-0.0070147817,-0.022309631,0.017332254,-0.0874255,-0.03322288,0.0066388403,0.037611272,0.025963271,-0.015581404,0.057646494,0.023645213,-0.041236836,-0.007689346,0.002369571,-0.011441862,0.006215702,-0.008133164,0.037873894,0.0036783174,0.0005171982,-0.02627649,0.015599308,0.00023355016,0.034989182,-0.029324267,-0.033472233,-0.048728816,-0.016425839,9.989293e-05,0.049473252,0.0069431,0.015143085,-0.026308162,0.005094759,-0.004526784,-0.017941205,-0.033817824,0.010855254,0.0009094773,-0.0074326224,0.035414193,0.038244072,0.01900988,0.019452134,-0.028014507,-0.041506864,-0.0030584056,-0.04572619,-0.002073016,-0.00611804,-0.030948747,0.03517736,0.023191977,-0.007879675,-0.007023069,-0.039429188,0.013445075,-0.040418886,-0.007800099,0.01234245,0.017136209,0.020036949,0.0030909458,0.025731986,-0.01247251,0.0023254228,-0.039442632,0.024769422,0.035687566,0.0014483939,-0.026750773,0.011089504,0.055018567,-0.004603155,0.016521879,0.046493076,0.04408953,-0.012007101,0.03246802,-0.007722297,0.0011411413,0.003012265,0.020097898,0.008471453,0.02982605,-0.04355995,-4.5197237e-05,0.0085302405,0.001169246,-0.046272013,-0.030744644,-0.0069485228,-0.038004834,-0.0002495715,-0.0072754854,-0.028103517,0.026104024,-0.013403239,0.07105811,-0.06176563,-0.05387989,-0.056016292,0.015331407,-0.01267826,0.015174997,0.011457771,-0.0077009965,-0.008305108,0.048087195,-0.02325087,0.012899402,-0.013540424,-0.043998297,0.012126542,0.050026953,-0.01908224,-0.0010177251,0.022431888,-