	 ('3a9d7f4d-63e6-45bb-a4b4-ef68cf1e3209'::uuid,'Philosoraptor','This meme template features a stylized image of a dinosaur, specifically a Velociraptor, set against a background divided into four quadrants of varying shades of green. The dinosaur''s head and one of its claws are depicted in a high-contrast, black-and-green sketch style that gives it a vintage or comic book appearance.

The raptor''s head dominates the upper left portion of the image. It''s shown in profile, facing right, with a large, expressive eye that seems to convey a sense of contemplation or scheming. The dinosaur''s mouth is slightly open, revealing a hint of teeth, which adds to its pensive expression. The scales and texture of the dinosaur''s skin are intricately detailed, creating a realistic yet stylized effect.

Below the head, in the lower right corner, a single claw of the Velociraptor is visible. This claw is curved and sharp, characteristic of the species'' feared hunting appendage. The inclusion of just the claw creates a sense of anticipation or threat, as if the creature is ready to act or pounce.

The background''s four-quadrant design uses different shades of green, creating a simple yet effective contrast that makes the black dinosaur image pop. This color scheme gives the meme a cohesive, monochromatic look while also referencing the prehistoric, jungle-like environment associated with dinosaurs.

This image is widely recognized as the "Philosoraptor" meme, typically used to pose paradoxical questions or humorous philosophical ponderings. The thoughtful expression of the dinosaur, combined with the threatening claw, creates a juxtaposition between intellect and primal instinct that lends itself well to contemplative or ironic humor.

The simplicity and stark contrast of the image make it highly versatile as a meme template, allowing for easy addition of text and quick recognition by viewers familiar with internet culture. Its enduring popularity speaks to its effectiveness in conveying a range of complex ideas through a simple, visually striking image.','/memes/Philosoraptor.jpg',2,'{}','{"green dinosaur","dinosaur wondering","philosiraptor meme","dinosaur ponder"}',0.0,'[0.013732992,-0.006457674,0.018305266,0.02491642,0.008519874,-0.018805021,-0.035661917,0.0226977,0.0015298841,0.05417876,-0.002359833,-0.044116437,0.02944206,0.021578606,0.009369974,0.018650237,0.02001529,-0.012495825,-0.036859307,0.021599332,-0.024491068,-0.0103158085,-0.060872946,-0.04966546,0.001748591,0.05213154,0.014011159,0.017780509,0.0880357,0.010176883,-0.018046185,0.0054549747,0.0048238174,-0.060471497,-0.003238185,-0.01800244,0.004888298,-0.031846292,-0.014537323,-0.0020837411,0.05030167,-0.025731256,0.043257102,-0.004151917,-0.031259492,-0.037519187,-0.016611015,-0.017668752,-0.00956232,-0.04406908,0.041284114,-0.013262903,0.00014340329,-0.018058319,-0.052025843,-0.019140411,-0.0028498434,0.00076433696,-0.00078136846,0.02206761,0.039305184,0.007686013,0.025768494,-0.030301714,-0.038312867,-0.0033912992,-0.0016144278,0.009949521,-0.011812484,-0.013810912,-0.004075882,0.014346734,0.02046253,-0.0032332954,-0.04468724,0.013772258,-0.004634167,-0.031726673,0.018671125,0.026952753,0.032058783,0.046659324,-0.03650829,0.005441172,-0.028171543,-0.007659927,-0.008572349,0.049616348,-0.00030202113,-0.04377833,-0.017683461,0.06845468,0.012747431,0.03160887,0.03799281,0.029901894,-0.035846744,0.046836942,-0.00912297,-0.0067645065,-0.025223581,0.02807233,-0.015278846,0.025567546,-0.039430633,0.0070017083,0.019754728,-0.036244467,-0.019225664,-0.045565546,0.029714903,-0.004274998,0.006873973,-0.026638439,-0.030117624,0.015118884,-0.0062546064,0.029697556,-0.031105367,-0.023088764,-0.07046438,-0.038110167,-0.03610476,0.023494512,-0.