	 ('4245fe6f-d53a-4f8d-b4fe-594338c49414'::uuid,'Trump-Bill-Signing','This meme template features a prominent political figure seated at what appears to be the Resolute Desk in the Oval Office of the White House. The image captures a moment during an official signing ceremony or executive order presentation.

The central figure is an older man with distinctive blonde hair, wearing a dark suit with a blue tie. His expression is serious and somewhat stern as he looks directly at the camera. He is holding up a large white document or executive order folder, which is open to display blank pages inside.

The composition of the image is tight, focusing primarily on the upper body of the seated figure and the document he''s displaying. In the background, we can see glimpses of the iconic gold curtains often associated with the Oval Office, as well as parts of other suited individuals standing behind him, though they are partially out of frame.

The document being held is the focal point of the image, with its blank white pages clearly visible. This element is particularly significant in the meme context, as it''s often used as a template where text or images can be edited onto the blank pages for humorous or satirical effect.

The image has a slightly grainy quality, suggesting it may be a screenshot from a video broadcast. The lighting is warm, emphasizing the golden tones of the room and the figure''s hair.

